NK072(nu)002:1: // dpal gsang ba snying po'i spyi don gtan la 'bebs
NK072(nu)002:2: pa'i thal 'gyur rigs pa'i sgo 'byed ces bya ba
NK072(nu)002:5: bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha dbyer ma mchis pa dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK072(nu)002:6: bla med theg pa'i bcud 'dus pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:7: gsang sngags kun gyi rgyal po'i rgyud //
NK072(nu)002:8: gsang ba'i snying por nges pa can //
NK072(nu)002:9: ston mdzad drug pa kun tu bzang //
NK072(nu)002:10: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog tu //
NK072(nu)002:11: sku lnga'i tshul gyi 'khor lnga la //
NK072(nu)002:12: gsung lnga rang byung rig pa'i dbyangs //
NK072(nu)002:13: sgrog mdzad kun bzang rigs lngar 'dud //
NK072(nu)002:14: rgyal ba'i bka' yi bsdu ba po //
NK072(nu)002:15: gsang 'dzin lag na rdo rje ni //
NK072(nu)002:17: rnam kun rigs kyi bdag por mchod //
NK072(nu)002:18: gter chen bla ma'i ye shes gang //
NK072(nu)002:19: bzhad pa'i rdo rjer 'phos pa yis //
NK072(nu)002:20: skal ldan pho nya'i rten 'brel gyis //
NK072(nu)002:21: mkha' spyod gnas su khrid der 'dud //
NK072(nu)002:22: d+aa ki gsang ba'i lung byang gis //
NK072(nu)002:23: bskul ba'i skyabs mchog bzhad pa'i bka' //
NK072(nu)002:24: spyi bor lhung las 'gong ma nus //
NK072(nu)002:25: rtsom la spobs pa'i snang ba stsol //
NK072(nu)002:26: mtha' bral chos nyid zab mo'i don //
NK072(nu)002:27: tha snyad tshig gis mtshan min yang //
NK072(nu)002:28: tshad ma gsum gyi gtan tshigs kyi //
NK072(nu)002:30: nang na ma dang mkha' 'gro yis //
NK072(nu)002:31: bzod par bzhes la grogs mdzod cig /
NK072(nu)002:32: de la thog mar 'phros tshul gyi rnam bzhag dang bshad tshul gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:34: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK072(nu)002:36: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:37: zhes pa'i gzhung 'di la 'phros pa yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:39: gzhung snga ma'i skabs su rgyud 'di'i ched du bya
NK072(nu)002:40: ba'i gdul bya la dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum
NK072(nu)002:42: mtshan bstan pa tsam gyis rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don
NK072(nu)002:43: khong du chud par 'gyur ba'i dbang po yang rab
NK072(nu)002:44: mchog tu gyur pa rnams kyi don du sdud pa
NK072(nu)002:45: po gsang bdag gis bka' bsdu mdzad pa'i thog mar
NK072(nu)002:46: rgyud don gyi ngo bo dang mthun pa'i mtshan klad
NK072(nu)002:47: du bkod tshul gyis rnam bzhag dag de nyid bstan
NK072(nu)002:48: nas / rang gi ston pa la bstod phyag mdzad tshul gyi rnam bzhag de ston pa la /
NK072(nu)002:49: bcom ldan dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK072(nu)002:50: zhes pa'i gzhung 'di byung ba gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:51: rgyud kyi gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa de la
NK072(nu)002:52: thun mong ma yin pa'i phyogs bzung nas mdor bstan
NK072(nu)002:53: pa / rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gzhi tshogs tshul gyi sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa /
NK072(nu)002:54: sdud pa po gsang bdag rang nyid rigs lnga dbyer
NK072(nu)002:55: mi phyed pa rgyal ba drug pa nyid du khas
NK072(nu)002:56: blangs na gleng gzhi'i don bsdus te bstan pa dang
NK072(nu)002:57: gsum las / thun mong ma yin pa'i phyogs bzung
NK072(nu)002:58: nas gleng gzhi mdor bstan gyi rnam bzhag de ston
NK072(nu)002:62: bstan bshad bsdud gsum gyi sgo nas rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyud gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa las /
NK072(nu)002:63: rgyud 'byung ba'i rkyen gleng bslang ba la /
NK072(nu)002:64: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:66: thun mong ma yin par lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi
NK072(nu)002:67: ched du ston pas mdun bsus te gleng bslang tshul
NK072(nu)002:71: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK072(nu)002:72: rdzogs pa'i skye mched byang chub sa chu me rlung
NK072(nu)002:73: nam mkha' srid gsum thams cad sangs rgyas sangs rgyas
NK072(nu)002:74: nyid la sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK072(nu)002:78: phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben /
NK072(nu)002:79: srid snyigs ma phung po thams cad mchog gi gzhan
NK072(nu)002:80: du nyid las btsal kyang rgyal bas mi brnyes so
NK072(nu)002:82: thun mong du gleng bslang pa /
NK072(nu)002:85: rdzogs pa'i skye ba skyes pa 'gag pa gnas pa dmigs pa 'gro 'ong nyid na 'gro 'ong med //
NK072(nu)002:86: zhes pa'i gzhung tshan gsum po 'di byung /
NK072(nu)002:87: thun mong gi gleng bslang de la gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:89: lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang la brten nas sangs rgyas te /
NK072(nu)002:90: ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pas rgyud zhu ma dgos kyang /
NK072(nu)002:91: gzhan don du go phye ba'i 'khor rnams rgyu lhan
NK072(nu)002:92: cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas lhag pa don dam
NK072(nu)002:93: gyi bden pa ma rtogs pas ye nas gsang /
NK072(nu)002:94: kun btags kyi ma rig pas lhag pa kun rdzob
NK072(nu)002:95: kyi bden pa ma rtogs pas rang bzhin gyis gsang
NK072(nu)002:96: / snang stong ya gyal du bzung bas lhag pa
NK072(nu)002:97: bden pa dbyer med ma rtogs pas ngo bo nyid
NK072(nu)002:98: kyis gsang yul dang yul can du bzung bas spyod
NK072(nu)002:99: yul dang bral bar ma rtogs pas shin tu gsang
NK072(nu)002:100: / ba ste / de ltar gsang ba bzhis chod
NK072(nu)002:101: pa'i gdul bya rnams la rgyud bstan pa'i sgo nas
NK072(nu)002:102: thugs rjes bzung bar rigs so zhes lhan cig pa'i
NK072(nu)002:103: 'khor rnams kyis ston pa la zhus tshul gyi rnam
NK072(nu)002:104: bzhag de ston par byed pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:105: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos /
NK072(nu)002:106: sna tshogs ngo bo gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK072(nu)002:107: zhes pa'i gzhung 'di byung ston pas lan rtsal tshul ni /
NK072(nu)002:108: sems can thams cad bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po can yin pa las /
NK072(nu)002:109: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis bcings grol ltar snang yang /
NK072(nu)002:111: 'khor ba'i chos rnams thag khra yis //
NK072(nu)002:112: sbrul ltar med pa nyid du 'dod //
NK072(nu)002:113: ces pa ltar gshis la bcings grol gnyis ka ma
NK072(nu)002:114: grub pa'i tshul mtshon dpe dang bcas pa'i rnam bzhag
NK072(nu)002:115: de nyid ston par byed pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:118: rang gi rnam rtog sna tshogs gnas dang /
NK072(nu)002:120: sus kyang bcing par rnam rtog nan gyis mkha' la mdud pa bor //
NK072(nu)002:122: de ltar ston pa'i thugs rje skyes te /
NK072(nu)002:123: bcings grol med pa'i gshis de kho na nyid kyi chos ston par dgyes nas /
NK072(nu)002:124: rang nyid sku dang ye shes su ye nas lhun
NK072(nu)002:125: gyis rdzogs pa 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du gsal
NK072(nu)002:126: ba'i don sangs rgyas kun gyis thugs su chud pa'i
NK072(nu)002:127: chos de lhan cig pa'i 'khor la dngos su bstan
NK072(nu)002:128: nas / go phye ba'i 'khor la brgyud nas ston pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:129: sprul pa spro bar zhal gyis bzhes tshul gyi rnam bzhag de ston par byed pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:130: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:131: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas ches //
NK072(nu)002:132: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK072(nu)002:133: zhes pa'i gzhung 'di byung ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:136: de la thog mar mtshan klad du smos pa'i dgos pa /
NK072(nu)002:138: de la rtsod pa spongs pa gsum /
NK072(nu)002:140: mtshan klad du smos pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:142: bum pa zhes pa'i ming las /
NK072(nu)002:143: lto ldir zhabs zhum chu skyor gyi don byed nus pa'i dngos po go ba ltar /
NK072(nu)002:146: dbang po rab kyis gzhung gi don go ba dang
NK072(nu)002:147: 'bring gis don gyi rnam grangs khong du chud pa
NK072(nu)002:148: dang / tha mas kyang sman gyi kha byang ltar glegs bam btsal bde ba'i ched yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:150: 'dis ni rang bzhin che ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:151: mtshan nyid dang ni don bstan phyir //
NK072(nu)002:152: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud chen las //
NK072(nu)002:153: mdor bsdus gtan la phab pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:154: rang bzhin gsang ba zhes bya ste //
NK072(nu)002:155: che ba zhes bya snying po'i don //
NK072(nu)002:156: de kho na nyid mtshan nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:157: nges pas nges don mdor bstan pa //
NK072(nu)002:158: de ltar rnam pa bzhi po ru //
NK072(nu)002:159: mdor bsdus spyi yi don du bshad //
NK072(nu)002:161: rgyud 'di'i ched du bya ba'i gdul bya dbang rnon de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:162: khyod kyis mtshan 'di la brten nas go tshul dang rtog tshul yod de /
NK072(nu)002:163: gsang ba sogs mtshan bzhis rim pa bzhin /
NK072(nu)002:166: mtshan nyid gzhan rnam par bcad pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:167: drang don ma yin par nges don the tshom dang bral bar go ba gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:168: ston tshul de dang rjes su mthun par rgyud kyi
NK072(nu)002:169: rang bzhin dang che ba sogs kyang rtogs pa yin
NK072(nu)002:170: pa'i phyir / gsang ba zhes pa'i mtshan de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:171: khyod la dbye na gsum du yod de /
NK072(nu)002:172: rang bzhin dang gab pa dang sbas pa'i gsang ba gsum du yod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:173: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba chos can khyod bshad du yod de /
NK072(nu)002:174: sems nyid bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos skur
NK072(nu)002:175: ye nas rang chas su gnas kyang blo'i spyod yul
NK072(nu)002:176: dang ma bral bar ma rtogs pa de yin pa'i
NK072(nu)002:177: phyir / dper na nam mkha' nyid mig gis mthong byar ma gyur pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:179: e ma ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK072(nu)002:180: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK072(nu)002:181: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK072(nu)002:182: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK072(nu)002:183: zhes pas gsang tshul bzhi ste /
NK072(nu)002:184: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas don dam bden pa ma rtogs pas ye nas gsang ba /
NK072(nu)002:185: kun rtags kyi ma rig pas kun rdzob bden pa ma rtogs pas rang bzhin gyis gsang ba /
NK072(nu)002:186: snang stong so sor bzung bas dbyer med ma rtogs pas ngo bo nyid kyis gsang ba /
NK072(nu)002:187: yul yul can du bzung bas spyod yul dang bar ma rtogs pas shin tu gsang ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:188: gsang tshul bzhis chod pa'i tshul du gsang ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:189: gab pa'i gsang ba chos can /
NK072(nu)002:191: gdul bya 'khrul pa'i blo can gyi rtogs dka' ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:192: re chod can gyi rtogs su mi rung bas gab pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:193: dper na mig ser can la dung gi kha dog bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:194: de yang rang bzhin gyi rgyud du gab pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:195: khyod rang la rang chas su gnas kyang rtog pas sgrib nas gab pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:196: de 'byin byed lung tshad ma'i bdag po ston pa
NK072(nu)002:197: sangs rgyas nyid kyis 'byin par mdzad pa'i phyir dkyus
NK072(nu)002:198: yi ge la gab pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:199: khyod bshad du yod de ras chod can mgo rmongs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:202: man ngag gab pa'i tshul du gnas pa de //
NK072(nu)002:203: man ngag tshad ma'i bdag po rdo rje slob dpon gyis 'byin par mdzad pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:205: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK072(nu)002:206: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK072(nu)002:207: zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:208: sbas pa'i gsang ba chos can /
NK072(nu)002:210: rgyud zab mo 'di gsang sngags kyi man ngag med pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:211: sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa rnams la sbas pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:212: de dag gi spyod yul ma yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:213: gcan gzan chen po'i sgyu rtsal spre'usa mi bzod pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:214: seng zho snod ngan du blug bya ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:216: gsang sngags kyi mdzad spyod sbyor sgrol la sogs pa
NK072(nu)002:217: lta spyod 'brel bas spyad byar gsungs pa de dag
NK072(nu)002:218: brda'i tshul gyis sbas pa te /
NK072(nu)002:220: gsang sngags skyon yod ma yin te //
NK072(nu)002:221: sems can don phyir rab tu gsang //
NK072(nu)002:222: gsang thub dngos grub mi yal bas //
NK072(nu)002:223: gsang phyir brda' dag sna tshogs gsungs //
NK072(nu)002:224: zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:226: snying po zhes pa'i mtshan de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:227: khyod la'ang dbye na gsum du yod de /
NK072(nu)002:228: rgyu dang 'bras bu dang bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po dang gsum du yod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:232: rgyud 'di theg pa thams cad kyi 'phro gazhi'am 'byung
NK072(nu)002:233: ba'i rgyu lta bur gyur pas na de ltar du
NK072(nu)002:236: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK072(nu)002:237: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK072(nu)002:238: zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:239: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i snying po chos can /
NK072(nu)002:241: theg pa'i sgo gang nas bsgrubs kyang /
NK072(nu)002:242: mthar rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di'i don mngon du byed dgos pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:244: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK072(nu)002:245: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK072(nu)002:247: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK072(nu)002:248: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK072(nu)002:249: zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:250: gsum pa bcud 'dus pa'i don gyi snying po chos can /
NK072(nu)002:252: gtan tshigs kyi sgo gang nas gtan la phab kyang
NK072(nu)002:253: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i ngo na rtog
NK072(nu)002:254: tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa
NK072(nu)002:255: gnyis su sangs rgyas pas 'khor ba rang bzhin gyis
NK072(nu)002:256: rnam par dag pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:258: don bsdus gsung rab bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK072(nu)002:259: de las lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK072(nu)002:260: de ni rnam dag lam min te //
NK072(nu)002:261: rang blos bsam pa'i 'khrul pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:264: de kho na nyid zhes pa'i mtshan 'di chos can /
NK072(nu)002:265: khyod la'ang dbye na gsum du yod de ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK072(nu)002:266: ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK072(nu)002:267: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid dang gsum du yod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:269: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid chos can /
NK072(nu)002:271: rtog tshogs thams cad rang rig las mi gzhan pas
NK072(nu)002:272: snang stong gnyis med rang byung gi ye shes la
NK072(nu)002:273: sgom byed kyi blos ma bcos par bzhag pas na
NK072(nu)002:274: de skad du brjod pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:276: ma bcos lhun mnyam ji bzhin ngang bzhag ngang //
NK072(nu)002:277: zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:279: ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:281: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid de goms pa
NK072(nu)002:282: las 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi phyag rgya
NK072(nu)002:284: ma nor bas de ltar du brjod pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:286: rgyu 'bras lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK072(nu)002:287: zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:289: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:291: 'bras bu de'ang sgrib byed kyi zhen pa dag pa'i tshe rang la yod pa'i don snang ba las /
NK072(nu)002:292: gzhan nas byung ba ma yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:294: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK072(nu)002:295: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK072(nu)002:298: ji snyed brgyud pa'i kha brgyud kyang //
NK072(nu)002:299: yang dag don gyi snying po ni //
NK072(nu)002:300: gzhan nas btsal kyang mi rnyed de //
NK072(nu)002:301: rang rig sgrib med dag pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:306: khyod la'ang dbye na gsum du yod de /
NK072(nu)002:307: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bur nges pa gsum du yod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:308: dang po gzhir nges pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:310: gzhi'i rgyud rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po de chos
NK072(nu)002:311: nyid sgro skur dang bral bar bden pas na de
NK072(nu)002:312: ltar du brjod pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:314: sgro dang bskur ba zhi ba yi //
NK072(nu)002:315: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK072(nu)002:316: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyungs //
NK072(nu)002:318: gnyis pa lam du nges pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:320: theg pa 'di'i lugs kyi ye nas gnas pa'i 'bras
NK072(nu)002:321: bu nyid shes thob kyi byed pas lam du byed
NK072(nu)002:324: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:325: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:327: gsum pa 'bras bur nges pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:329: rgyud 'di rang gi ngo bos brjod bya rgyal ba'i
NK072(nu)002:330: dgongs pa nges don mngon du phyungs nas ston pas
NK072(nu)002:331: na de ltar du brjod pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:333: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK072(nu)002:334: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK072(nu)002:335: zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:337: mtshan rgyud don yin min la rtsod pa /
NK072(nu)002:338: mtshan du rgyud don 'dus ma 'dus la rtsod pa /
NK072(nu)002:339: man ngag kho na'i mtshan nas smos par rtsod pa /
NK072(nu)002:340: rgya skad mi smos par bod skad smos par rtsod pa dang bzhi las /
NK072(nu)002:342: mtshan rgyud don yin nam ma yin na gleng gzhi gleng bslangs dgos med du thal ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:344: rgyud 'di'i ched du bya ba'i gdul bya dbang po yang rab des mtshan mthong ba'am /
NK072(nu)002:345: thos pas rgyud don mi rtogs par thal lo zer /
NK072(nu)002:348: gleng gzhi gleng bslang mi dgos pa'i skyon med de /
NK072(nu)002:349: sngon 'byung 'og min du gleng gzhi tshogs te gleng bslang nas rgyud don gsung pa /
NK072(nu)002:350: mi yul du gsang bdag gis tshig dang yi ger 'god pa'i tshe /
NK072(nu)002:351: blo rab 'bring tha gsum la dgongs nas mtshan klad
NK072(nu)002:352: du smos pa'i phyir zhes snga rabs pa dag gis
NK072(nu)002:353: lan de ltar gsung yang mi 'thad de /
NK072(nu)002:355: khyod rgyud don ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:356: khyod de rtogs byed kyi thabs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:358: ston pas 'og min du rgyud 'di brjod byed tshig tu ma gsungs par thal /
NK072(nu)002:359: dam bca' de 'thad pa'i phyir zer na /
NK072(nu)002:360: dgongs pa brda'i bshad pa nyid gsang bdag gis tshig tu bsdus pa'i tshe /
NK072(nu)002:361: rang nyid ston pa dang dgongs pa mnyam par khas blangs nas /
NK072(nu)002:363: zhes bsdus par bzhed pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:365: da ni sdud pa pos bcom ldan 'das kyi lung
NK072(nu)002:366: dang mthun pa ltar rgyud kyi gleng gzhi mdzad pa
NK072(nu)002:367: bla'am man ngag gis bshad par bya ste /
NK072(nu)002:369: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:371: mtshan du rgyud don 'dus sam ma 'dus /
NK072(nu)002:372: 'dus na mtshan dang rgyud kyi dngos po bcu brang sprad la sbyor rigs par thal /
NK072(nu)002:373: ma 'dus na dbang rab kyis mtshan la brten nas rgyud don mi rtogs par thal ba'i phyir zer /
NK072(nu)002:375: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu dang mtshan don so sor
NK072(nu)002:376: sbyor du med kyang mtshan don gzhi lam 'bras gsum
NK072(nu)002:377: du gnas pas / der rgyud don mtha' dag 'dus pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:378: mtshan mthong bas rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don rtogs par
NK072(nu)002:379: gsungs pa de sngon byung 'khor gyis rtogs tshul yin
NK072(nu)002:380: te / don mthong ba la brten nas mtshan du brtags pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:381: gsang bdag gis rang gi rgyud don thugs su chud
NK072(nu)002:382: nas 'khor la 'chad pa'i tshe gsang ba snying po
NK072(nu)002:383: zhes don mthong ba la brten nas mtshan btags pa'i
NK072(nu)002:384: phyir / sngon byung ngor mtshan du tshig don mtha' dag ma lus pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:385: skad cig tsam la rtogs pa'ang mi 'gal te /
NK072(nu)002:387: sgrib pa mtha' spong gdul bya la //
NK072(nu)002:388: skad cig tsam gyis snang bar mdzad //
NK072(nu)002:390: rjes 'jug tu mtshan la brten nas don go ba ni /
NK072(nu)002:391: der gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi brda 'phrad pa tsam du go ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:392: ming gis don mtshon par nus pa tsam gyis ming yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:393: dper na bum pa zhes brjod pas /
NK072(nu)002:394: lto ldir zhabs zhum chu skyor kyi don byed nus pa'i dngos po tsam go yang /
NK072(nu)002:395: gser bum sogs khyad chos rnams go bas ma khyab pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:396: gsum pa ni thugs thig las /
NK072(nu)002:397: dang por mtshon pa mtshan gsum ldan //
NK072(nu)002:400: rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK072(nu)002:401: zhes pas rgyud 'di las rgyud lung man ngag gi mtshon gsum du grags pa las /
NK072(nu)002:402: glegs bam gyi klad du rgyud dang lung gi mtshan nas mi smos par /
NK072(nu)002:403: man ngag kho na'i mtshan nas smos pa la rgyu mtshan med de zer /
NK072(nu)002:405: ma h+aa yo ga la'ang nang gses kyi rgyud lung man ngag gsum mam /
NK072(nu)002:406: pha ma gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum du gnas pa la /
NK072(nu)002:407: rgyud 'di ni ma h+aa'i a ti thabs shes gnyis
NK072(nu)002:408: med du ston pa'i rgyud yin pa'i gnad kyis man
NK072(nu)002:409: ngag gi mtshan nas smos pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:411: rgyud 'di rgya gar nas bsgyur ba ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:412: klad du rgya skad ma smos pa'i phyir zer /
NK072(nu)002:415: rang lan gdab pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:417: kha cig na re rgya skad gtan med na bod du bsgyur ba mi rigs pas /
NK072(nu)002:418: bod skad du zhes pas rgya skad du yod par shugs kyis brda' 'jal bar bya'o //
NK072(nu)002:420: bod kyi skad la rgya nag la sogs pa'i skad sbyar du rung bas /
NK072(nu)002:422: bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos rnams la'ang rgya skad
NK072(nu)002:423: shugs la sbyar du rung ba'i phyir rgya gar mar
NK072(nu)002:424: thal ba sogs kyi skyon gnas so //
NK072(nu)002:425: gnyis pa rang lan gdab pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:426: 'dir rgya skad med pas bod mar 'gyur ba'i khyab pa med de /
NK072(nu)002:427: bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos du mar yang klad du rgya skad bkod pa yod mod /
NK072(nu)002:428: des rgya gar mar mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:430: klad du rgya gar gyi skad gcig po ma smos pas bod mar 'gyur ram /
NK072(nu)002:431: skad gnyis ka ma smos pas bod mar 'gyur /
NK072(nu)002:433: rgya nag nas bsgyur ba'i chos de rnams chos can /
NK072(nu)002:435: klad du de ma smos pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:436: gnyis pa ltar rgya gar gyi dpe de rnams chos can /
NK072(nu)002:438: klad du de gnyis ka ma smos pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:439: gzhan yang rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid chos can /
NK072(nu)002:440: khyod bod mar thal ba'i skyon dang /
NK072(nu)002:442: khyod yongs su grags pa'i rgya gar gyi pan chen rnams kyis mang du bkral ba gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:443: gsang 'dus kyi 'grel ba bi shwa mi tras mdzad
NK072(nu)002:444: par yang rgyud 'di'i lung mang du drangs pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:445: dang / dus phyis kyang rgya dpe rnyed pa las /
NK072(nu)002:446: thar lo nyi ma rgyal mtshan dang /
NK072(nu)002:447: 'gos lo gzhon nu dpal ba sogs thub bstan yongs
NK072(nu)002:448: su rdzogs pa'i lo ts+aa ba chen po dag gis
NK072(nu)002:450: mtshan de ldan gyi rgyud don bshad pa la /
NK072(nu)002:451: ston pa la dbang mi za ba'i phyir klad don phyag dang /
NK072(nu)002:452: bka'i don bde blag tu rtogs par bya ba'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:453: gzhung don gtan la phab pa gnyis yod pa las
NK072(nu)002:455: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK072(nu)002:462: byed pa'i mu bzhi dang sbyar na phyag gang gis btsal na /
NK072(nu)002:463: sdud pa po gsang bdag gis /
NK072(nu)002:465: rgyud kyi ston pa bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la /
NK072(nu)002:466: dus gang gi tshe na sdud pa pos 'og min du dang por shes rgyud la btus te /
NK072(nu)002:467: de nas mi yul du tshig tu bsdud pa'i tshe na'o //
NK072(nu)002:468: tshul ji ltar btsal na rab lta ba 'jal ba /
NK072(nu)002:470: tha ma mos gus gyi phyag gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:471: 'di ni sdud pa po'i phyag yin pa'i phyir dang po'o //
NK072(nu)002:472: gnyis pa tshig gi don de rgyas par 'chad na /
NK072(nu)002:475: mnyam nyid dbyings su bdud bzhi ngang gis bcom //
NK072(nu)002:476: phyag rgya'i rang bzhin tshogs gnyis rdzogs par ldan //
NK072(nu)002:477: yod med mtha' 'das bdag gzhan yongs kyi dpal //
NK072(nu)002:478: thams cad rang bzhin rtogs dang thugs rje bzang //
NK072(nu)002:479: kun bzang lha yi lha khyod dbyer med la //
NK072(nu)002:480: rtogs dang gus pas rab tu phyag 'tshal lo //
NK072(nu)002:481: zhes gsungs pa'i don sbyor ba dag don tu dril na /
NK072(nu)002:482: ston pa kun tu bzang po chos can /
NK072(nu)002:483: khyod kyi mtshan la bcom zhes pa de chos nyid
NK072(nu)002:484: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su bdud bzhi ngang gis
NK072(nu)002:485: dag pas na bdud bzhi bcom pa'i mtshan yin te
NK072(nu)002:486: / rgyu nyon mongs pa'i mtshan ma rang sar grol
NK072(nu)002:487: bas 'bras bu nyer len gyi phung po mi len
NK072(nu)002:488: / zhing / de ma blangs na skye shi dang
NK072(nu)002:489: lha bu'i bdud kyi bar du gcod pas mi tshugs
NK072(nu)002:490: / zhing / pa'i phyir / de ltar yang /
NK072(nu)002:492: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /
NK072(nu)002:493: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK072(nu)002:494: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor te //
NK072(nu)002:495: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung gnas //
NK072(nu)002:498: khyod kyi mtshan la ldan zhes smos pa de yon tan gyis mtshan yin te /
NK072(nu)002:499: spyir b+ha ga wan gyi sgra las b+ha ga ni bcom pa la 'jug par ma zad /
NK072(nu)002:500: rnam pa gcig tu na skal ba'am legs pa rnam
NK072(nu)002:501: pa drug la 'jug par yang bshad pa'i phyir te
NK072(nu)002:503: dbang phyug dang ni gzugs bzang dang //
NK072(nu)002:504: dpal dang grags dang ye shes dang //
NK072(nu)002:505: brtson 'grus phun sum tshogs ldan pa //
NK072(nu)002:506: drug pa de la skal zhes bya //
NK072(nu)002:509: skabs 'di ni tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan dang ldan pa'i mtshan yin /
NK072(nu)002:510: chos sku'i phyag rgya ye shes kyi tshogs dang /
NK072(nu)002:511: gzugs sku'i phyag rgya bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs pas
NK072(nu)002:512: sku lnga la sogs pa'i yon tan rang rig pa'i
NK072(nu)002:513: ye shes la rang bzhin gyis ldan pa'i phyir te
NK072(nu)002:515: sku lnga la sogs yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK072(nu)002:517: 'o na 'das zhes pa'i don de gang zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:519: 'jig rten pa'i b+ha ga w+aan las khyad par /
NK072(nu)002:520: 'das zhes bla thabs su bsnan te /
NK072(nu)002:522: b+ha ga'i sgra srid pa dang 'jigs par 'gro ba la 'jug te /
NK072(nu)002:523: de las 'das pa na b+ha ga w+aan no //
NK072(nu)002:524: 'dir ni 'das pa zhes pa'i mtshan de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:526: chos sku skye ba med pas yod pa'i mtha' dang /
NK072(nu)002:527: gzugs sku 'gag pa med pas med pa'i mtha' ste /
NK072(nu)002:528: spros pa'i mtshan ma kun las 'das pa'i don yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:531: spros pa kun las rab 'das pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:532: bcom ldan 'das ni mkha' rab zhi //
NK072(nu)002:535: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK072(nu)002:538: khyod la dpal zhes brjod pa de che ba'i mtshan nyid yin te /
NK072(nu)002:539: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dpal gzhi chos dbyings shin tu dri med de nyid mngon du gyur pas /
NK072(nu)002:540: 'bras chos sku rtogs pa bdag gi dpal dang /
NK072(nu)002:541: gzugs sku thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal mnga' ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:542: de ltar yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK072(nu)002:543: rang bzhin mngon byas ma lus re ba skong //
NK072(nu)002:545: ston pa rigs drug pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:546: khyod la kun tu bzang po zhes brjod pa de rang gi ngo bo'i mtshan yin te /
NK072(nu)002:547: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad 'ching grol med pa'i
NK072(nu)002:548: rang bzhin mngon du rtogs pas spyod yul yongs su
NK072(nu)002:551: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK072(nu)002:552: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK072(nu)002:555: khyod kun tu bzang po yin te /
NK072(nu)002:556: gnas lugs ye sangs rgyas pa ni rang bzhin kun tu bzang po /
NK072(nu)002:557: de nyid rtogs pa'i yon tan mngon du gyur pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:558: rtogs pa kun tu bzang po /
NK072(nu)002:559: de las gzugs kyi sku mngon du snang ba'i thugs rje kun tu bzang po yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:561: kun tu bzang po yin te /
NK072(nu)002:562: 'gro ba la phyogs dus kun tu gnas skabs dang
NK072(nu)002:563: mthar thug gi phan bde bzang po ster bar mdzad
NK072(nu)002:564: pa po yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:566: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad du //
NK072(nu)002:567: mngon mtho nges legs rab ster ba //
NK072(nu)002:568: kun tu bzang por brjod pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:570: la zhes pa ni phyag bya ba'i yul mtshon par byed pa'i rnam dbye ste /
NK072(nu)002:571: sdud pa po gsang bdag gis rang dang ston pa'i
NK072(nu)002:572: thugs gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i sgo nas phyag
NK072(nu)002:574: de ltar yang 'grel pa mngon rtogs las /
NK072(nu)002:575: de yang thun mong pa dag lus ngag yid gsum
NK072(nu)002:576: gyis so sor bltas nas phyag 'tshal ba ni shin
NK072(nu)002:577: tu 'gal te / tshe tshad par 'gyur ro //
NK072(nu)002:578: rmad du byung ba'i theg pa 'dir kun tu bzang
NK072(nu)002:579: po dang rig pa gnyis med du 'jal ba phyag
NK072(nu)002:580: tu gsungs te / dpe mar gyi nang du mar blug pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:583: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag dang //
NK072(nu)002:584: ji ltar mar la mar bzhag bzhin //
NK072(nu)002:585: rang gis rang gi ye shes gang //
NK072(nu)002:588: gsum pa rtsod pa spangs pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:593: klad du smos pa'i phyag 'di lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur phyag yin gyi /
NK072(nu)002:594: sdud pa po'i phyag ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:597: zhes pa man chad yin pa'i phyir zer /
NK072(nu)002:598: gnyis pa de spang ba ni /
NK072(nu)002:599: 'o na sdud pa pos bka' bsdu byed pa'i thog
NK072(nu)002:600: mar rang gi ston pa la bstod phyag byas pa
NK072(nu)002:601: med par thal / dam bca' de 'thad pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:604: so thar gyi mdo'i bka' bsdu ba'i tshe ston pa
NK072(nu)002:605: la bstod phyag byas nas bka' bsdus pa'i phyir te
NK072(nu)002:606: / de las 'gro ba'i gtso la spyi bos phyag 'tshal nas //
NK072(nu)002:607: thams cad mkhyen pa'i bslab gzhi dkon mchog snod //
NK072(nu)002:608: 'phags pa'i tshogs kyi dbus su dbye bar bya //
NK072(nu)002:609: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir byas pa las /
NK072(nu)002:611: 'o na rgyud 'di la lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur phyag med par thal /
NK072(nu)002:612: klad du bkod pa'i phyag 'di ni sdud pa po'i phyag yin la /
NK072(nu)002:613: de las gzhan pa'i 'gyur phyag med pa'i phyir zer /
NK072(nu)002:615: lo ts+aa bas rgyal po'i bka' bcad dang bstun na'ang /
NK072(nu)002:616: ston pa kun bzang la phyag 'tshal bar rigs //
NK072(nu)002:617: rang gi 'dod pa'i lha la 'tshal na'ang ston pa
NK072(nu)002:618: kun bzang la phyag bya bar rigs par mthong nas
NK072(nu)002:619: / 'gyur phyag zur du ma bkod pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:620: dus 'khor bsdus rgyud kyi klad du'ang yi ge pa'i
NK072(nu)002:621: phyag gis go bcad de 'gyur phyag ma bkod pa
NK072(nu)002:622: bzhin no // gnyis pa gzhung don gtan la dbab pa la /
NK072(nu)002:624: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK072(nu)002:625: mthun par gsang bsgrag gzhan du min //
NK072(nu)002:626: zhes gsungs pa ltar gyi rgyud 'di nyid kyi ched
NK072(nu)002:627: du bya ba'i gdul bya dbang po rab 'bring tha
NK072(nu)002:628: gsum la ltos nas 'chad tshul gsum ste /
NK072(nu)002:630: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK072(nu)002:633: de las 'dir bar ma'i dbang du byas na /
NK072(nu)002:634: gzhung tshogs le'u nyer gnyis kyang chos lngar 'du ste /
NK072(nu)002:636: spros pa la dga' ba dbang po 'bring gi don
NK072(nu)002:637: du rgyud kyi don rnam par phye bas lnga ste
NK072(nu)002:639: de la lnga po de gang yin zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:641: rgyud gzhung gzhi bslang yongs su shes //
NK072(nu)002:646: bco lnga pa rnams kyis rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:647: le'u gnyis pas rkyen gleng bslang ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:648: le'u gsum pa'i smad nas nyer gcig pa yan gyis 'bras bus yongs shes rgyud don dang /
NK072(nu)002:649: de dag la khyab byed du rgyud kyi dgos 'brel dang /
NK072(nu)002:650: le'u tha mas 'khor la gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa dang lnga las /
NK072(nu)002:652: gleng gzhi bstan pa'i dgos ched /
NK072(nu)002:655: ji snyed bstan pa'i rnam grangs dang bzhi las /
NK072(nu)002:657: gleng gzhi tshogs pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:658: dgos pa gnyis su nges te /
NK072(nu)002:659: khyod kyis rgyud don 'byung ba'i rgyu byed pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:660: de'i lo rgyus la brten nas ma 'ongs pa'i gdul
NK072(nu)002:661: bya rnams yid ches shing rgyud la 'jug par 'gyur
NK072(nu)002:663: gnyis pa ni ston pa la sogs pa phun sum
NK072(nu)002:664: tshogs pa lnga'i bdag nyid rgyud don 'byung ba dang
NK072(nu)002:665: yid ches kyi nges par ster ba'i rigs gnas /
NK072(nu)002:667: gang gleng na bstan pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:668: de'i rgyu'am gzhi ni phun sum tshogs pa lnga po de yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:670: d+aa na zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK072(nu)002:671: nges pa sbyin pa zhes bya ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:672: bka' ma yin par rtog pa'i the tshom can gyi
NK072(nu)002:673: blo la yid ches kyi nges pa sbyin byed yin
NK072(nu)002:674: pa'i phyir / bzhi pa ji snyed bstan pa'i rnam grangs de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:675: khyod la rnam pa gnyis su nges te /
NK072(nu)002:676: thun mong ma yin pa'i dang /
NK072(nu)002:677: thun mong gi gleng gzhi gnyis su nges pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:678: de la thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK072(nu)002:679: bshad rgyud rgya mtsho dang bshad rgyud thal ba gnyis kyis ston cing /
NK072(nu)002:680: 'dir thun mong gi gleng gzhi de la /
NK072(nu)002:681: rgyud 'byung ba khyad par gyi gleng gzhi /
NK072(nu)002:682: zhar byung gdul bya dgos byed du ston pa khro bo'i gleng gzhi /
NK072(nu)002:683: sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba'i gleng gzhi dang gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:685: 'di nyid kyi le'u dang pos ston te /
NK072(nu)002:687: dang po chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:688: 'di skad bshad pa zhes pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:689: de yang sbyor ngag tu ston na /
NK072(nu)002:690: 'di skad bshad pa zhes pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:691: khyod rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad mtshon pa'i tshig 'phrad yin te /
NK072(nu)002:692: gsang bdag rang nyid ston par khas blangs nas ngas
NK072(nu)002:693: sngar 'og min du bshad pa nyid yang 'dir bshad
NK072(nu)002:694: par bya'o zhes pa'i ngag tshig yin te /
NK072(nu)002:696: nga ni che ba'i rgyal po ste /
NK072(nu)002:697: 'chad dang nyan pa'ang nga nyid yin /
NK072(nu)002:699: gnyis pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:702: dus na zhes pa'i dus de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:703: khyod dus re 'ga' ba las 'das pa'i thun mong ma yin pa'i dus yin te /
NK072(nu)002:704: longs sku rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lo chos gsung ba'i dus yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:705: 'di dag la rtsod pa spang ba las /
NK072(nu)002:711: 'di skad bdag gi thos pa dus gcig na //
NK072(nu)002:713: 'dir de ltar ma smos pa'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:714: gleng gzhi log pas bka' yang dag pa ma yin no zer /
NK072(nu)002:716: gzhan lan la dpyad pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:717: rang lan gdab pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:719: lha rje glan shaka bzang na re /
NK072(nu)002:720: bshad thos gnyis tshig mi mthun kyang ston pas 'khor la bshad pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:721: 'khor gyis ston pa las thos pa don mthun gsung /
NK072(nu)002:722: de ltar na thos pa la bshad pas khyab ces pa'i skyon gnas so //
NK072(nu)002:724: rje sgro phug pa na re /
NK072(nu)002:725: sku gnyis kyi bstan pa'i khyad par yin te /
NK072(nu)002:726: longs sku tshig tu mi gsungs pas rna bas thos su med pa'i phyir bshad ces dang /
NK072(nu)002:727: sprul sku tshig tu gsung ba'i phyir thos bya bar 'ong ba yin zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK072(nu)002:728: longs skus gsungs pa'i rgyud yin na /
NK072(nu)002:729: bshad ces 'byung bas ma khyab pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:730: gnyis pa rang lan gdab pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:731: gsang bdag gi bsdu ba byed pa na rang nyid ston pa nyid du khas blangs te /
NK072(nu)002:732: sngar ngas 'og min du bshad pa nyid /
NK072(nu)002:735: nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel las bshad ces
NK072(nu)002:736: pas ni 'khor ston pa gnyis su med par bstan
NK072(nu)002:737: pa yin la / zhes sogs dang /
NK072(nu)002:739: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi ste /
NK072(nu)002:740: rgyud gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:742: gsum pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:743: dang po ston pa'i rang bzhin ni /
NK072(nu)002:744: de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag pa sogs nas dbyer med pa zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan /
NK072(nu)002:745: ston pa kun tu bzang po chos can /
NK072(nu)002:746: khyod la de bzhin gshegs pa zhes brjod pa de
NK072(nu)002:747: de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i rang bzhin mnga'
NK072(nu)002:748: ba yin te / khyod chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK072(nu)002:749: kyi don sgrib byed kyi zhen pa dang bral bas
NK072(nu)002:750: ba yin te / nar son zhing / de'i ngo
NK072(nu)002:751: bo mngon du gyur pas na gshegs pa zhes brjod
NK072(nu)002:752: ba yin te / nar son zhing / pa'i phyir te / rdo rje las /
NK072(nu)002:753: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa yang //
NK072(nu)002:754: sna tshogs zhen las grol bar bshad //
NK072(nu)002:757: gang phyir de bzhin nyid du gshegs //
NK072(nu)002:758: de bzhin gshegs par mngon par brjod //
NK072(nu)002:761: khyod la yon tan ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub
NK072(nu)002:762: pa'i yon tan mnga' bas yang dag par rdzogs pa
NK072(nu)002:764: khyod kyi rang byung gi ye shes la spang bya ma grub pas ma nor /
NK072(nu)002:766: mi bslu bas yang dag pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:767: thams cad 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su rang
NK072(nu)002:768: snang bas spang thob med par ye rdzogs su gnas
NK072(nu)002:769: pas de ltar du brjod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:771: khyod la ye shes mtha' dbus med par brdal ba'i
NK072(nu)002:772: rang bzhin mnga' bas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa yin
NK072(nu)002:773: te / mi mthun pa dang gnyen po dbyer med
NK072(nu)002:774: pa'i yon tan mthar thug pas na de ltar du
NK072(nu)002:777: ma rig pa nyid ye shes gsal //
NK072(nu)002:778: nyon mongs sdug bsngal byang chub mchog /
NK072(nu)002:781: rang gi ngo bo gtan du med pa'i rang bzhin
NK072(nu)002:782: mnga' bas bcom ldan 'das zhes brjod pa yin te
NK072(nu)002:783: / bdud bzhi bcom zhing che ba'i yon tan gyi 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:785: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdongs kyis bcoms //
NK072(nu)002:786: sku lnga la sogs yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK072(nu)002:787: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK072(nu)002:790: khyod kyis mnyam pa nyid kyi don mngon du mdzad
NK072(nu)002:791: kyang spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin mnga' bas
NK072(nu)002:792: longs spyod chen po zhes brjod pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:793: khyod 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la spyad bya
NK072(nu)002:794: spyod byed du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dang bral ba'i
NK072(nu)002:795: sgo nas longs spyod pas gzhan las chos mchog tu
NK072(nu)002:796: gyur pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:797: de ltar yang 'chi med mdzod las /
NK072(nu)002:798: chen po mchog dang tshad med dang //
NK072(nu)002:799: mkhas mtshon spro ba'i las 'di nyid //
NK072(nu)002:800: shin tu rmad byung byed pa ni //
NK072(nu)002:801: chen po zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:804: khyod la de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag nyid
NK072(nu)002:805: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i rang bzhin gyi
NK072(nu)002:806: mtshan sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid zhes brjod
NK072(nu)002:808: khyod phyogs dus bde gshegs thams cad kyi rten byed pa'i ngos nas sku lnga /
NK072(nu)002:809: brda' sprod pa'i ngos nas gsung lnga /
NK072(nu)002:811: dgos 'dod byung ba'i yon tan lnga /
NK072(nu)002:812: gzhan don mdzad pa'i ngos nas phrin las lnga ste /
NK072(nu)002:813: 'bras chos nyer lnga po de dag gcig dang du ma bral zhing /
NK072(nu)002:814: rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK072(nu)002:816: ngo bo 'dus ma byas pa rdo rje'i bdag nyid du ro gcig pas de ltar brjod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:818: khyod khams gsum dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'khor
NK072(nu)002:819: ba'i chos thams cad dang so so ma yin tha
NK072(nu)002:820: mi dad pa'i rang bzhin can yin te /
NK072(nu)002:821: khyod dang de lta bu'i 'khor ba'i chos gnyis ka'ang /
NK072(nu)002:822: kun rdzob tu rig pa sgyu ma lta bu yin pas so so ma yin /
NK072(nu)002:823: don dam par sems nyid du ma skyes pas tha mi dad /
NK072(nu)002:824: bden pa gnyis ka'i tha snyad las kyang 'das pas na /
NK072(nu)002:825: dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin can yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:826: gnyis pa ston pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK072(nu)002:828: rgyab med pa thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal zhing sogs nas /
NK072(nu)002:829: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbu gsum dang /
NK072(nu)002:832: khyod chos sku'i bdag nyid du gnas pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:833: khyed bde gshegs rang snang la sku mdun dang /
NK072(nu)002:834: rgyab ma grub cing gdul bya'i snang ba la ris
NK072(nu)002:835: med par thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal
NK072(nu)002:836: bas gzugs sku'i yon tan mi 'gag pa'i phyir te
NK072(nu)002:838: kun tu bzang po'i zhal ni phyogs bcur gsal //
NK072(nu)002:839: kun gzigs kun bzang sku la mdun rgyab med //
NK072(nu)002:840: phyogs bcu gang bar spyan gyis rnam par gzigs //
NK072(nu)002:843: longs sku'i bdag nyid du'ang gnas pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:844: thun mong dang khyad par gyi mtshan gyi me tog
NK072(nu)002:845: la dpe byad kyi 'bras bu spras pa'i bdag nyid
NK072(nu)002:848: sprul sku'i bdag nyid du gnas pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:849: khyod kyi mdzad pa'i snang tshul ni /
NK072(nu)002:850: rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab cing tshad med par snang ba'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:851: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las zhi
NK072(nu)002:852: ba'i blo gros nam mkha' ji tsam khyab pa de
NK072(nu)002:853: tsam du de bzhin gshegs pa'i skus khyab bo //
NK072(nu)002:856: khyod la thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs kyi bzhugs tshul bshad du yod do //
NK072(nu)002:857: thabs snying rje chen po dang /
NK072(nu)002:858: shes rab stong pa nyid kyi brdar zhabs gnyis yab
NK072(nu)002:859: yum gnyis ka bzhengs pa lta bu ma yin par
NK072(nu)002:860: yab rdo rje'i skyil dkrung dang /
NK072(nu)002:861: yum pad+ma'i skyil krung du bcings nas bzhugs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:863: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga chos can /
NK072(nu)002:864: khyod rnams kyi bzhugs tshul yod de /
NK072(nu)002:865: yab rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil krung dang /
NK072(nu)002:866: yum rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil krung gis g.yon phyogs
NK072(nu)002:867: nas 'khyud pa'i tshul du bzhugs pa yin pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:869: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i don rtags bshad du yod de ye shes lnga /
NK072(nu)002:870: rang byung gi ye shes dang drug /
NK072(nu)002:871: des 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags su phyag mtshan drug 'dzin pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:872: sgyu 'phrul rol pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK072(nu)002:873: ye shes drug gi bdag nyid kyi //
NK072(nu)002:874: phyag rgya rin chen 'bar ba'i mtshan //
NK072(nu)002:875: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK072(nu)002:877: zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:879: khyod la rnam par gsum mnga' ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:880: de gsum gyi mtshan mar dbu dkar dmar mthing gsum gyi kha dog tu bstan pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:881: bzhi pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK072(nu)002:885: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na /
NK072(nu)002:888: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la sogs nas /
NK072(nu)002:889: gos pa med pa pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la zhes pa'i bar gyi ston pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:892: sgra don gtan la dbab pa dang gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:894: don dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa las /
NK072(nu)002:895: de'i rtags snang gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang snang ba'i rigs gnas te /
NK072(nu)002:897: gnas kyi rang bzhin de bzhin nyid //
NK072(nu)002:898: ngo bo 'og min gzhal yas khang //
NK072(nu)002:901: a ka nish+tha zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK072(nu)002:903: don gdul bya'i blo las 'das shing /
NK072(nu)002:904: rtags de 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min las nyis 'gyur gyis spang ba'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:907: nyams 'gyur shin tu spang ba na //
NK072(nu)002:909: gsum pa gtan la dbab pa la /
NK072(nu)002:910: gnas de'i rang bzhin chos can /
NK072(nu)002:911: khyod mtha' dbus la sogs pa'i spros pa thams cad las 'das pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:912: khyod chos kyi dbyings yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:914: mtha' dbus med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK072(nu)002:915: de ni gnas kyi bla mar 'dod //
NK072(nu)002:917: gnas kyi ngo bo de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:918: khyod dbyings dang ye shes dbyer mi phyed pa'i rtags
NK072(nu)002:919: su gzhal yas khang gi yon tan gyi rnam par
NK072(nu)002:921: gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya la sogs pa'i don bcu gcig gi rnal 'byor rang snang ba'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:923: gzhal yas gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya //
NK072(nu)002:924: dbyibs dang glo bur rtse mo dang //
NK072(nu)002:925: rgyan dang sgo 'khyud rta bab dang //
NK072(nu)002:926: mtshan nyid gdan gyi rnam pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:929: khyod ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i rtags su 'khor lo'i rnam par snang ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:930: khyod rgya khyon tshad med pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK072(nu)002:931: lte ba dang bcas pa'i rnam par snang ba'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:932: / de'i nang gi 'og gzhi chos can /
NK072(nu)002:933: khyod la dpags pa zhes brjod pa'i rgyu mtshan yod dam /
NK072(nu)002:934: sgo dang 'khyams sogs nas lte ba'i bar rim pa
NK072(nu)002:935: ltar rdo rje 'greng bu res dpags pa de theg
NK072(nu)002:936: pa 'og ma nas 'dir 'phar ba'i don yin pa'i
NK072(nu)002:937: phyir / gzhal yas khang de'i rgyu chos can /
NK072(nu)002:938: khyod rin po che las grub pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:939: ye shes nyidarina po che'i dbyibs dang kha dog tu
NK072(nu)002:940: rang snang bas re ba skong ba yin pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:942: khyod phyogs bcu kun tu yongs su ma chad par snang ste /
NK072(nu)002:943: khyod chos dbyings mtha' klas par khyab pa rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:945: khyod gru bzhi pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:946: khyod de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan gyis khyab pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:948: rgyas pa'i don yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:950: mnyam pa'i phyir dang khyab pa'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:951: rgyas pa'i phyir ni gru bzhir brjod //
NK072(nu)002:954: khyod gru chad las phyir 'phyang ba'i dbyibs mkhar gyi 'bur thabs lta bu snang ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:955: khyod ye shes re re'ang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi
NK072(nu)002:956: bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su kha dog rigs bzhi'i
NK072(nu)002:957: mdog can gyi rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes
NK072(nu)002:959: de'i rtse mo'i tshad dbyibs chos can /
NK072(nu)002:960: tshad dpag tu med pa dang dbyibs bum pa zlum
NK072(nu)002:961: po'i rnam par 'khyil ba'i rang bzhin du snang ste
NK072(nu)002:962: / khyod chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes la mthar
NK072(nu)002:963: thug pa med cing spros pa dang bral ba'i rtags
NK072(nu)002:964: su snang ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:968: rin po che'i rgyan de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:969: khyod kyi khyad chos bshad du yod de /
NK072(nu)002:970: khyod gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal ma
NK072(nu)002:971: 'gags par rang snang ba'i rtags su pany+tsa re kha'i
NK072(nu)002:972: rtsig pa'i steng du rin po che'i pha gu dang
NK072(nu)002:976: mda' yab la sogs pa'i rgyan khyad par du 'phags pa du mas spras par snang ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:978: khyod 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs rnam dag
NK072(nu)002:979: rgyan du rdzogs pa'i rtags su rang snang ba yin
NK072(nu)002:980: te / khyod gzugs rdo rje ma la sogs pa'i
NK072(nu)002:981: lha mos phyogs kun tu 'khrigs par rang snang ba'i
NK072(nu)002:982: te / phyir / steng rgyan chos can /
NK072(nu)002:984: dbus bum pa zlum po'i steng du bre mtshon pa'i 'phyur po'i rtser /
NK072(nu)002:985: pad+ma la gnas pa'i 'khor lo rim pa bcu gsum gyi steng na rat+na'i gdugs kyis spras pa'i steng /
NK072(nu)002:986: rdo rje rin po che'i tog gis mdzes par snang ba de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:987: gzhan yas khang der 'jug pa'i sgo chos can /
NK072(nu)002:988: khyod bshad du yod de rnam par bzhi'i ting nge
NK072(nu)002:989: 'dzin gyi sgo nas byang chub chen por lhun gyis
NK072(nu)002:990: 'jug byed phyogs kyi dbye bas sgo bzhir snang ba
NK072(nu)002:992: gzhal yas khang de'i rta bab chos can /
NK072(nu)002:993: khyod kyi grangs nges bshad du yod de /
NK072(nu)002:995: 'bras bu'i rta bab brgyad de bcu drug tu grangs nges pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:998: thun mong gi rnam thar brgyad kyi yon tan gyi
NK072(nu)002:999: rtags su sgo phubs phyi nang gnyis su them skas
NK072(nu)002:1000: bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1003: theg pa brgyad kyi grub mtha'i yon tan brgyad rdzogs
NK072(nu)002:1004: pa'i rtags su sgo logs kyi phyir zur bzhi nas
NK072(nu)002:1005: ka bas btegs pa'i steng du rgyan gyi rta babs
NK072(nu)002:1006: brgyad dang ldan pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1007: gzhal yas khang de'i mtshan nyid chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1008: khyod la phyi dang nang med par kun tu nang
NK072(nu)002:1009: du gyur pa zhes brjod pa'i rgyu mtshan yod de
NK072(nu)002:1010: / khyod chos kyi dbyings rdo rje kun tu bzang mo'i b+ha ga nyid du 'dus pas na /
NK072(nu)002:1011: tha snyad tsam du nang zhes brjod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1012: gzhal yas khang de'i gdan khri'i don de ji lta bu yin zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:1013: de la gsum yod pa'i dang po 'og gzhi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1015: khyod rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i phyag rgyas rtog tshogs
NK072(nu)002:1016: gcod pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun mi chad par
NK072(nu)002:1017: bskor ba'i rtags su rang shar ba de yin pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1018: phyir / gnyis pa sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1020: mi 'jigs pa bzhi sogs lhun gyis grub pa'i yon
NK072(nu)002:1021: tan gyi rtags su seng ge la sogs pa sems
NK072(nu)002:1022: can lnga po re re'ang brgyad brgyad kyi gdan khri
NK072(nu)002:1023: dang ldan pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1024: gsum pa yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1026: rgyal ba'i thugs rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal zhing thabs shes dbyer med pa'i rtags su nyi zla dang /
NK072(nu)002:1027: nyes skyon gyis ma gos pas pad+ma dang /
NK072(nu)002:1028: re ba skang zhing dkor bdun lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1029: rtags su rin po che'i khri rkang mdzod mig bdun
NK072(nu)002:1030: ldan rnams su shar ba de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1031: lnga pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK072(nu)002:1032: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor dang /
NK072(nu)002:1033: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1035: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i sogs te /
NK072(nu)002:1036: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po la sogs pa de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga po de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1037: khyod rnams kyi rigs dang ye shes kyi dbye ba bshad du yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1038: mi bskyod pa ni thugs rdo rje'i rigs dang chos dbyings ye shes /
NK072(nu)002:1039: rnam snang ni sku'i rigs dang me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK072(nu)002:1040: rin 'byung ni rin po che'i rigs dang mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK072(nu)002:1041: snang mtha' ni pad+ma'i rigs dang sor rtog ye shes /
NK072(nu)002:1042: don grub ni las kyi rigs dang bya grub ye shes rnams su nges pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1044: rigs kyi yum lnga de de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1045: khyod la btsun mo zhes brjod pa la rgyu mtshan yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1046: bskyed par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK072(nu)002:1047: spyad par bya ba'i yul gyur pas na de ltar du brjod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1049: khyod la dbye na bzhir yod pa de rnams la
NK072(nu)002:1050: mthong ba la sogs par smos pa ni rim pa
NK072(nu)002:1051: ltar mig rna ba sna lce'i rnam shes bzhi yin
NK072(nu)002:1052: pas rtog pa'i mtshan yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1053: khyod dbang po bzhi la brten nas yul gzugs mthong
NK072(nu)002:1054: ba la sogs pa dbang shes bzhir 'jog pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:1055: / mthong ba la sogs pa bzhi po chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1056: khyod lha'i dus na thugs kyi sems dpa' bzhi yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1060: myong ba spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug rnams su nges pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1061: de rnams la thugs kyi sems dpa' zhes brjod pa la chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1063: rtog pa'i dus su rnam shes kyi nang du 'dus pa gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:1064: lha'i dus su thugs rdo rje'i rigs su nges pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1066: ka ni spyan gyi sogs nang sems bzhi po'i yum chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1067: khyod rnams la mthong bar bya ba la sogs par
NK072(nu)002:1068: smos pa ni rim pa ltar yul gzugs sgra dri
NK072(nu)002:1069: ro bzhi yin pas rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK072(nu)002:1070: khyod rnams kyi mthong bya gzugs la sogs pa'i yul bzhi po de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1072: lha'i dus na sku'i sems ma bzhir grags te /
NK072(nu)002:1073: mthong bar bya ba l+aa s+ye ma /
NK072(nu)002:1074: gnyan par bya ba girti ma /
NK072(nu)002:1075: snom par bya ba m+aa le ma /
NK072(nu)002:1076: myong bar bya ba nirti ma rnams su nges pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1077: de rnams la sku'i sems ma zhes brjod pa la chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1079: yul bzhis rnam par shes pa bzhi'i rten byed pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1081: tsa ni spyan gyi sku yi mchog sogs /
NK072(nu)002:1083: khyod rnams la mthong byed la sogs par smos pa
NK072(nu)002:1084: ni rim pa ltar mig rna ba sna lce'i dbang
NK072(nu)002:1085: po bzhi yin pas rtog pa'i mtshan yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1086: khyed rtog pa'i dus kyi rnam shes bzhis yul bzhi
NK072(nu)002:1087: mthong ba'i bdag rkyen dbang po bzhi byed pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:1089: khyed rnams lha'i dus na gsung gi sems dpa' bzhir grags pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1090: khyed rnams rim bzhin mthong byed byams pa thos byed sgrib sel /
NK072(nu)002:1092: myong byed 'jam dpal dbyangs rnams su nges pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1093: de rnams la gsung gi sems dpa' zhes brjod pa la chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1095: dbang pos yul dang shes pa gnyis kyi phyi nang gi brda' sbyor byed pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1097: sa ni spyan gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK072(nu)002:1099: phyi sems bzhi'i yul chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1100: de dag la 'das pa la sogs par smos pa ni rtog pa'i mtshan yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1101: dus bzhis go phye nas dbang po bzhi bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1103: lha'i dus na dus bzhi'i lha mor grags pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1104: 'das pa'i dus bdug pa ma da ltar ba me tog ma /
NK072(nu)002:1105: 'byung ba ste ma 'ongs pa mar me ma /
NK072(nu)002:1106: ma byon pa ste 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus dri chab ma rnams su nges pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1108: ya na skye ba rnam par dag sogs /
NK072(nu)002:1109: dus bzhi po de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1111: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka spyad zin pa'i dus ni 'das pa /
NK072(nu)002:1112: rgyu spyad cing 'bras bu ma spyad pa ni da ltar ba /
NK072(nu)002:1113: rgyu 'bras tshogs la ma spyad pa ni ma 'ongs pa /
NK072(nu)002:1114: rgyu 'bras yod la tshogs pa ni 'das ma 'ongs
NK072(nu)002:1115: gang la'ang ma nges pa'i dus yin pa'i phyir te
NK072(nu)002:1116: / dper na dbyar gyi dus lta bu zhig gzhir bzhag nas rtsi na /
NK072(nu)002:1120: dgun ni ma nges pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:1121: dbyar gyi dus 'di las sngar 'das phyis 'byung gnyis ni 'das ma 'ongs par nges la /
NK072(nu)002:1122: dgun ni 'das ma 'ongs gang rung gcig tu kha tshon ma chod pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1123: dpyid kyi snga logs kyi dgun ni 'das pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1124: ston gyi phyi logs kyi dgun ni ma 'ongs pa ltar snang ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1127: rgyu 'bras nges pa ma tshogs pas //
NK072(nu)002:1128: 'byung bar ma nges dus zhes grags //
NK072(nu)002:1130: gnyis pa 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor bshad pa de la mtshan gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1132: 'jigs byed yab bzhi po chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1133: khyed rnams la 'joms pa chen po rdo rje zhes pa'i rgyu mtshan yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1134: phyi lus kyi chos bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK072(nu)002:1135: rtog pa'i rang bzhin mngon du gyur pa'i khro bo
NK072(nu)002:1136: bzhi'i sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pas bdud log 'dren
NK072(nu)002:1138: nang gsang ba'i khams bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK072(nu)002:1139: 'og sgo gsang ba'i khams gsum 'dus pa'i bde bas
NK072(nu)002:1140: rtog pa dang lha'am bde bar 'dzin pa'i zhen pa
NK072(nu)002:1141: gnyis ka 'joms pa la thogs pa med pas na
NK072(nu)002:1142: rdo rje zhes brjod pa gang zhig des 'joms pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1143: phrin las gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas na
NK072(nu)002:1144: chen po zhes brjod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1145: de dag gi yum bzhi chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1146: khyed rnams la btsun mo zhes brjod pa'i rgyu mtshan yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1147: de lta bu'i 'joms byed kyi gnyen po de yang
NK072(nu)002:1148: rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi ma yin pa'i chos nyid
NK072(nu)002:1149: yum gyis ngo bo des bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1150: dper na dkar po 'joms pa de dkar po ma
NK072(nu)002:1151: yin pa gzhan zhig gis bskyed pa bzhin yin pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1152: phyir / gnyis pa bye brag gi mtshan ni /
NK072(nu)002:1153: sgo ba bzhi po de rnams chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1154: khyod rnams la reg pa la sogs par smos pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:1156: phyi ltar lus kyi 'dus te reg pa'i tshor ba bskyed pa la /
NK072(nu)002:1157: reg byed lus dbang reg bya yul /
NK072(nu)002:1158: de gnyis 'dus pa'i reg shes rnams su yod pa de yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:1160: gsang ba'i yul dbang rnam shes gsum 'dus kyi reg pa bskyed pa la /
NK072(nu)002:1161: reg byed gsang dbang thabs kyi rdo rje /
NK072(nu)002:1162: reg bya gsang yul shes rab kyi pad+ma /
NK072(nu)002:1163: gsang ba'i rig shes dga' ba nyams su myong ba rnams su yod pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1165: lha'i dus na mthar byed sgo ba bzhir rim par ltar yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1166: phyi nang gi rtog pa gnyis ka go rim bzhin du /
NK072(nu)002:1167: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1170: gshin rje gshed po rnams su dag pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1171: de dag gi yum bzhi po de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1172: khyed rnams la rtag par ma yin pa zhes sogs smos pa ni rtog pa'i mtshan yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1173: rtag par ma yin te phung po mi rtag par 'dzin pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1174: chad par ma yin pa de sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin ngar 'dzin pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1175: bdag tu ma yin pa ste bdag med du 'dzin pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1176: mtshan mar ma yin pa de stong par 'dzin pa
NK072(nu)002:1177: rnams su yod pa de dag lha'i dus na go
NK072(nu)002:1178: rim ji lta ba bzhin du khro mo lcags kyu
NK072(nu)002:1179: zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma dang bzhir nges
NK072(nu)002:1181: yang rtag chad bdag mtshan du 'dzin pa'i phyin ci log gi rtog pa bzhi ltar na /
NK072(nu)002:1182: rtag par 'dzin pa la sogs pa'i rtog pa bzhi po chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1183: khyod rang ga mar snang ba ltar ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1184: khyod rnam pa ma spangs par sgo ma bzhi'i rang bzhin du dag pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1185: zhar byung go phye ba'i 'khor chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1188: sprul sku thub pa drug dang /
NK072(nu)002:1189: rjes 'jug chos kyi mig dang ldan pa'i gang zag
NK072(nu)002:1190: skal ba dang ldan pa rnams la 'jog pa de
NK072(nu)002:1191: yin pa'i phyir / de ltar yang 'di nyid las /
NK072(nu)002:1192: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:1193: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK072(nu)002:1195: rjes mthun 'khor gyi grangs tshad bshad pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1196: khyod la dbye na gnyis su yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1198: mang ba'i tshad gnyis su yod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1199: khyab pa'i tshad de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1201: kun tu khyab cing mtha' yas par khyab pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1202: dper na til gang de til 'bras kyis gang zhing
NK072(nu)002:1203: khyab pa bzhin du gnas pa de yin pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:1204: / mang ba'i tshad de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1206: khyod sngar smos pa de lta bu'i 'khor tshogs kyi
NK072(nu)002:1207: grangs tshad 'di tsam zhes brjod kyis mi lang ba'i
NK072(nu)002:1208: phyir / 'o na khyab pa dang mang ba'i bdag
NK072(nu)002:1209: nyid tsam gyi 'khor de dag dang gnyis su med
NK072(nu)002:1210: par bzhugs tshul de lta bu zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:1212: rang bzhin gnyis su med par bzhugs pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1213: de bzhin gshegs pa dang byang chub sems dpa' ma
NK072(nu)002:1214: lus pa thams cad dpal kun tu bzang po'i rang
NK072(nu)002:1215: bzhin du 'dus pa gang zhig 'gro ba'i phung khams
NK072(nu)002:1216: skye mched ji snyed pa'ang lha'i rang bzhin du gnas
NK072(nu)002:1218: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK072(nu)002:1219: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK072(nu)002:1220: brjod med brjod kyis mi lang ba //
NK072(nu)002:1222: mngon rdzogs rgyal por de nyid nges //
NK072(nu)002:1223: gnyis med lhun grub dkyil 'khor na //
NK072(nu)002:1224: thams cad bdag nyid rtag par bzhugs //
NK072(nu)002:1226: zhar byung le'u'i bsdu ba de /
NK072(nu)002:1229: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang gnyis su med pa'i nas /
NK072(nu)002:1230: rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:1231: zhes pa 'dis bstan pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1232: de yang tshig don du sgril na /
NK072(nu)002:1233: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa zhes sogs gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa'i don de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1235: khyod de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i spyi
NK072(nu)002:1236: gzugs rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i ston pa nyid
NK072(nu)002:1237: kyi thugs la rgyud don ji ltar shar ba'i don
NK072(nu)002:1238: mngon sum du snang bas na phyung ngo zhes tha
NK072(nu)002:1240: e e ma e ma'o zhes sogs kyi don de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1241: khyod kyi gang gsungs pa'i bstan pa de nyid bstan pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1242: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi brjod bya gzhi lam 'bras gsum du 'du ba gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:1243: gzhung 'dis rgyud gsum mdor bstan pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1245: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid zhes pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1246: khyod kyi gzhi'i rgyud mdor bstan pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1247: gnas lugs de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings de nyid 'khor
NK072(nu)002:1248: 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur
NK072(nu)002:1251: rang snang bar nyid ting 'dzin gzugs brnyan sgyu ma rnam dag gsal ba ni /
NK072(nu)002:1253: khyod kyi lam gyi rgyud mdor bstan pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1254: lam ni shes 'jug byed rtsol dang bcas pa'i gdul bya'i snang ba gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:1255: gzhi 'ching grol med pa'i gnas lugs de nyid rtogs pa la dbang bsgyur ba'i lta ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:1256: sems nyid lha'i dkyil 'khor du rang gsal bar sgom
NK072(nu)002:1257: pa'i ting 'dzin gyis thabs yan lag dang bcas pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1258: don 'phro gzhi'i rtsa ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1259: ye shes dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i ngang //
NK072(nu)002:1261: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las /
NK072(nu)002:1262: zhes pa man chad chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1263: khyod kyis 'bras bu'i rgyud don mdor bstan pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1264: chos nyid mngon gyur skyed du byar med par son
NK072(nu)002:1265: pa ni 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba gang
NK072(nu)002:1266: zhig / de shes 'jug gi rkyen des rtog bya'i yul gyi grub 'bras su nges pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1268: bsdu ba'i tshigs su bcad pa 'di chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1269: khyod kyis bstan pa rgyud don mdor bstan du bshad pa'i mi 'thad par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1270: de 'thad na 'og tu gleng bslang ba dgos pa med pa'i phyir zer /
NK072(nu)002:1271: 'di la mgo mtshungs dang rnal lan gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1273: glad du bkod pa'i gsang ba'i snying po zhes sogs kyi mtshan de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1274: khyod kyis rgyud don yongs su rdzogs pa bstan pa mi 'thad par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1276: 'og tu gleng bslang ba la dgos pa med pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1278: ston pa'i thugs la rgyud don ji ltar shar ba'i don gsang bdag gi bsdu ba byed pa'i tshe /
NK072(nu)002:1279: gdul bya dbang rab kyi tshul du bstan pa rgyud
NK072(nu)002:1280: don mdor bstan gyi tshul du bsdus pa yin pas
NK072(nu)002:1281: skyon med cing 'og tu gleng bslang ba la dgos
NK072(nu)002:1282: pa med par yang mi 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:1283: gdul bya dbang rab 'bring man chod la rgyud don
NK072(nu)002:1284: 'og tu ston pas na 'di nyid gleng gzhi'i don
NK072(nu)002:1285: bsdus su bzhed pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:1286: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK072(nu)002:1287: zhes pa'i don de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1289: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK072(nu)002:1290: kyi gsang mdzod 'dzin pa po rgyal sras lag na
NK072(nu)002:1291: rdo rje de / rgyud 'di nyid kyi sdud pa
NK072(nu)002:1292: por ston pas de ltar lung bstan pa'i phyir te
NK072(nu)002:1293: rdo rje de / / rgya mtsho las /
NK072(nu)002:1294: 'khor gyi nang na skal ldan mchog /
NK072(nu)002:1295: 'dul ba'i dus bab gsang ba'i bdag /
NK072(nu)002:1296: lag na rdo rjes bsdu ba mdzad //
NK072(nu)002:1298: de ltar rgyud 'dir sdud pa pos smos pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1300: sdud pa po med na ston pas /
NK072(nu)002:1301: bstan kyang gtam lkugs pa ltar phyis mi 'byung ba'i skyon dang /
NK072(nu)002:1303: ston pa gang gis 'khor gang la bstan cing gtad /
NK072(nu)002:1304: de nas su zhig gi spel /
NK072(nu)002:1305: zhes pa'i sgro bkur spang ba'i ched yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1306: 'phros don du zhar byung gdul bya dgos ched du ston pa khro bo'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK072(nu)002:1308: gdul bya la ltos pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:1309: gong du smos pa'i gleng gzhi de nyid gdul bya'i snang ba la so sor byung ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:1310: gdul bya gdug pa can la khro bo'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK072(nu)002:1311: thun mong gi gdul bya rnams la sprul sku'i gleng gzhir snang ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:1312: 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa'i bshad rgyud las kyang /
NK072(nu)002:1313: gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK072(nu)002:1314: 'og min gnas dang ri rab rtse //
NK072(nu)002:1316: byang chub sems dang lha rnams dang //
NK072(nu)002:1317: mi rnams kyi ni don du gsungs //
NK072(nu)002:1318: ston pa yang ni rnam gsum ste //
NK072(nu)002:1319: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK072(nu)002:1320: sprul sku 'khor lor bsgyur ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:1321: sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NK072(nu)002:1322: zhes bshad pa ltar yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1323: da ni de dag la rtsod spong gi rig pa 'a chad de /
NK072(nu)002:1324: de la rtsod pa 'god pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:1326: le'u dang po'i 'khor 'di rnams rang snang yin par mi 'thad de /
NK072(nu)002:1327: bzang ngan du snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:1329: gdul bya rang rgyud pa med par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1330: 'dul byed sprul pa tshogs pa don med pa'i phyir zer ba mi 'thad te /
NK072(nu)002:1331: 'dir tshogs pa'i 'khor la cha gnyis su yod par lung rig gnyis kyis grub pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1332: gnas lugs kyi dbang du byas na /
NK072(nu)002:1334: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK072(nu)002:1335: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK072(nu)002:1336: brjod med brjod kyis mi lang ba //
NK072(nu)002:1338: mngon rdzogs rgyal po de nyid nges //
NK072(nu)002:1339: gnyis med lhun grub dkyil 'khor na //
NK072(nu)002:1340: thams cad bdag nyid rtag par bzhugs //
NK072(nu)002:1342: rig pas gnod de srid gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba yod do cog chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1343: khyod dpal kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin du yod pa ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1344: khyod le'u dang po'i gtso 'khor gyi nang du ma 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1345: yang snang lugs kyi dbang du byas na yang lung rigs gnyis kyis grub ste /
NK072(nu)002:1347: dang po'i sangs rgyas pa rgyal ba //
NK072(nu)002:1348: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK072(nu)002:1349: brjod kyi mi lang tshad med dang //
NK072(nu)002:1350: rnam gnyis tshul du bzhugs pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:1353: rtog tshogs sbyar ba'i gtso 'khor gyi rnam pa can
NK072(nu)002:1354: gyi rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po de chos
NK072(nu)002:1355: can / khyed gang zag gcig gi rtog pa rgyal
NK072(nu)002:1356: ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su dag pa de ma
NK072(nu)002:1357: can / yin par thal / khyod rnams rgyud thams cad dad pa'i bzang ngan can yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1361: khyod rgyud 'di'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu rgyal ba
NK072(nu)002:1362: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gnas pa de yin pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1364: don bsdus gsung rab bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK072(nu)002:1365: de las lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK072(nu)002:1366: de ni rnam dag lam min te //
NK072(nu)002:1367: rang blos bsam pa 'khrul pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:1369: 'dul byed tshogs pa'ang don med du mi 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:1370: rang snang du gtso 'khor gyi rnam par bstan nas
NK072(nu)002:1371: rgyud mi gsung ba'i gsung ba chen po de gzhan
NK072(nu)002:1372: snang du de dang cha 'dra ba'i gtso 'khor gyi
NK072(nu)002:1373: bkod pa rang shar du byung nas don mdzad pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1376: skabs 'dir rgyud gsungs pa po'i ston pa phun sum tshogs pa de yin na /
NK072(nu)002:1377: rigs drug pa kun tu bzang po yin pas khyab ste /
NK072(nu)002:1378: des ma gsungs pa'i mdo rgyud med pa'i phyir zer na /
NK072(nu)002:1379: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje mi bskyod pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1385: rigs lnga'i nang tshan gyi thugs rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1389: thugs kyi sgyu 'phrul 'chad pa'i skyes bu de yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1392: mi bskyed skyed bu mdun na gnas //
NK072(nu)002:1395: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa yin na /
NK072(nu)002:1397: rigs lnga gang rung yin pas khyab zer na'ang /
NK072(nu)002:1399: thub drug sogs kyis sgrub byed sngar las dpag ste shes par bya'o //
NK072(nu)002:1402: khyod ston pa ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1404: go phye ba'i 'khor yin pa gang zhig rig pa'i skyes bu yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1406: rigs lnga nang phan tshun 'gal ba ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1407: gzhi gcig gi steng du gnas pa'i lha yin pa'i phyir zer na /
NK072(nu)002:1408: 'o na mi bskyod pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1409: rigs bzhi ka yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1410: gzhi gcig gi steng du gnas pa'i lha yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1411: rnam snang gi rang bzhin du 'dus shing dag pa'i lha yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1412: rtog pa'i dus su phung po gzhan bzhi po gzugs phung la ldan pa'i chos gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:1413: lha'i dus su'ang rtog pa de rnams rnam snang gi
NK072(nu)002:1414: gnas de dang de rnams su dag pa'i lha yin
NK072(nu)002:1415: pa'i phyir / 'di dag gi rnal lan ni /
NK072(nu)002:1416: ngo bo'i sgo nas lha gcig gi bdag nyid du khas len te /
NK072(nu)002:1417: til 'bru dang snum gnyis rdzas gcig gi ngo bor yod bzhin yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1418: rnam pa so so bar khas len te /
NK072(nu)002:1420: til gong bu'i rnam pa gnyis 'gal ba ltar grub
NK072(nu)002:1421: pa'i phyir de ltar na tha dad ma yin pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1422: tha dad du khas len dgos te /
NK072(nu)002:1424: tha dad min las tha dad pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:1425: nang dang nang gi phyi rol gyi //
NK072(nu)002:1426: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK072(nu)002:1427: 'jigs med kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK072(nu)002:1429: des mtshon te thams cad la rigs 'dre shes dgos so //
NK072(nu)002:1430: yang gnas kyi skabs su 'jig rten gyi khams dang /
NK072(nu)002:1431: 'og min chen po gnyis gcig dang tha dad gang yin zer na /
NK072(nu)002:1432: ngo bo'i sgo nas gcig tu 'dod de gong du
NK072(nu)002:1433: smos pa'i snum dang til gyi dpe bzhin du khas
NK072(nu)002:1434: blangs pa la gnod byed med cing sgrub byed yod
NK072(nu)002:1435: pa'i phyir / gnod byed med de /
NK072(nu)002:1437: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na /
NK072(nu)002:1439: ngan song gnas kyang 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK072(nu)002:1442: ma dag pa'i 'jig rten 'di chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1443: khyod dag pa'i ngo na 'og min gnas su yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1444: khyod spangs pa'i pha rol na 'og min chen po'i gnas btsal du med pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1445: 'di ltar dri ma med par grags pa'i thun mong gi mdo'i lung gi kyang grub pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1447: 'di ltar rang ga mar snang ba 'di yang min la /
NK072(nu)002:1448: 'di las gzhan du brjod du'ang med do //
NK072(nu)002:1450: yang khro bo'i gleng gzhi'i skabs su kha cig na re /
NK072(nu)002:1451: ru tra de sprul pa ba yin nam /
NK072(nu)002:1454: ngan song gi sdug bsngal myong bar bshad pas rigs pa ma yin no zer /
NK072(nu)002:1456: yi dwags srin po chen po zer bas 'dod khams pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1457: des gzugs khams dbang du bsdus pa mi 'thad de /
NK072(nu)002:1458: der 'grod pa la bsam gtan gyi ting nge 'dzin thob dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:1459: dpal chen po spyod yul gcig tu ma spyad pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1460: zhal mthong ba'i dngos kyi gdul byar gyur pa'ang mi 'thad do zer /
NK072(nu)002:1462: sems can gyi don du de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul
NK072(nu)002:1463: pa tha mal pa'i gzugs su snang ba rnams chos
NK072(nu)002:1464: can / khyod tha mal par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1466: 'dod pa'i rten can gyi 'phags pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1467: khyod kyis gzugs khams dbang du bsdu mi nus par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1468: khyod 'dod pa'i rten can yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1471: skye bo ma rig gis ldongs pa /
NK072(nu)002:1472: srid rtse'i bar du song nas kyang /
NK072(nu)002:1473: zhes pa'i lung gis gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:1474: sh+aakya thub pa mthong ba'i sems can rnams chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1475: khyod kyis thub pa dang spyod yul gcig tu spyad par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1478: des rgyud 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi bshad pa song nas /
NK072(nu)002:1479: gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba la /
NK072(nu)002:1483: dang po gleng bslang gi dgos pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1485: rgyud don gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par myur du
NK072(nu)002:1486: 'byung ba de khyod kyi dgos pa yin pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:1487: / gnyis pa gleng bslang gi ngo bo chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1489: ston 'khor dri lan gcig gi rkyen du gcig gyur pas /
NK072(nu)002:1490: bstan pa 'byung ma rag pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1491: gsum pa gleng bslang gi sgra don de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1493: gleng bar bya ba bstan pa yin la /
NK072(nu)002:1494: de gleng bar bskul ba ni bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen du gyur pas na /
NK072(nu)002:1495: bslang zhes brjod pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1496: bzhi pa gleng bslang gi rnam grangs chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1497: khyod la dbye na gnyis su yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1498: thun min lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi ched du ston pas mdun bsus te gleng bslang ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:1499: thun mong pa go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du
NK072(nu)002:1500: 'khor gyis gus pas dris te gleng ba gnyis su
NK072(nu)002:1501: yod pa'i phyir / de'i dang po thun min lhan
NK072(nu)002:1502: cig pa'i 'khor gyi ched du ston pas mdun bsus
NK072(nu)002:1503: te gleng bslang ba'i go don ni /
NK072(nu)002:1504: ston pa yab yum gyi lhan cig pa'i 'khor la
NK072(nu)002:1505: zab dbang gsum bskur bas zhen pa dag nas rang
NK072(nu)002:1506: bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don rtogs pa de chos
NK072(nu)002:1507: can / khyod thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1508: don dam nges pa'i tshig gis rang bzhin gsang ba'i
NK072(nu)002:1509: snying po'i don dngos su ston pa yin pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:1510: / de ltar yang khog gzhung las /
NK072(nu)002:1511: thun mong ma yin ston pa nyid //
NK072(nu)002:1512: yab yum chags bskul rol pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:1513: dgyes bstar 'khor la dbang bskur bas //
NK072(nu)002:1514: rgyud don 'byung phyir bslang zhes bya //
NK072(nu)002:1516: de gtan la dbab pa la gnyis te /
NK072(nu)002:1518: dbang gnyis kyis las thun mong dus bstan pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:1519: dang po gsang dbang bskur ba la'ang /
NK072(nu)002:1520: yab kyis thabs kyi cha bzung nas sku dang ye shes kyi don gleng bslang ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:1521: yum gyis shes rab kyi cha bzung nas dbyings kyi don gleng bslang ba gnyis /
NK072(nu)002:1522: de'i dang po yab kyi gleng bslang ba de nyid
NK072(nu)002:1523: 'chad par byed pa la de nas bcom ldan 'das
NK072(nu)002:1524: byed pa po rdo rje yid kun tu bzang po
NK072(nu)002:1525: thams cad ma lus pa'i nas /
NK072(nu)002:1526: zhes brjod pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad gnyes par gyur to //
NK072(nu)002:1527: zhes pa'i gzhung 'dis bstan pa yin la /
NK072(nu)002:1529: rgyud kyi ston pa rigs drug pa yab yum gnyis chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1530: khyod la byed pa po rdo rje yid dang /
NK072(nu)002:1531: bya ba mo chos zhes smos pa la rgyu mtshan yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1532: ma rtogs pa'i dus na yid kyi rtog pa ni 'khor ba'i byed pa po dang /
NK072(nu)002:1533: rtogs pa'i dus na 'das pa'i byed pa po rang
NK072(nu)002:1534: rig pa'i ye shes gnyis rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed
NK072(nu)002:1535: pas na rdo rje yid kun tu bzang po zhes
NK072(nu)002:1537: bya ba mo ni dbang po lnga'i yul du ma gyur pa'i 'dus byas dang /
NK072(nu)002:1538: 'dus ma byas kyi chos kyi khams yin la /
NK072(nu)002:1539: des yid bskyed par byed cing yid kyi yul du
NK072(nu)002:1540: gyur pas na btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun
NK072(nu)002:1541: tu bzang mo zhes brjod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1542: de lta bu'i ston pa yab yum gnyis snyoms par zhugs pa la chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1544: de ltar zhugs pa las byung ba'i nyi zla byang chub kyi sems kyis rgyu byas shing /
NK072(nu)002:1545: yab yum gyis nyams su bstar ba'i don ched du brjod pas rkyen byas te /
NK072(nu)002:1546: de'i 'bras bu rtogs pa brjod pas lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams kyis bden pa mthong ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1547: e ma'o rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK072(nu)002:1548: zhes sogs kyi don de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1550: yab kyi thabs kyi cha bzung nas 'khor 'das kyi
NK072(nu)002:1551: chos thams cad phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gcig gi rang
NK072(nu)002:1552: bzhin du sangs rgyas pa la ngo mtshar ba'i tshul
NK072(nu)002:1553: gyis de ltar gleng bar mdzad pas /
NK072(nu)002:1554: 'khor rnams kyis lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa
NK072(nu)002:1555: mthong nas phung khams skye mched zhing la sogs pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1556: chos thams cad lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du
NK072(nu)002:1557: rtogs pas sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos rdul
NK072(nu)002:1558: tsam yang ma grub par rtogs pa yin pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:1559: / de ltar brjod pa la chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1561: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1562: gnyis pa yum gyis gleng bslangs ba 'chad par byed pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:1563: de nas btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mos nas /
NK072(nu)002:1564: zhes brjod pas thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen te /
NK072(nu)002:1565: zhes pa'i gzhung 'dis bstan pa yin la /
NK072(nu)002:1568: rkyen kye ma'o phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben /
NK072(nu)002:1569: zhes sogs kyi don chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1571: yum gyis shes rab kyi cha bzung nas rang gi
NK072(nu)002:1572: nyams su bstar ba'i don dbyings kyi don la ngo
NK072(nu)002:1573: mtshar ba'i tshul gyis de ltar gleng bar mdzad pas
NK072(nu)002:1574: / 'khor rnams kyis lhag pa don dam pa'i bden pa mthong nas /
NK072(nu)002:1578: phung po lnga ste tha snyad bzhis bsdus kyi chos
NK072(nu)002:1579: thams cad ye nas chos kyi skur mngon par sangs
NK072(nu)002:1580: rgyas pas 'bras bu gzhan nas btsal du med par
NK072(nu)002:1581: rtogs pa'i phyir / de ltar brjod pa la chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1583: rtog tshogs thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par de
NK072(nu)002:1584: bzhin gshegs pa ston pa nyid kyis mkhyen pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:1585: te / 'khor rnams kyis dbang thob pa la brten
NK072(nu)002:1586: nas don dam pa'i bden pa rtog med kyi ye
NK072(nu)002:1587: shes skyes kyang ston pa'i dgongs pa dbyer med kyi
NK072(nu)002:1588: ye shes chen po da dung nyams su ma myong
NK072(nu)002:1589: ba'i phyir gsang ba'i dbang zhes brjod pa yang yin
NK072(nu)002:1590: te / pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:1591: de ltar gsang dbang bskur nas /
NK072(nu)002:1593: dbyer med bde chen gyi dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du ston par bzhed nas /
NK072(nu)002:1594: de nas gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen pos zhes sogs gsungs pa yin la /
NK072(nu)002:1595: de ltar gsungs pa'i don de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1598: rtags yab yum nyi zla gnyis su med pa'i ngang nas /
NK072(nu)002:1599: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK072(nu)002:1600: zhes sogs kyi rtog pa brjod pa'i rkyen las 'khor gyis sems lnga bskyed pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1601: sems lnga'i dngos gzhi'i rtog pa brjod pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:1602: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad gyi chos //
NK072(nu)002:1603: skye ba med las zhes sogs gsungs pa yin la /
NK072(nu)002:1604: de ltar gsungs pa'i don de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1611: mthar phyin pa'i sems lnga'i mthar dngos po lhan cig
NK072(nu)002:1612: skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su myong nas shes rab
NK072(nu)002:1613: ye shes kyi dbang thob cing /
NK072(nu)002:1614: mas brtan dga' bzhi'i 'gros kyis sems lnga'i mthar rang
NK072(nu)002:1615: bzhin lhan skyes kyi ye shes nyams su myong nas
NK072(nu)002:1616: ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pa de
NK072(nu)002:1617: yin pa'i phyir / thun mong gi gleng bslang ni /
NK072(nu)002:1618: e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK072(nu)002:1620: de ltar gsungs pa'i don de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1622: lhan cig pa rnams rang don du rgyud zhu ma
NK072(nu)002:1623: dgos kyang gzhan don go phye ba'i 'khor gsang ba
NK072(nu)002:1624: bzhi chod pa rnams thugs rjes bzung bar rigs zhes
NK072(nu)002:1625: brjod pa de yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1626: de ltar zhal gyis bzhes nas lan rtsal ba ni /
NK072(nu)002:1627: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las /
NK072(nu)002:1628: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK072(nu)002:1629: sems can thams cad bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po
NK072(nu)002:1630: can yin pas gshis la bcings grol med pa'i don
NK072(nu)002:1631: de chos can / bshad du yod de /
NK072(nu)002:1632: sems can thams cad ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis bcings grol ltar snang kyang /
