NK072(nu)002:1633: snang tsam nyid nas gshis la de ltar ma grub
NK072(nu)002:1634: pas 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid lhag pa'i chos sku
NK072(nu)002:1635: chen por ye nas lhun rdzogs su bzhugs pa de
NK072(nu)002:1636: yin pa'i phyir / de ltar sangs rgyas kyis thugs
NK072(nu)002:1637: su chud pa'i lhun gyis grub pa'i chos de chos
NK072(nu)002:1638: yin pa'i phyir / can / khyod mtshon par byed
NK072(nu)002:1639: pa'i rgyud 'di dngos brgyud kyi gdul bya la ji
NK072(nu)002:1640: ltar bstan pa'i tshul yod de dgyes pa'i tshul drug
NK072(nu)002:1641: gi sgo nas lhan cig pa'i 'khor la dngos su
NK072(nu)002:1643: go phye ba'i 'khor gdul bya thun mong pa rnams
NK072(nu)002:1644: lam stegs kyi theg pa la brten nas rim gyis
NK072(nu)002:1645: lam 'dir dkri ba'i ched du sprul pa thub pa
NK072(nu)002:1646: drug spro ba sogs sna tshogs su snang nas bsam
NK072(nu)002:1647: gyis mi khyab pa'i mdzad pa 'khor ba ji srid
NK072(nu)002:1648: kyi bar de srid du rgyun mi chad par ston
NK072(nu)002:1650: de yan chad kyis gleng gzhi dang /
NK072(nu)002:1651: gleng bslang gzhung gi 'bru 'brel sbyor ngag nas bshad pa song nas /
NK072(nu)002:1652: da ni spyi'i don la 'jug ste /
NK072(nu)002:1653: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gsum pa /
NK072(nu)002:1654: 'bras bu yongs shes rgyud don bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK072(nu)002:1655: rgyud gsum gyi rnam bzhag spyir bshad pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1656: lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bcu bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1659: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de /
NK072(nu)002:1662: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa bzhi'i rgyu'i rgyud /
NK072(nu)002:1663: rang bzhin mngon du byed pa thabs sam lam gyi rgyud /
NK072(nu)002:1664: rang bzhin mngon du byas pa 'bras bu'i rgyud de shes thob kyi bya byed 'brel ba can no //
NK072(nu)002:1665: dang po gzhi la spyir mtshan nyid /
NK072(nu)002:1667: lung rig gi sgo nas mtha' dpyad pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1668: de'i don bye brag tu bshad pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1670: chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa'i dri bcas de bzhin nyid de /
NK072(nu)002:1671: mtshan nyid des ni ngo bo dang /
NK072(nu)002:1672: rtags gzhi gnyis ka la khyab cing /
NK072(nu)002:1673: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis rnam par bcad pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:1678: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa /
NK072(nu)002:1679: dri ma'i sbugs na yod pa'i gnas lugs de bzhin nyid de /
NK072(nu)002:1681: 'dam gyi dbus na yod pa'i nor bu rin po che lta bu'o //
NK072(nu)002:1683: sa yi nang na gnas pa'i chu //
NK072(nu)002:1684: dri ma med par rang dag gnas //
NK072(nu)002:1685: nyon mongs nang na ye shes kyang //
NK072(nu)002:1686: de bzhin dri ma med par gnas //
NK072(nu)002:1689: log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba glo bur bar gnas pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:1691: nor bu la yod pa'i 'dam rdzab lta bu'o //
NK072(nu)002:1693: gang zhig log par rtog pas med mthong ba //
NK072(nu)002:1694: byis pa 'di dag med pa'i chos la spyod //
NK072(nu)002:1696: de yang yul yul can gnyis med la gnyis su bzung bas log rtog /
NK072(nu)002:1697: de ma yin pa der bzung bas 'khrul pa /
NK072(nu)002:1698: las dang log rtog gi blor snang ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:1703: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi de shes bya ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1704: de shes bya'i yul las 'das pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1705: sher phyin sum brgya pa las /
NK072(nu)002:1706: chos dbyings shes bya ma yin pas //
NK072(nu)002:1707: de ni rnam par shes mi nus //
NK072(nu)002:1710: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK072(nu)002:1711: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir zer ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:1712: yang yul rdzas su grub pa 'di dag shes pa
NK072(nu)002:1713: las gzhan du grub pa'i phyir mi 'thad do zer
NK072(nu)002:1715: de dgag pa la lung rigs gnyis kyis grub pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1717: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK072(nu)002:1718: shes par bya ba'ang kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa gnyis su zad do //
NK072(nu)002:1720: gal po las shes bya'i nang nas dam par ni /
NK072(nu)002:1721: gyur phyir nges pa'i tshig yin no //
NK072(nu)002:1725: tha snyad tsam du gtan la dbab bya ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1726: khyod tha snyad tsam du gzhal byar mi rung ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1727: der ma zad nam mkha' chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1728: khyod skyes bus 'jal ba ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1729: khyod sems rtog gi yul las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1730: sngar gyi lung rnams dang mi 'gal te /
NK072(nu)002:1731: mdor na gzhi lam 'bras gsum du phye ba rmi lam gyi rgyu 'bras so so snang ba ltar /
NK072(nu)002:1732: re zhig 'khrul snang kun btags kyi dbang gis so sor snang tsam la ba zhag mod /
NK072(nu)002:1733: chos kyi ngo bo nyid kyis phye ba ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1734: ngo bo rang rig pa'i byang chub sems su gcig pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:1735: do dam blo'i spyod yul ma yin kyang /
NK072(nu)002:1736: bden gnyis 'byed pa'i rnam bzhag gi tshe /
NK072(nu)002:1738: shes bya tsam gyi snang ba la //
NK072(nu)002:1739: bden pa gnyis kyi zhing sa 'grub //
NK072(nu)002:1743: yul shes la bdag gcig gi 'brel pa med par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1744: yul shes bdag mi gcig pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1747: de la de byung gi 'brel pa'ang med par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1748: bstan med thogs med kyi rigs tsam de las bem po'i rdzas skye mi srid pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1749: nam mkha' dang pad+mo bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:1752: khyod las yul rnams snang ba mi rigs par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1753: yul shes la 'brel pa ma grub pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1755: 'dod mi nus te mngon sum tshad mas gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:1756: de bas na sems las gzhan pa'i chos rdul tsam yang ma grub ste /
NK072(nu)002:1757: 'di ltar yul sogs snang ba nyams su myong ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1758: rmi lam gyi snang ba bzhin dang /
NK072(nu)002:1759: sems kyi ji ltar dbang bsgyur ba ltar rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1760: zad par goms pa'i snang ba bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:1763: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK072(nu)002:1764: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ste //
NK072(nu)002:1766: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK072(nu)002:1767: gdos pa can gyi chos min te //
NK072(nu)002:1768: rtog med rang rig 'od gsal ba'i //
NK072(nu)002:1772: sems las ma gtogs chos med phyir //
NK072(nu)002:1773: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK072(nu)002:1775: slob dpon dpal dbyangs kyi mtha'i mun sel sgron ma las /
NK072(nu)002:1776: chos rnams sems kyi 'khrul pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:1777: sems las ma gtogs chos rnams med //
NK072(nu)002:1779: thun mong gi lung las kyang gsungs te /
NK072(nu)002:1781: ji ltar byas pas btags pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:1782: phyi rol dngos po yod min par //
NK072(nu)002:1783: bag chags kyi ni sbags pa'i sems //
NK072(nu)002:1784: don gyi dngos po rab tu skyes //
NK072(nu)002:1786: mdo sde sa bcu par yang /
NK072(nu)002:1788: khams gsum po 'di dag sems tsam mo //
NK072(nu)002:1789: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:1791: so skye'i shes pa sor bzhag 'di gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhir 'dod na ni /
NK072(nu)002:1792: shes bya ma nor ba yul du byed pas /
NK072(nu)002:1793: 'phags pa'i mkhyen pa dang khyad med du 'gyur la /
NK072(nu)002:1794: de ngo bo'i gzhi ma yin na ni /
NK072(nu)002:1795: 'khrul snang 'di chos nyid kyi khyab bya ma yin
NK072(nu)002:1796: par thal ba sogs kyi skyon gnas so zer na
NK072(nu)002:1798: rang bzhin chos nyid du yongs su rdzogs /
NK072(nu)002:1800: ngo bo la dbyer med ces bya ste /
NK072(nu)002:1802: zhe sdang ma 'dres mnar sems pa //
NK072(nu)002:1803: yongs su rdzogs par stong bdag med //
NK072(nu)002:1804: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK072(nu)002:1805: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK072(nu)002:1807: 'o na ma 'dres pa chos nyid ma yin pa bzhin du /
NK072(nu)002:1808: yongs rdzogs kyi nges nas kyang ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:1809: de nyid ngo bo dbyer med yin pas so zer na /
NK072(nu)002:1811: til 'bru dang snum gnyis rdzas dbyer med na'ang til 'bru khu ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:1812: snum gong bur mi snang ba bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:1813: bzhi pa gzhi'i don bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:1814: lhag pa kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:1815: lhag pa don dam bden pa gnyis //
NK072(nu)002:1816: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:1819: chu zla ltar bden dngos kyis stong pa'i snang ba ris su ma chad pa'i chos so //
NK072(nu)002:1820: de sgrub pa la lung rigs gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1823: kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa yang //
NK072(nu)002:1824: 'dus byas dngos po sna tshogs ni //
NK072(nu)002:1825: sgyu ma'i tshul du thams cad snang //
NK072(nu)002:1826: 'phral snang bya ba kun byed kyang //
NK072(nu)002:1827: rtog pa kun gyi mtshan char snang //
NK072(nu)002:1828: 'di dag thams cad gzugs brnyan de //
NK072(nu)002:1829: bya byed med bzhin dngos po med //
NK072(nu)002:1830: chu zla'i tshul du thams cad gnas //
NK072(nu)002:1831: thams cad snang la rang bzhin med //
NK072(nu)002:1833: gnyis pa rig pas sgrub pa la /
NK072(nu)002:1834: snang tsam dgag med du sgrub pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1835: bden pas stong pa'i snang ba ris med du sgrub pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:1838: khyod dgag med du snang ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1839: khyod kyi gshis la yang dag pa'i ye shes zhig yod pa'i rgyus rang snang ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1840: de yod par gtan tshigs bzhis grub pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1842: snang ba ma grub na 'khrul snang 'byung mi rigs pa'i gtan tshig dang /
NK072(nu)002:1843: snang ba med na don dam shes byed ma grub pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK072(nu)002:1844: snang tsam pa 'di sus kyang dgag mi nus pa'i dang /
NK072(nu)002:1845: rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par rang snang ba'i gtan tshigs dang bzhi las /
NK072(nu)002:1847: da ltar gyi 'khrul snang 'di chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1849: khyod snang ba ris su ma chad pa'i rgyu las byung ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1852: khyod don dam stong nyid klong na dkor bdun du lhun gyis grub pa'i rtsal snang yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1855: thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyag gis kyang mi khegs par bshad pa mi 'thad par thal /
NK072(nu)002:1856: khyod thams cad du rang snang ba ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1859: khyod thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par rang snang ba yin /
NK072(nu)002:1860: de ma yin na khyod bem stong dang khyad par med pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:1861: gnyis pa snang ba bde stong ris med du sgrub pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:1862: de yang mthun snang gi chos can gcig la sgrub na /
NK072(nu)002:1863: rang cag mi rnams la snang du gyur thun mong du dmigs pa'i chu 'di chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1864: rig pa sgyu ma'i snang yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1865: snang ba'i ngo bo ris su ma nges pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1866: ka ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim las /
NK072(nu)002:1867: dmyal ba rang sems me sogs snang //
NK072(nu)002:1868: yi dwags sdig sems mi gtsang yul //
NK072(nu)002:1869: byol song gyen thur ngam grog ste //
NK072(nu)002:1870: mi la mthong yul 'di nyid snang //
NK072(nu)002:1871: de bzhin lha min go mtshon sogs //
NK072(nu)002:1872: lha la dge sems rin chen snang //
NK072(nu)002:1874: rgyu mtshan des rig pa sgyu ma'i snang ba yin par grub ste /
NK072(nu)002:1876: ji ltar sgyu ma mkhan gyi sprul pa'i gzugs /
NK072(nu)002:1877: rta dang glang po shing rta sna tshogs byas /
NK072(nu)002:1878: de la ji bzhin snang ba gang yang med //
NK072(nu)002:1879: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par bya //
NK072(nu)002:1882: sgyu ma mig g.yor sprul pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:1883: smig sgyu 'ja' tshon chu zla bzhin //
NK072(nu)002:1884: zhes pa'i dpes sgyu ma'i dngos po drug tu dbyer te /
NK072(nu)002:1885: de la log rtog sgyu ma ni /
NK072(nu)002:1887: de ma yin pa la der 'dzin gyi zhen pa'i log rtog /
NK072(nu)002:1889: dbang po slad pa'i mig g.yor gyi gzugs ltar snang la ma grub pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1891: snang la tshim pa med pa smig rgyu'i dpes bum
NK072(nu)002:1892: pa la bum par snang ba lta bu'i snang cha
NK072(nu)002:1893: dang / phyag rgya sgyu ma ni /
NK072(nu)002:1894: snang la rtog pa med pa chu zla'i dpes bden
NK072(nu)002:1895: dngos kyis stong pa'i snang ba lha skur gsal ba'i
NK072(nu)002:1896: cha dang / ye shes sgyu ma ni /
NK072(nu)002:1897: med bzhin du rnam par bkra ba 'ja' tshon gyi
NK072(nu)002:1898: dpes rig pa phyi nang med par gsal ba'i cha
NK072(nu)002:1899: dang / thabs sgyu ma ni gcig tu ma nges
NK072(nu)002:1900: pa sprul pa'i dpes de dang der snang ba 'gag
NK072(nu)002:1901: med du 'char ba'i cha nas bzhag pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:1902: de ltar sgyu ma'i dngos po drug po tha dad
NK072(nu)002:1903: med par rig pa la gsal ba ni lhag pa
NK072(nu)002:1905: de ltar kun rdzob dang bden pa dbyer med la khyad par med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:1906: snang yang bden pas stong pa tsam du ngo bo gcig kyang /
NK072(nu)002:1907: gtan la 'bebs tshul gyi ldog pa tha dad pas skyon med de /
NK072(nu)002:1908: 'khyag pa dngos su mthong bas chu lkog gyur du shugs la rtog pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:1909: gnyis pa lhag pa don dam bden pa la /
NK072(nu)002:1910: mtshan nyid ni snang ba ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa'i spros bral gyi chos nyid /
NK072(nu)002:1911: de sgrub pa la lung rigs gnyis te /
NK072(nu)002:1913: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK072(nu)002:1914: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK072(nu)002:1915: mtshan med ma yin rigs rgyud min //
NK072(nu)002:1916: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK072(nu)002:1917: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK072(nu)002:1918: de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes de //
NK072(nu)002:1919: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK072(nu)002:1922: spros bral du sgrub pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1923: de nyid snang ba ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub par sgrub pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1925: phar phyin theg pa'i rig pa dang mtshungs la /
NK072(nu)002:1926: gnyis pa ni spros bral gyi chos nyid de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1927: khyod snang ba ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1928: khyod snang tsam nyid nas brtags na yang dag par ma grub cing /
NK072(nu)002:1929: khyod snang tshod tsam zhig ma 'gags pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1931: med pa nyid na sna tshogs snang //
NK072(nu)002:1932: thams cad shes rab dbyings las byung //
NK072(nu)002:1934: gsum pa lhag pa bden pa dbyer med ni /
NK072(nu)002:1936: snang stong dbyer med par dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid /
NK072(nu)002:1937: de sgrub pa la lung rigs gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1940: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med par //
NK072(nu)002:1941: 'phrul dag'i tshul de tha dad min //
NK072(nu)002:1944: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK072(nu)002:1946: 'dus byas snang ba rdo rje nyid //
NK072(nu)002:1949: rgyal 'gros ma mdzad ma bcos par //
NK072(nu)002:1950: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med ster //
NK072(nu)002:1953: bden pa dbyer med chos can /
NK072(nu)002:1954: khyod thig gu dkar nag sgril ba lta bu'o //
NK072(nu)002:1955: thabs shes dbyer med ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1956: khyod phan tshun gcig gis gcig mi gtong ba'i ngo
NK072(nu)002:1957: bo bdag gcig pa'i dbyer med yin pa'i phyir te
NK072(nu)002:1959: gser dang gser gyi ser po dang //
NK072(nu)002:1960: g.yu dang g.yu'i sngon po lta bu'o //
NK072(nu)002:1961: de nyid mtshan nyid blo bral du sgrub pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:1963: blo'i yul las 'das pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:1964: rang rig mngon sum gyi yul med rang gsal du la zla ba'i chos can yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:1966: bshad du med gang brjod du ji ltar yod //
NK072(nu)002:1969: ji tsam zab pa'i tshig brjod kyang //
NK072(nu)002:1970: don dang mthun par mi 'gyur ro //
NK072(nu)002:1973: mtshan nyid dang de gtan la dbab pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1975: gnas lugs la go bar rtog pa'i zhen snang ngo //
NK072(nu)002:1980: 'khor ba'i chos gtan la phab pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:1981: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos gtan la phab pa dang gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:1983: 'khor bar 'khrul ba'i gzhi ji ltar 'khrul pa'i tshul /
NK072(nu)002:1984: 'khrul pa'i rang bzhin chos nyid las ma g.yos par la zla ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:1986: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa
NK072(nu)002:1987: ye nas dri ma med pa bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK072(nu)002:1990: e ma bde bshegs snying po las //
NK072(nu)002:1991: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK072(nu)002:1994: rgyu rgyud bde gshegs snying po'i snang ba des /
NK072(nu)002:1995: 'khrul gzhi byas nas rkyen lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas 'khrul te /
NK072(nu)002:1997: rtag tu rang bzhin snang gyur kyang //
NK072(nu)002:1998: mig gi mig bzhin ma rig pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2000: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa de gang zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:2002: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa ni lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2004: de'i grogs kun brtags kyi ma rig pa ni yul
NK072(nu)002:2005: yul can du snang ba'i log rtog las gzung 'dzin
NK072(nu)002:2006: gnyis snang shes pa skyes pas /
NK072(nu)002:2007: las dge sdig gi bag chags kun gzhi la bzhag ste 'khor ba mtho dman du lhan cig pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2009: ma rig rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi //
NK072(nu)002:2010: shes dang gzung 'dzin spros la 'chol ba yi //
NK072(nu)002:2011: rnam rtog zhags pas so sor 'dzin //
NK072(nu)002:2014: de ltar brtag gzhi 'khor ba'i chos de dag tu
NK072(nu)002:2015: 'khrul pa ltar snang yang rang bzhin chos nyid las
NK072(nu)002:2017: tho yor la mir snang yang tho yor las ma yos pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:2019: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK072(nu)002:2021: log rtog nyid las gzhan du ci yang med //
NK072(nu)002:2022: stong nyid bdag med ye mkhyen rang rig thugs //
NK072(nu)002:2023: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par rang dbang bsgyur //
NK072(nu)002:2024: ngo mtshar sku gsum yon tan zhing khams las //
NK072(nu)002:2025: gzhan na med de de nyid de ltar yin //
NK072(nu)002:2028: myang 'das kyi ngo bo 'bras bu'i skabs su 'chad cing /
NK072(nu)002:2029: 'dir sku dang ye shes su zhen pa sgro btags kyi blo de brtags gzhi yin te /
NK072(nu)002:2031: brtags pa'i spyod yul gnyis la gzhal //
NK072(nu)002:2035: gnyis pa rang bzhin mngon du byed pa thabs sam /
NK072(nu)002:2037: dpe chung rang gnas las rang bzhin mngon du byed rgyu ni ngo bo dang ni rkyen nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:2038: zhes pas brjod bya don gyi rgyud lam gyi ngo bo nyid dang /
NK072(nu)002:2039: brjod byed tshig gi rgyud lam rkyen du gyur pa gnyis te /
NK072(nu)002:2040: dbye na mdo sngags gnyis ka'i 'jug yul du gyur pa'i thun mong spyi'i lam dang /
NK072(nu)002:2041: ma h+aa yo ga nyid kyi 'jug yul du gyur pa khyad par gyi lam mo //
NK072(nu)002:2042: thun mong gi lam ni nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi dang phyi rgyud sde gsum mo //
NK072(nu)002:2044: thun mong gi lam de khyad par gyi lam du 'agro'am mi 'gro /
NK072(nu)002:2045: 'gro na thun khyad khyad med du thal ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:2046: gal te mi 'gro na thun mong gi dam bca' nyams so zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:2048: dngos su khyad par gyi lam ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:2049: lam thabs grol gang rung la spyod mi nus pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:2050: rim gyis pa la ltos na lam de la bslab dgos pa /
NK072(nu)002:2052: dngos po gso sbyong byin par bya //
NK072(nu)002:2053: de rjes bslab pa'i gnas bcu nyid //
NK072(nu)002:2055: de nas kyee'i rdo rje bstan //
NK072(nu)002:2057: sngags lam don gnyer gyi gang zag rim gyi sa de'i bslab bya yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:2058: sngags lam zab mo de rtogs pa'i thabs rmad du byung ba'ang yin pa'i phyir skyon med do //
NK072(nu)002:2060: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK072(nu)002:2061: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK072(nu)002:2062: ye shes ngo mtshar rab 'byams kyi //
NK072(nu)002:2063: don du mi 'gyur yongs ma gsungs //
NK072(nu)002:2065: de bas na lam de dag gis rang rang gi
NK072(nu)002:2066: 'bras bu sgrub pa dang 'di'i lam stegs su bgrod
NK072(nu)002:2067: pa thun mong du byed pa'i phyir thun mong gi
NK072(nu)002:2068: lam zhes bya'o // lam rgyud kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:2069: rgyu rgyud de glo bur gyi dri ma dang bral
NK072(nu)002:2070: bar byed pa'i thabs shes 'jug gi byed rtsol dang
NK072(nu)002:2071: bcas pa dang / de nyid mthar phyin pa gang rung gi rigs gnas /
NK072(nu)002:2072: de yang ngo bo shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis
NK072(nu)002:2073: thun mong dang mchog gi sems lnga skyes sam skye
NK072(nu)002:2076: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK072(nu)002:2077: sems lnga skyes par bstan pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:2080: skye sa rkyen gyi skye tshul dang //
NK072(nu)002:2081: skyes pa'i ngo bo sems rim pa //
NK072(nu)002:2082: zhes pas skye sa ni gzhi'i sa nas dang /
NK072(nu)002:2088: gnas skabs rigs chad pa dang gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:2090: nyan rang byang sems kyi rigs can gsum mo //
NK072(nu)002:2092: sngar grub mtha' blo ma bsgyur ba'i rkyen gyis dbang gis sems gang du'ang skyer rung ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:2094: theg pa gang du bstan par ma nges pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:2096: yang na nges med 'di zhes brtag tu med //
NK072(nu)002:2100: chos kyi dbyings kyi kun la khyab gyur kyang //
NK072(nu)002:2101: rang rig rtogs pa'i skabs dang mi ldan na //
NK072(nu)002:2102: ji ltar dmus long mdun du mdog bstan bzhin //
NK072(nu)002:2103: 'di ni skal med rigs chad sa pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:2105: thun mong gi lung las kyang /
NK072(nu)002:2106: la la thar pa cha mthun dge ba med //
NK072(nu)002:2108: dkar po dman pa yod pa rgyu dang bral //
NK072(nu)002:2110: de la kha cig na re /
NK072(nu)002:2111: rang bzhin gyi rigs chad yod de //
NK072(nu)002:2113: yang dag pa'i lam dang bral ba dag /
NK072(nu)002:2115: rtsa ba yin te rigs med gyur //
NK072(nu)002:2116: zhes bshad pa'i phyir zer na /
NK072(nu)002:2118: khyod la sangs rgyas kyi rgyu bde gshegs snying po med par thal //
NK072(nu)002:2119: khyod rigs chad kyi sems can yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2122: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab //
NK072(nu)002:2124: dgyes rdor gyi rgyud las kyang /
NK072(nu)002:2125: 'di nyid ye shes chen po ste //
NK072(nu)002:2126: brtan dang g.yo bar khyab nas gnas //
NK072(nu)002:2129: re zhig thar thob kyi skal ba med pa la rigs chad zhes bya ste /
NK072(nu)002:2131: de nas yun ring du 'gyang pa tsam la brjod pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2134: lam rigs bzhi nas skye ba yin te lha mi dang /
NK072(nu)002:2135: nyan rang dang byang sems dang /
NK072(nu)002:2136: phyi rgyud rnams rim gyis bgrod pa'am /
NK072(nu)002:2137: gang rung la sbyor 'phro nas 'dir 'jug pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2139: gzhi yi theg pa dang por gzhog /
NK072(nu)002:2140: de nas rim gyis bgrod bya ste //
NK072(nu)002:2143: la la thun mong lam rnams nas rkyen rgyus 'dir 'jug bslab par nges //
NK072(nu)002:2146: 'og ma'i 'bras bu mthar phyin nas 'dir 'jug pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2148: thun mong sa mthar byas pa'i tshe //
NK072(nu)002:2152: gshin rje mgon las lung gnyis thos //
NK072(nu)002:2153: yon tan mthong dang skyon mthong dang //
NK072(nu)002:2154: de yi skyo rmongs brod dang bas //
NK072(nu)002:2155: gnyis pa'i rgyu ru gsungs pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:2157: de la kha cig na re /
NK072(nu)002:2158: lam rigs bzhi nas sems bskyed pa mi 'thad de /
NK072(nu)002:2159: rang rgyal sngags lam du mi 'jug pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:2160: de nas skye ba snga ma smon lam gsum btab
NK072(nu)002:2161: nas sangs rgyas dang nyan thos mi bzhugs pa'i dus
NK072(nu)002:2164: sangs rgyas rnams ni mi 'byon zhing //
NK072(nu)002:2165: nyan thos rnams kyang zad pa na //
NK072(nu)002:2166: rang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni //
NK072(nu)002:2167: brten pa med par rab tu skye //
NK072(nu)002:2169: de dgag pa la rigs pa dang lung gnyis te /
NK072(nu)002:2172: khyod sangs rgyas kyi dngos kyi gdul bya ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:2178: rang rgyal rnams la bswe ru'i tshul //
NK072(nu)002:2180: gnyis pa lung gis grub ste /
NK072(nu)002:2182: rang rgyal rnams la grogs po'i gzugs //
NK072(nu)002:2183: bstan nas theg chen dmigs la 'dzud //
NK072(nu)002:2185: rnam par 'phrul pa'i rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK072(nu)002:2186: gang dag rang sangs rgyas kyi gzugs kyis gdul bar
NK072(nu)002:2187: bya ba de dag la ni rang sangs rgyas kyi
NK072(nu)002:2188: gzugs su 'dug ste rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba
NK072(nu)002:2189: dang lhag pa'i chos brdas yang dag par ston to
NK072(nu)002:2192: dbang po la ltos te rim dang cig car du 'jug pas skye ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:2194: de yang rang bzhin sbyangs pa yis //
NK072(nu)002:2195: snod du gyur pas nye ring phyir //
NK072(nu)002:2196: rim dang cig car bzhi cha yis //
NK072(nu)002:2203: rang gnas rgyal po'i 'grel par chos nyid kyi rigs
NK072(nu)002:2204: pas mun pa'i sa nas sems phal pa brgyad skye
NK072(nu)002:2205: ste // zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:2208: bskal pa zhing gi rdul rnyed du //
NK072(nu)002:2209: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:2211: ring ba'ang rim dang cig car ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:2214: dbang rnon yin na sbyangs rno yin pas khyab ste /
NK072(nu)002:2215: rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon gzhi ma grub pa'i phyir zer /
NK072(nu)002:2217: chos nyid kyi rigs pas dbang po chig chod du gnas pa'i gang zag de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:2221: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las lha mi'i sems can dbang po mi mthun pas /
NK072(nu)002:2222: la la dbang po ye nas chig chod yod /
NK072(nu)002:2223: la la sbyangs pa'i dbang po 'phro can yod //
NK072(nu)002:2226: kha cig thog ma nas de ring /
NK072(nu)002:2227: kha cig sbyangs pa las gyur pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2231: ma sbyangs grub pa gsum phyir gyis //
NK072(nu)002:2232: mtho brtan myur rno rgya che yangs //
NK072(nu)002:2233: zab mo rgyu yi gang zag de //
NK072(nu)002:2235: bzhi pa skyes pa rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK072(nu)002:2237: 'jig ldang la sogs byang sems lnga //
NK072(nu)002:2238: nges par skyes pa ngo bor 'dod //
NK072(nu)002:2241: grol lam dang thabs lam gyi sems lnga'o //
NK072(nu)002:2244: dang po g.yo ldang byang chub sems //
NK072(nu)002:2245: gnyis pa smon pa gsum 'jug sems //
NK072(nu)002:2246: gnas pa mthar phyin bzhi lnga pa //
NK072(nu)002:2248: gnyis pa thabs lam gyi sems lnga ni /
NK072(nu)002:2250: 'jig dang ldang dang gnas pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:2251: smon pa byang chub sems yin no //
NK072(nu)002:2252: g.yo dang bskyod dang ldang dang gnas //
NK072(nu)002:2254: grol lam gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:2255: gtso bor thos bsam sgom gsum gyi sgo nas 'ching
NK072(nu)002:2256: ba chos nyid du grol bar byed pa'i rigs gnas
NK072(nu)002:2258: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK072(nu)002:2259: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK072(nu)002:2260: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK072(nu)002:2262: thabs lam gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:2263: gtso bor thabs dang gdams ngag gi sgo nas /
NK072(nu)002:2264: 'ching ba la brtul zhugs kyi spyod pas 'bras bu myur du 'grub par byed pa'i rigs can te /
NK072(nu)002:2265: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK072(nu)002:2266: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK072(nu)002:2267: sgyu mar snang ba mig yor tshul //
NK072(nu)002:2268: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK072(nu)002:2269: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK072(nu)002:2271: de ltar lam de gnyis dpes mtshon nas /
NK072(nu)002:2272: bshad na bde blag tu go bar 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:2273: mak+shi ka'i sbyor bas lcags khams gser du bsgyur ba
NK072(nu)002:2274: bzhin thabs la mkhas pa'i myur lam yin pas thabs
NK072(nu)002:2275: lam dang / de la ma brten par gser 'gyur gyi thabs gzhan med pa'ang ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:2276: rin po che ke tu b+ha dang lhan cig bzhag
NK072(nu)002:2277: pa'i rdo'i khams gser du 'gyur pa nyid grol lam
NK072(nu)002:2281: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK072(nu)002:2282: zhes pas rim gyis pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:2285: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK072(nu)002:2286: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK072(nu)002:2287: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK072(nu)002:2288: zhes pas mtshan nyid gsum ste /
NK072(nu)002:2289: dang po rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni /
NK072(nu)002:2290: lam bsgom pa'i sngon du 'gro dgos te /
NK072(nu)002:2291: ma rtogs par bsgoms kyang ltung bar bshad pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:2293: bsam gyis mi khyab ma mthong bar //
NK072(nu)002:2295: blun po mun sprul blo can de //
NK072(nu)002:2296: long ba'i grong khyer chen por 'gro //
NK072(nu)002:2297: zhes gsungs pas de kho na nyid lta bu'i rgyud kyi skabs su 'og tu 'chad do //
NK072(nu)002:2298: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK072(nu)002:2299: mos bsgom dang nges rdzogs gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:2301: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob kyang mos pa lam du byed pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2303: spros pa'i 'khor lo mos bsgom zhing //
NK072(nu)002:2306: lam so so la g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin gyi nyams lnga mthar phyin par bslab pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2307: bi ma la'i phyag rgya bsam gtan las /
NK072(nu)002:2308: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin lnga //
NK072(nu)002:2309: bsam gtan nyams kyi skye tshul yin //
NK072(nu)002:2311: nges rdzogs kyi lam de la dbye na /
NK072(nu)002:2313: srid pa rim par smin tshul gyis //
NK072(nu)002:2314: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bzhag /
NK072(nu)002:2315: ces pas tshogs sbyor gyi lam lnga ste /
NK072(nu)002:2318: phyag rgya gcig pa phyag rgya spros bcas te tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi dang /
NK072(nu)002:2319: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK072(nu)002:2320: 'dir de re re yang chos bzhin bzhes ston pa las /
NK072(nu)002:2321: dang po tshogs lam stong pa chen po'am de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin la /
NK072(nu)002:2323: chos sku'i rtogs pa rgyu mthun du sgrub par byed pa'i thar pa cha mthun gyi rigs gnas /
NK072(nu)002:2324: de yang mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid la blo
NK072(nu)002:2325: gnas par byed pa'i thabs la 'bad pa 'grub ste
NK072(nu)002:2328: shin tu mi dmigs dbyings su bsgom //
NK072(nu)002:2331: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i /
NK072(nu)002:2333: mnyam pa nyid kyi de bzhin nyid de /
NK072(nu)002:2335: gnyis med lhun mnyam de bzhin nyid //
NK072(nu)002:2337: gnyis pa tshogs lam snying rje sgyu ma'am kun snang gi lam la gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:2339: stong 'dzin gyi 'ching ba dgrol zhing gzugs sku'i rtogs
NK072(nu)002:2340: pa rgyu mthun du sgrub par byed pa'i thar pa
NK072(nu)002:2341: cha mthun no // de yang rang rig sgyu ma ltar gsal ba'i snying rje bskyed pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2343: rang rig ye shes snying rjes gzigs //
NK072(nu)002:2346: 'khor ba'i chos la ltos nas log rtog /
NK072(nu)002:2349: sgyu ma dang gsum 'das pa'i chos la ltos nas /
NK072(nu)002:2352: phyag rgya sgyu ma gsum du phye bas drug go //
NK072(nu)002:2353: gsum pa phyag rgya gcig la gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:2355: snang stong tha dad du zhen pa dgag cing rtog
NK072(nu)002:2356: tshogs sku dang ye shes su gsal ba'i thar pa
NK072(nu)002:2357: cha mthun no // phyag rgya bzhi ldan gyi sku snang stong dbyer med du gsal ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:2359: mkha' dkyil dngas pa'i dbyings nyi zla ye shes rgyal po stangs dpyal bsgom //
NK072(nu)002:2362: don gyi rgya gcig pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:2363: rtags kyi rgya pa gcig go //
NK072(nu)002:2365: bden pa dbyer med rang gi mtshan nyid du rdzogs pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2366: gnyis pa la phra rags gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:2370: phyi nang snod bcud h'u du bsdu //
NK072(nu)002:2373: lha'i sku phyag rgya gcig pa bsgom pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2374: zhi ba rgyan gcig pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:2376: bzhi pa phyag rgya spros bcas gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:2378: spros bcas las su rung bas tshogs sgrub kyi dngos rgyur 'gyur rung gi thar pa cha mthun no //
NK072(nu)002:2379: de yang rtog tshogs mtha' dag rig pa gnyis med
NK072(nu)002:2380: kyi lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bar bsgom pa ste
NK072(nu)002:2382: de phyir bden gnyis dbye ba med //
NK072(nu)002:2383: phyi nang snod bcud ye nas dag /
NK072(nu)002:2387: lam phyag rgya spros pa dang gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:2389: rtog tshogs thams cad ye nas lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa'i /
NK072(nu)002:2391: 'og min na 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sangs rgyas du ma snyed bzhugs pa de'o //
NK072(nu)002:2398: rnam grangs spros pa dang bzhi las /
NK072(nu)002:2399: dang po la rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum mo //
NK072(nu)002:2400: gnyis pa la gcig gsum lnga pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2401: gsum pa la zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:2403: khyad par khro bo la dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa nas /
NK072(nu)002:2404: dbu phyag grangs med pa'i bar ro //
NK072(nu)002:2406: zhi ba la sangs rgyas stong dang /
NK072(nu)002:2409: khro bo la stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu dang /
NK072(nu)002:2410: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu /
NK072(nu)002:2411: bsam yas lhun grub gsum mo //
NK072(nu)002:2412: lnga pa sbyor lam bar chad med pa'i lam /
NK072(nu)002:2413: tshom bu tshogs sgrub la gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:2415: lam gzhan gyis bar ma chod par chos nyid rang
NK072(nu)002:2416: mtshan mthong ba la dngos su sbyor bar byed pa'i
NK072(nu)002:2420: nges par legs pa'i dgos pa 'grub //
NK072(nu)002:2422: de yang rtog tshogs thams cad snang stong gnyis med
NK072(nu)002:2423: lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal zhing brtan pa la blo
NK072(nu)002:2425: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bas mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:2429: zhi ba dang khro bo'i tshogs sgrub gnyis /
NK072(nu)002:2430: de gnyis ka nyams su len pa'i dus su /
NK072(nu)002:2431: phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi bzung /
NK072(nu)002:2434: bcings te nyams su len pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2435: zhar byung tshogs sbyor gyi lam lnga la rtsod pa spong ba ni /
NK072(nu)002:2436: 'dod pa brjod pa dang lan gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:2438: stong pa chen po'i lam de /
NK072(nu)002:2439: rgyu shes pa'i lta ba las ngan du song bar thal /
NK072(nu)002:2440: don dam brkyang pa bsgom pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:2441: snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs su lam gong du bgrod pa don med par thal /
NK072(nu)002:2442: snga ma don dam las phyi ma kun rdzob kha spos pas ngan du song ba'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:2445: rten 'brel dngos po sgyu ma gsum sgom pas grol na /
NK072(nu)002:2446: sems can thams cad 'bad med du grol bar thal /
NK072(nu)002:2447: de dag la goms shing bar med du spyod pa'i phyir zer na /
NK072(nu)002:2448: gnyis pa de dgag pa la lung rigs gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:2451: de ltar tshul gsum brjod pa yis //
NK072(nu)002:2452: mthong ba gang yin shes rab spyan //
NK072(nu)002:2453: de yang mngon sum gzhan yangs te //
NK072(nu)002:2454: sgra tshig rten 'brel zhen tsam min //
NK072(nu)002:2455: yul min rang rig bden dbyer med //
NK072(nu)002:2456: blo yi gting go mngon sum yul //
NK072(nu)002:2459: tshogs lam stong pa chen po la /
NK072(nu)002:2460: gnas pa'i gang zag chos can /
NK072(nu)002:2461: khyod thos bsam gyi lta ba don spyi rtogs pa
NK072(nu)002:2462: de sngags kyi tshogs lam thob nas mngon sum gyi
NK072(nu)002:2463: nyams su myong nas gsal brten du byas pa ma
NK072(nu)002:2464: yin par thal / don spyi lam mngon sum gyis
NK072(nu)002:2465: myong ba de sngar las ngan par khas blangs pa'i
NK072(nu)002:2466: yin par thal / phyir / de rigs kyi skabs lung ni /
NK072(nu)002:2467: snga ma snga ma rgyud ldan pas //
NK072(nu)002:2468: phyi ma phyi ma gsal bar byed //
NK072(nu)002:2470: de rang rgyud la ldan pa'i stong kun snang gi yon tan ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:2472: tshogs lam snying rje sgyu ma la gnas pa de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:2473: khyod bden gnyis res 'jog tu byed pa'i gang zag tu thal /
NK072(nu)002:2474: khyod snga ma don dam las /
NK072(nu)002:2475: phyi ma kun rdzob la kha spos pas ngan du song ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2479: khyod kyi rgyud kyi snang ba kun rdzob bden pa
NK072(nu)002:2480: de dag pa lhar snang gi kun rdzob ma yin
NK072(nu)002:2481: par thal / don dam sgrib byed kyi kun rdzob la 'dod pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:2483: gti mug rang bzhin sgrib phyir kun rdzob ste //
NK072(nu)002:2484: zhes bshad pa la 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2485: yang sgyu ma'i chos drug sgom pa'i lung /
NK072(nu)002:2487: 'khor ba yang sgyu ma lta bu rmi lam lta bu /
NK072(nu)002:2488: mya ngan las 'das pa yang sgyu ma lta bu rmi lam lta bu /
NK072(nu)002:2490: chos thams cad rang bzhin ma grub pa'i tshul du
NK072(nu)002:2491: bltas nas bsgom pa ma go ba'i log rtog go
NK072(nu)002:2493: snying rje sgyu ma la gnas pa'i tshogs lam pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:2496: dngos po sgyu ma rnams bden zhen a 'thas su byed pa'i gang zag yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:2497: khyod kyi de gsum la spyod pa de sems can
NK072(nu)002:2498: tha mal pas spyod pa dang khyad med pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:2503: khyod kyi de gsum 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bur spyod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2504: gzhan yang tshogs sbyor gyi lam lnga'i 'bras bu la log rtog bsal ba ni /
NK072(nu)002:2507: snang stong dbyer med rnal 'byor mtha' //
NK072(nu)002:2508: mngon byas lhag pa'i chos skur sbyor //
NK072(nu)002:2510: snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs su /
NK072(nu)002:2511: lam 'dir cha rkyen rdzogs bsgrubs na //
NK072(nu)002:2512: mtshan dang dpe byad kun dang ldan //
NK072(nu)002:2513: dbang phyug chen po'i gnas nyid du //
NK072(nu)002:2514: mngon du 'byung bar the tshom med //
NK072(nu)002:2515: ces pas longs spyod sku dang /
NK072(nu)002:2517: spros tshogs sgrub gsum gyi skabs su /
NK072(nu)002:2519: rnal 'byor las su rung rnams kyi //
NK072(nu)002:2520: phyag rgya chen po rdzogs 'gyur zhing //
NK072(nu)002:2521: gsal la yid gnyis med pas na //
NK072(nu)002:2524: nges par ting nge 'dzin de dang des sku gsum
NK072(nu)002:2525: so sor dngos su thob zer ba mi 'thad de
NK072(nu)002:2526: / de ting gis chos sku thob na snying rje
NK072(nu)002:2527: sgyu ma man chad bsgom pa don med du 'gyur
NK072(nu)002:2529: phyogs mthun brjod kyis rigs ma yin //
NK072(nu)002:2531: des na 'di dag chos mthun rtsis pa'i sku gsum
NK072(nu)002:2532: gyi brgyud rgyu tsam du khas blang bar bya ba'i
NK072(nu)002:2533: don no // gsum pa lam gyur gyi 'bras bu ni zag med kyi lam la dbye ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:2534: de gtan la dbab pa gnyis las dang po la /
NK072(nu)002:2539: nang gses kyis dbye na gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:2540: lhag med mya 'das rnam smin dang /
NK072(nu)002:2541: lhag bcas myang 'das tshe dbang gnyis su nges pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2543: lhag ma med dang yod pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:2544: mya ngan 'das pas mtha' sbyor ba //
NK072(nu)002:2545: zhes pas rig 'dzin de gnyis mthong lam du khad mnyam par bshad do //
NK072(nu)002:2549: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin /
NK072(nu)002:2550: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin bshad pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2553: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong yang blo chung ba'i
NK072(nu)002:2554: stobs kyis 'byung ba snyigs ma'i lus ye shes kyi
NK072(nu)002:2555: mes sbyong bar ma nus pa'i lhag med myang 'das
NK072(nu)002:2558: yid lha'i skur gsal zhing rdzogs par smin pa /
NK072(nu)002:2559: lus rnam smin sha khrag gi phung po dang ma bral ba /
NK072(nu)002:2560: lus rgya dang bral ma thag tu phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:2562: yid kyi lha yi gzugs gzung zhing //
NK072(nu)002:2563: lus kyi rgya mdud grol gyur nas //
NK072(nu)002:2564: rgyal ba'i sku nyid gsal gyur pa //
NK072(nu)002:2565: rnam par smin zhes de la brjod //
NK072(nu)002:2567: gsum pa rnam grangs ni rnam smin gyi lus 'di
NK072(nu)002:2568: rgya chen gyi sar mi khyer bas na lhag med
NK072(nu)002:2569: myang 'das dang / 'byung ba'i lus med pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:2570: las kyi lus med pa zhes bya /
NK072(nu)002:2571: rang don du srid pa'i mngal phyi ma mi len
NK072(nu)002:2572: pas na srid pa tha ma pa zhes kyang bya
NK072(nu)002:2573: ste / yid lha'i skur snang bar smin pa'i rnam
NK072(nu)002:2574: smin gyis lus ma dor bas rnam smin rig 'dzin
NK072(nu)002:2577: lhag med 'byung med las lus med //
NK072(nu)002:2578: mya ngan 'das pa'ang smin chos brjod //
NK072(nu)002:2580: bzhi pa cha lugs ni lus sngon gang yin dang
NK072(nu)002:2581: rtsa ba'i lha gang yin gyi cha lugs 'dzin pa
NK072(nu)002:2582: ste / yid kyi lha yi gzugs gzung zhing //
NK072(nu)002:2584: lnga pa mngon shes kyi yul don ni /
NK072(nu)002:2585: zag med lha yi spyan rnam par dag pa la
NK072(nu)002:2586: sogs pas gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten tsam yul du
NK072(nu)002:2587: gyur cing de dag gi don byed nus pa ste
NK072(nu)002:2589: dpag tshad gling khams lus la sbyor //
NK072(nu)002:2592: rnam smin gyi lus rgya dang bral ma thag tu phyag chen 'od kyi lus la sbyor ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:2594: gang de bral ma thag pa ru //
NK072(nu)002:2595: rgya bzhi rdzogs par bdag gyur pa //
NK072(nu)002:2596: rdo rje lnga sogs rig pa 'dzin //
NK072(nu)002:2597: phyag rgya chen po'i rigs 'bras bu //
NK072(nu)002:2599: tshe dbang rig 'dzin la chos drug las /
NK072(nu)002:2601: chos nyid rang mtshan gsal ba'i ngo bor bskyed du
NK072(nu)002:2602: byar med par mthong zhing skye 'jig med pa rdo
NK072(nu)002:2603: rje'i lus su gyur pa'i lhag bcas myang 'das so
NK072(nu)002:2606: don mthong 'jug pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:2607: tshogs spyod sgrub pa'i dngos grub kyi //
NK072(nu)002:2608: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK072(nu)002:2609: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK072(nu)002:2613: ngo bo thabs dang sman rig 'dzin //
NK072(nu)002:2615: lam mchog rdzogs pa'i rim pa bzhi //
NK072(nu)002:2617: de yang dang po gsum rtogs goms kyi mthu med
NK072(nu)002:2618: pas rdzas dang thabs brkyang pa la brten pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:2619: tshe la dbang bar 'dra na'ang zag bcas dang /
NK072(nu)002:2620: phyi ma ni zag med do //
NK072(nu)002:2622: mi dang 'dod gzugs kyi lha'i gtso bo'i cha byad du ston te /
NK072(nu)002:2624: lha mi'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin //
NK072(nu)002:2626: de lta na'ang lha mi gzhan dang khyad par che
NK072(nu)002:2627: ste skye ba la rang dbang can du gnas pa'i
NK072(nu)002:2629: mi dang lha dang tshangs pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:2630: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK072(nu)002:2631: khyad par sa la gnas 'gyur yin //
NK072(nu)002:2633: de dag kyang sprul pa'i cha lugs yin cing /
NK072(nu)002:2635: da lta'i lus 'di rdo rje'i lus kyi rnam pa can no //
NK072(nu)002:2636: lnga pa mngon shes kyi yul de bzhin spyi'i mngon shes drug dang /
NK072(nu)002:2637: bye brag tu sgo lnga'i dbang shes nyi shu rtsa
NK072(nu)002:2638: lngas gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgya'i zhing khams dang
NK072(nu)002:2639: mnyam pa yul du gyur cing /
NK072(nu)002:2640: de snyed kyi don byed pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2642: gnyis su med par mngon rtogs goms //
NK072(nu)002:2643: mthong bas dri ma drug sbyang phyir //
NK072(nu)002:2644: de snyed gzugs sgra dri ro reg /
NK072(nu)002:2645: shes pa'i bye brag rtsa lnga shar //
NK072(nu)002:2646: gzhan du lha yi rna ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:2647: spyan gyi mngon par shes pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:2648: pha rol gnas kyi sems shes dang //
NK072(nu)002:2651: rim gyis sam thod brgal ba'i tshul gyis lam gong mar sbyor ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:2653: sngon bzhin rim dang cig car ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:2655: gsum pa phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:2657: bsgom bya mngon du gyur pas sngon gang bsgoms kyi
NK072(nu)002:2658: lha'i cha lugs rang mtshan pa 'dzin cing mi g.yo
NK072(nu)002:2659: ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis lhan cig gnas pa'i dri
NK072(nu)002:2660: ma sbyong ba la zhugs pa'i bslab pa'i rig 'dzin
NK072(nu)002:2662: rang sems phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK072(nu)002:2663: bsgoms pas mngon du gyur pa'i sku //
NK072(nu)002:2664: thun mong mchog gi mtshan dper ldan //
NK072(nu)002:2665: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK072(nu)002:2669: ye shes sku yi cha lugs can //
NK072(nu)002:2670: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus las grol //
NK072(nu)002:2676: ma h+aa yo ga'i mchog lnga ste /
NK072(nu)002:2678: de nyid rigs gsum rigs bzhi dang //
NK072(nu)002:2679: lnga dang mchog lnga'i rigs 'dzin pas //
NK072(nu)002:2682: lha sku phyag rgya chen po las mi g.yo zhing //
NK072(nu)002:2684: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa //
NK072(nu)002:2685: sprul pa'i lus kyis 'dul bar byed //
NK072(nu)002:2687: lnga pa mngon shes kyi yul don ni /
NK072(nu)002:2688: rnam shes drug gi bye brag nyer lnga dang bcas pa tshe dbang dang 'dra na'ang /
NK072(nu)002:2689: 'di gsal brtan gyis khyad par du byas shing /
NK072(nu)002:2690: yul longs sku'i zhing dang mnyam pas /
NK072(nu)002:2691: don yang de snyed du byed par nus pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2693: de snyed yul gyi khyad par dang //
NK072(nu)002:2694: don rdzogs mthu dang 'dul byas yongs //
NK072(nu)002:2698: lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag /
NK072(nu)002:2699: brtsol ba med par lhun grub thob //
NK072(nu)002:2701: bzhi pa lhun grub rig 'dzin la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:2703: dbyer med lam gyi rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i sangs
NK072(nu)002:2704: rgyas kyi sa thob ma rag pa'i rgyun mtha' la
NK072(nu)002:2707: de ltar dag pa'i shes pa nyid //
NK072(nu)002:2708: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'dzin //
NK072(nu)002:2709: lhun mnyam ngang las mi g.yo zhing //
NK072(nu)002:2710: mi rtogs nyid du bzhugs pa'ang //
NK072(nu)002:2711: bag la nyal ba 'joms byed cing //
NK072(nu)002:2712: skad cig rag las rig 'dzin mtha'o //
NK072(nu)002:2716: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi rigs gsum lnga /
NK072(nu)002:2717: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i sku lnga lhun grub kyi rgyal mtshan rnam par gsum ste /
NK072(nu)002:2719: bya ba lhun mnyam rnal 'byor gyi //
NK072(nu)002:2723: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'chang chen po'i tshul 'dzin pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2725: cha byad rgyal ba nyid du ste //
NK072(nu)002:2726: lnga po lhun gyis grub phyir na //
NK072(nu)002:2727: de 'dra de nyid rgyal tshab ston //
NK072(nu)002:2729: lnga pa mngon shes kyi yul don ni /
NK072(nu)002:2730: ji snyed mkhyen pa'i yul rgyal ba nyid dang shas
NK072(nu)002:2731: cher 'dra zhing nam mkha' khyab tshad kyi don mang
NK072(nu)002:2734: kun mkhyen ye shes mnga' ba'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:2735: yul ni tshad med rgyal ba nyid //
NK072(nu)002:2736: ji ltar me long lta bu'i tshul //
NK072(nu)002:2739: mthar lam gyi skad cig rgyun mtha' la rdo rje
NK072(nu)002:2740: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bdag tu rtog pa
NK072(nu)002:2741: bzang ngan gyi mtshan ma bag la nyal phra ba
NK072(nu)002:2742: yang bcom ste rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi sar sbyor ba
NK072(nu)002:2743: nyid do // de ltar yang snga ma las /
NK072(nu)002:2744: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK072(nu)002:2745: bdag rtog mtshan ma kun bcom nas //
NK072(nu)002:2746: rdo rje dbyings su thim par byed //
NK072(nu)002:2748: gnyis pa thod rgal gyi lam la /
NK072(nu)002:2751: de ltar 'byung mi 'byung gi rgyu mtshan /
NK072(nu)002:2753: zhar la log rtogs gsal ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:2755: zag bcas kyi lam gyi phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis dang /
NK072(nu)002:2756: zag med kyi tshe dbang dang phyag chen gnyis nas 'byung srid pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2758: lam bar nas bor te gong ma la 'chong nas sbyor ba zhig go //
NK072(nu)002:2760: thod brgal 'byung ba la lam rim gyis pa gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:2761: chos gsum dang ldan dgos te /
NK072(nu)002:2763: lam gzhan bar nas bor du yod pa /
NK072(nu)002:2765: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med du bsgom nus pa dang gsum gzhi gcig la 'tshogs pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2768: de bzhin nyid dang kun snang gnyis dbyer med sgom
NK072(nu)002:2769: pa'i lam pa ma yin pa'i phyir mi 'byung la
NK072(nu)002:2771: lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis lam bar nas bor du med pa'i phyir mi 'byung /
NK072(nu)002:2772: rnam smin gyi dngos 'bras rgya chen du nges pa'i phyir mi 'byung ngo //
NK072(nu)002:2775: tshogs sgrub nas kyang thod brgal 'byung ste /
NK072(nu)002:2776: rgyud las gnyis med gyur nas phyag rgya che //
NK072(nu)002:2777: zhes tshom bu gcig pa nas phyag chen la sbyor ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:2779: zhes tshom bu gsum pa nas lhun grub rig 'dzin la sbyor ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:2780: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub //
NK072(nu)002:2781: ces tshom bu lnga pa nas sangs rgyas par sbyor bar bshad pa'i phyir zer ba mi 'thad de /
NK072(nu)002:2782: rgyud kyi lung tshan gsum ni /
NK072(nu)002:2783: tshogs sgrub kyii dus tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa bsgrub pas thob pa'i tshe dbang de /
NK072(nu)002:2785: mthar lam sangs rgyas la sbyor ba'i lung yin gyi /
NK072(nu)002:2786: tshogs sgrub nas thod brgal 'byung ba'i lung ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:2787: gal te yin na zag med lam gyi 'du ba dang dbye ba mthong lam ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:2788: tshogs sgrub nas thod brgal 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2791: lam mchog dbye sa gcig yin no //
NK072(nu)002:2792: zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:2794: zag bcas zag med kyi khyad par spyir bshad /
NK072(nu)002:2795: zag ldog yod med kyi sa mtshams bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2797: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa'i las kyi
NK072(nu)002:2798: kun nas blangs te khams gsum du zag cig 'pho
NK072(nu)002:2800: de las log pa ni zag med do //
NK072(nu)002:2803: phyin ci log gi sgro btags nyon mongs pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:2804: lus rang dbang med par 'dod ba lus kyi dang /
NK072(nu)002:2805: bde mi bde rang dbang med par myong ba khams kyi dang /
NK072(nu)002:2806: las kyi stobs kyis rang dbang med par lus len pa skye gnas kyi zag pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2807: de la nyon mongs pa'i 'dzin pa ni gtso bo ste /
NK072(nu)002:2808: des 'khor bar zag pa'i rgyu'i sa bon drung pa byed pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2809: bran ni phyi ma gsum ste /
NK072(nu)002:2810: de tsam gyis 'khor bar 'ching mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:2812: spyir zag ldog yod med kyi mu bzhi ste /
NK072(nu)002:2813: zag pa med la bzlog pa yod pa'i lam ni /
NK072(nu)002:2814: theg pa chung ngu'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu dgra bcom thob pa zhig /
NK072(nu)002:2815: sngags kyi theg pa la zhugs nas tshogs lam gang rung la gnas pa de'o //
NK072(nu)002:2816: rgyud rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK072(nu)002:2817: ji srid sa brgyad ma thob bar //
NK072(nu)002:2818: de srid theg pa dman pas 'jigs //
NK072(nu)002:2820: gnyis pa zag ldog gnyis ka yod pa'i lam ni /
NK072(nu)002:2821: tshogs sbyor gyi rnam par bzhi ste /
NK072(nu)002:2823: de phyir lam bzhir zag ldog yod //
NK072(nu)002:2825: gsum pa de yod kyang ldog pa med pa'i lam ni /
NK072(nu)002:2826: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs sgrub ste spyod pa'i dus
NK072(nu)002:2827: grangs nges pas zag med la dngos su sbyor ba'i
NK072(nu)002:2828: bar chad med lam yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:2830: bar chad med par sbyor ba yis //
NK072(nu)002:2832: bzhi pa zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam ni /
NK072(nu)002:2835: zag kun zad pa'i rigs chen ni //
NK072(nu)002:2836: ji ltar spyad kyang ldog pa med //
NK072(nu)002:2838: gnyis pa grol lam cig car ba la /
NK072(nu)002:2841: rnam par dbye bas gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2843: dbang po yang rab kyis 'bras bu myur du thob pa'i ched du'o //
NK072(nu)002:2845: rtogs goms gcig chod du mthar phyin par byed pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:2846: gsum pa la sngar ltar mtshan nyid gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:2848: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs dbyer med chig chod
NK072(nu)002:2849: du rtogs pas gzhal bya dang gtan tshigs la sogs
NK072(nu)002:2850: pa'i tha snyad kyis stong pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2852: chos dang chos can kun bral bar //
NK072(nu)002:2854: mi phyed rdo rje thugs mchog go //
NK072(nu)002:2856: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin la mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:2858: cho ga'i yan lag la ma ltos par skad cig dran rdzogs su bskyed cing /
NK072(nu)002:2862: snying po brjod pas 'khor lor shar //
NK072(nu)002:2866: thig le chen po'i rang bzhin la //
NK072(nu)002:2867: bsgom pa rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK072(nu)002:2870: rig 'dzin bzhi'i char gtogs pa'i ye shes gcig chod du mngon du gyur pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2872: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK072(nu)002:2873: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:2876: gdam ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo //
NK072(nu)002:2878: rim gyis pa steng sgo dang /
NK072(nu)002:2881: 'khor lo drug la brten nas rdub dgangs skyil dbab la sogs te /
NK072(nu)002:2882: gtum mo ye shes kyi me dang /
NK072(nu)002:2883: thig le byang chub kyi sems 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor
NK072(nu)002:2884: bas 'khor lor bzhir bde ba'i ye shes rim gyis
NK072(nu)002:2885: bskyed pa'i phyir steng sgo ste /
NK072(nu)002:2887: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK072(nu)002:2890: dngos su rlung sems la dbang thob pas 'og sgo nyams su blang du rung zhing //
NK072(nu)002:2891: brgyud 'bras 'og sgo dang thun mong du'o //
NK072(nu)002:2892: gnyis pa ni mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas dbab
NK072(nu)002:2893: bzung ldog bkram la sogs pa'i man ngag gis bde
NK072(nu)002:2894: stong gnyis med kyi ye shes cig car du nyams
NK072(nu)002:2895: su myong bar byed pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:2898: dal rdo rje lce yi blangs zhes pa'i bar /
NK072(nu)002:2909: theg pa thun mong gi dang /
NK072(nu)002:2913: de nas sa bcu rim gyis 'byang //
NK072(nu)002:2914: bla med byang chub yang dag thob //
NK072(nu)002:2919: 'o na gzhi ji lta ba bzhin mngon du byas
NK072(nu)002:2920: pas spangs thob med par sku dang ye shes kyi
NK072(nu)002:2921: dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba mthar thug pa'i chos
NK072(nu)002:2922: so // de ltar yang 'di nyid las /
NK072(nu)002:2923: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK072(nu)002:2924: gzhan las yod 'ongs ma yin te //
NK072(nu)002:2925: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK072(nu)002:2926: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK072(nu)002:2928: bsam gtan mig sgron gyi rang 'grel las /
NK072(nu)002:2929: don du rang rig pa de bzhin nyid du son pa nyid sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thob //
NK072(nu)002:2934: gsang sngags kyi lam bde zhing myur ba'i thabs kyi
NK072(nu)002:2935: khyad par du byas kyi mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK072(nu)002:2938: don gcig na'ang ma rmongs dang //
NK072(nu)002:2939: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:2940: dbang po'i rnon po'i dbang byas nas //
NK072(nu)002:2941: thabs la gsang sngags khyad par 'phags //
NK072(nu)002:2944: rig pa dang lung gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:2946: rgyu'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu kun tu 'od kyi sa la gnas pa'i gang zag de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:2947: sngags kyi mi slob lam du 'jug mi dgos par thal /
NK072(nu)002:2948: khyod mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob zin pa'i gang zag yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:2952: khyod la mthar thug 'bras bu'i dbang bskur nas sangs rgya dgos kyi gang zag yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:2954: dgongs pa tha ma thob nas ni //
NK072(nu)002:2955: 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK072(nu)002:2960: pad+ma can du gyur pa na //
NK072(nu)002:2963: khyod kyi mthar phyin kun tu 'od //
NK072(nu)002:2964: thabs chen theg pa'i bsti gnas pa //
NK072(nu)002:2966: gzhan yang mdo sngags gnyis la /
NK072(nu)002:2967: dbang dang shes 'jug rtogs goms kyi lam la khyad par yod pa ltar /
NK072(nu)002:2968: mthar thug gi 'bras bu la yang yod dgos te /
NK072(nu)002:2969: gsang sngags kyi dbang sogs kyi rgyu med pa'i gsang
NK072(nu)002:2970: sngags kyi mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob pa mi
NK072(nu)002:2972: 'bras bu ni rgyu'i rjes su 'gro ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2973: yang kha cig na re lam goms pa'i rgyu rkyen las byung ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2974: 'bras bu 'dus byas su 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:2976: rang gi sems nyid sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas bzhugs pa nyid /
NK072(nu)002:2977: lam gyi zhen pa dag pa'i ngo na der gsal ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2978: dper na sprin dengs ba'i nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor snang ba bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:2980: shes rab dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK072(nu)002:2981: thabs kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:2983: de ltar na mtshan ma can du 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:2984: 'bras bu kun rdzob sku dang ye shes su snang ba'i phyir zer na /
NK072(nu)002:2986: de ltar yang de'i ngo bo cir yang bzung du
NK072(nu)002:2987: med pas na yod pa'i mtshan mar mi 'gyur zhing
NK072(nu)002:2988: / des don byed mi nus pa yang ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:2989: gzhan snang gzugs sku gnyis kyang rang snang yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:2990: sgyu ma lta bu'i 'phrin las kyis don mdzad la /
NK072(nu)002:2991: de'i dus na ngo bo nyid gzhan du 'gyur ba ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:2992: 'dus ma byas shing skye 'jig dang bral ba /
NK072(nu)002:2993: chos kyi sku las mi g.yo ba'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:2995: ye shes rol pa nyid kyang gsog /
NK072(nu)002:2996: rgyal ba mngon byung skyob pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:2997: byin rlabs ston pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK072(nu)002:2998: bya byed nus pa'i gzi byin gyis //
NK072(nu)002:2999: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan pa mchog /
NK072(nu)002:3002: sangs rgyas rnams la chos skus khyab pa gcig las
NK072(nu)002:3003: ma g.yos par gzugs sku tha dad du snang ba'i
NK072(nu)002:3005: khyab bya gzugs sku tha dad kyi rang bzhin chos
NK072(nu)002:3006: kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pas rgyud tha dad med
NK072(nu)002:3007: pa'i phyir du ma dang bral lo //
NK072(nu)002:3008: de la ltos pa'i gnyis ka dang gnyis ka ma yin pa'i mu yang med de /
NK072(nu)002:3009: gcig dang du ma ma grub pas de'i mu khegs pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3010: de las gzhan du sangs rgyas kyis kyang gzigs par mi 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:3011: gzigs bya gzigs byed kyi yul las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3012: de bas na dgongs pa yul dang yul can med par rang gsal ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:3014: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK072(nu)002:3015: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK072(nu)002:3016: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK072(nu)002:3017: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK072(nu)002:3025: thun mong min pa'i rgyal ming grangs //
NK072(nu)002:3026: bde gshegs de bzhin gshegs pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:3027: bcom ldan 'das dang sangs rgyas dang //
NK072(nu)002:3028: dgyes chen brjod sogs bsam mi khyab //
NK072(nu)002:3039: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK072(nu)002:3040: longs spyod zad med rin chen gter //
NK072(nu)002:3041: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK072(nu)002:3046: me long ye shes mi g.yo ste //
NK072(nu)002:3047: ye shes gsum ni de la brten //
NK072(nu)002:3048: mnyam pa nyid dang so sor rtog /
NK072(nu)002:3049: bya ba grub pa kho na'o //
NK072(nu)002:3052: ma 'dres rnam grangs su snang ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:3053: dbyer med lhun grub kyi ngo bo'o //
NK072(nu)002:3054: dang po la rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:3056: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga re re la'ang bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:3059: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3062: kun tu gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3065: kun tu thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3069: ye shes spyan gyis spras pa'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:3070: zhing dang yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK072(nu)002:3074: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK072(nu)002:3075: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK072(nu)002:3076: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub //
NK072(nu)002:3080: de yang skabs kyi lnga lnga ste //
NK072(nu)002:3081: zhes pas re re yang lnga lnga'o //
NK072(nu)002:3082: de bas dang po sku lnga ni /
NK072(nu)002:3083: rang don rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i ngo bo dbyings
NK072(nu)002:3084: thog tu rig pa'i ye shes grol ba ni chos
NK072(nu)002:3086: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK072(nu)002:3088: de las ma g.yo bar gdul bya las dag pa
NK072(nu)002:3089: sa bcu pa'i ngor rten lus nyid zag med du
NK072(nu)002:3090: gyur pa'i rgyu 'bras thun min gyi mtshan dpe dang
NK072(nu)002:3091: ldan par snang ba longs sku ste /
NK072(nu)002:3093: yang dag thar pa'i gzugs sku dang //
NK072(nu)002:3095: gdul bya ma dag pa 'gro ba drug la mos
NK072(nu)002:3096: pa dang mthun par snang nas don mdzad pa ni
NK072(nu)002:3099: mthun byas sku ni sna tshogs ston //
NK072(nu)002:3101: de ltar gzugs sku gnyis su snang yang rang rgyud pa med de /
NK072(nu)002:3102: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos pa'i chos sku dang /
NK072(nu)002:3103: gzugs sku dbyer mi phyed pa ni rdo rje'i sku ste /
NK072(nu)002:3105: ston nyid sgyu ma mig yor tshul //
NK072(nu)002:3106: tshul nyid dbyings las g.yos pa med //
NK072(nu)002:3108: de dag rig pa'i ye shes la /
NK072(nu)002:3109: lhun gyi rdzogs pas chos sku las ma g.yos bzhin
NK072(nu)002:3110: du gdul bya'i las dang mthun par sna tshogs su
NK072(nu)002:3111: snang ba ni mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ste
NK072(nu)002:3113: ma g.yos bzhin du sna tshogs pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:3114: de tshe mi mthun sna tshogs la //
NK072(nu)002:3115: so so 'dra bar snang ba ni //
NK072(nu)002:3116: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK072(nu)002:3117: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK072(nu)002:3120: ston pa sku lngas rang gi 'khor la brda' sprod pa'i bdag nyid can de /
NK072(nu)002:3121: de'ang chos nyid smra brjod dang bral ba nyid brjod
NK072(nu)002:3122: bya kun gyi gzhir gyur pa'i cha nas chos sku
NK072(nu)002:3123: skye med don gyi gsung ste /
NK072(nu)002:3125: sgra dang ming tshig kun las 'das //
NK072(nu)002:3126: sna tshogs sgra rnams gsal bar 'byung //
NK072(nu)002:3128: me long gis byad kyis dri ma ngos zin nas
NK072(nu)002:3129: sel bar byed pa ltar sku'i brdas 'khor gyi blo
NK072(nu)002:3130: la don 'jal bar ston pa ni longs sku dgongs
NK072(nu)002:3133: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK072(nu)002:3134: sku yi chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK072(nu)002:3136: gang la gang 'dul gyi sgra skad dang mthun par
NK072(nu)002:3137: dus gcig tu chos ston pa ni sprul sku brjod
NK072(nu)002:3140: brjod med de nyid sna tshogs sgra //
NK072(nu)002:3141: kun la grags shing so sor 'jal //
NK072(nu)002:3143: sgra skad thams cad grags stong gnyis su med pas
NK072(nu)002:3144: mtha' gnyis las grol ba ni dbyer med rdo rje'i
NK072(nu)002:3145: gsung ste / sgra nyid ma chags ngang du gsungs //
NK072(nu)002:3146: gsungs pa nyid na brjod du med //
NK072(nu)002:3148: sgra thams cad rang rigs pa'i ngang du lhun gyis
NK072(nu)002:3149: grub pas cir yang mi 'gag pa rig pa byin
NK072(nu)002:3150: rlabs kyi gsung ni mngon byang gi gsung ste /
NK072(nu)002:3152: grol thar lam dang 'khor ba'i sgra //
NK072(nu)002:3153: ji skad brjod kyang gsung mchog ste //
NK072(nu)002:3156: ye shes lnga la bya ste /
NK072(nu)002:3157: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes ni chos sku rnam par mi rtog pa'i thugs te /
NK072(nu)002:3159: bde ba chen po mchog gi thugs //
NK072(nu)002:3160: nam mkha' lta bur ye gsal stong //
NK072(nu)002:3162: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes ni longs sku mnyam pa chen po'i thugs te /
NK072(nu)002:3164: mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yo ba //
NK072(nu)002:3165: mnyam pa chen po mchog gi thugs //
NK072(nu)002:3167: bya grub ye shes ni sprul sku 'gro ba sgrol ba'i thugs te /
NK072(nu)002:3169: nyid kyi dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK072(nu)002:3170: bya byed med par rnam bzhi yis //
NK072(nu)002:3171: 'gro ba kun sgrol thugs chen yin //
NK072(nu)002:3173: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes ni mi 'gyed rdo rje'i thugs te /
NK072(nu)002:3175: chos dang chos can kun bral ba //
NK072(nu)002:3176: rang spyi dbyer med dus gcig tu //
NK072(nu)002:3177: mkha' la 'ja' ltar gsal ba ni //
NK072(nu)002:3178: mi phyed rdo rje'i thugs mchog go //
NK072(nu)002:3180: me long lta bu'i ye shes ni mngon byang gis ci yang sal le mkhyen pa'i thugs te /
NK072(nu)002:3182: chos spyi rang mtshan dbyer med kun //
NK072(nu)002:3183: yul med me long ltar gsal ba //
NK072(nu)002:3184: mngon sum kun gyi mchog yin te //
NK072(nu)002:3185: rnam par mi rtog mchog gi thugs //
NK072(nu)002:3187: bzhi pa yon tan lnga las /
NK072(nu)002:3188: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams ni //
NK072(nu)002:3190: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK072(nu)002:3192: zhing khams rnam dag bsam yas dang //
NK072(nu)002:3194: rgya tshad dang bral ba'i gzhal yas ni /
NK072(nu)002:3196: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK072(nu)002:3198: gsal zhing dag pa'i 'od zer ni //
NK072(nu)002:3201: khyad par du 'phags pa'i gdan khri ni //
NK072(nu)002:3202: seng+ge glang chen rta rma bya //
NK072(nu)002:3203: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK072(nu)002:3204: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK072(nu)002:3206: dgyes dgur spyod pa'i longs spyod ni //
NK072(nu)002:3207: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK072(nu)002:3209: lnga pa phrin las lnga ni /
NK072(nu)002:3214: lhun gyis grub pa ste rgyas pa las /
NK072(nu)002:3215: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK072(nu)002:3216: bya byed med las rnam bzhir mdzad //
NK072(nu)002:3217: mdzad dang mdzad par bya ba med //
NK072(nu)002:3224: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK072(nu)002:3225: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK072(nu)002:3227: che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa'i rten byed pas na sku /
NK072(nu)002:3228: gdul bya la brda' spros pas na gsung /
NK072(nu)002:3229: shes bya thams cad mkhyen pas na thugs /
NK072(nu)002:3230: mnga' thang rdzogs pas na yon tan /
NK072(nu)002:3231: gdul bya 'dul bas na phrin las te /
NK072(nu)002:3233: rten byed pas na sku nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:3234: go brda' sprod pas na gsung nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:3235: rig cing mkhyen pas na thugs nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:3236: 'dod dgu 'byung bas na yon tan nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:3237: bya ba byed pas na phrin las nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:3243: sgrib bral gyi dgongs pa dbyings ye zung du 'jug pa chos sku /
NK072(nu)002:3244: de nyid 'khor smon pa rgya mtsho la nges pa lnga ldan du snang ba longs sku /
NK072(nu)002:3245: 'khor mos pa rgya mtsho la snang ba sprul sku /
NK072(nu)002:3246: de gsum snang cha ma 'dres pa'i cha nas mngon byang /
NK072(nu)002:3247: dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha nas rdo rje sku ste lnga'o //
NK072(nu)002:3248: de gcig gam tha dad ce na /
NK072(nu)002:3249: sku lnga lhun grub kyi bdag nyid du ngo bo
NK072(nu)002:3250: gcig la de nyid yon tan gyi ldog cha nas
NK072(nu)002:3251: sku lngar snang ba tha dad de /
NK072(nu)002:3252: mkha' zla dang chu zla bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:3254: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK072(nu)002:3255: nyon mongs kun gyi zhing du gnas //
NK072(nu)002:3256: zad mi shes pa'i gter du 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:3257: thams cad dbyer med mnyam pa'i sku //
NK072(nu)002:3258: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes sku //
NK072(nu)002:3259: de tshe sku lnga kun kyang rdzogs //
NK072(nu)002:3261: de yang zur pa rnams mngon byang dang rdo rje'i
NK072(nu)002:3262: sku ni yon tan gyi ldog cha nas btags pa
NK072(nu)002:3263: tsam yin pa'i phyir sku btags pa ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:3264: sku mtshan nyid pa ni gsum du nges so gsung /
NK072(nu)002:3265: kun mkhyen klong chen pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:3266: chos sku mngon byang rdo rje'i sku gsum sangs rgyas
NK072(nu)002:3267: rang snang gis bsdus pas sku mtshan nyid pa dang
NK072(nu)002:3268: / longs sprul gnyis gdul bya'i blos bsdus pas btags pa'o gsung ngo //
NK072(nu)002:3269: gnyis pa dbyer med lhun grub kyi ngo bo ni /
NK072(nu)002:3270: 'bras bu nyer lnga po de dag kyang sku lnga'i
NK072(nu)002:3271: bdag nyid rgyal ba drug pa'i yon tan gyi ldog
NK072(nu)002:3273: de'i yon tan du 'du ba'i phyir gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i bdag nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:3275: sangs rgyas mnyam dang dbyings su grol //
NK072(nu)002:3276: de nyid chen por lhun gyis grub //
NK072(nu)002:3279: 'bras bu yon tan lhun grub pas //
NK072(nu)002:3280: yid bzhin nor bu ltar snang ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:3282: gsum pa sa'i rnam grangs ni /
NK072(nu)002:3284: sa yi khyad par bcu dang gsum //
NK072(nu)002:3285: zhes pa'i skabs kyi sa bcu pa man chad ni mtshan nyid pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:3286: spang bya spong ba dang gnyen po skye ba'i sa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3287: gsum po ni btags pa ba ni /
NK072(nu)002:3288: mthar thug 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sa gcig gi
NK072(nu)002:3289: ngo bo la sku gsum gyi cha las sa gsum
NK072(nu)002:3292: mthar thug sa gsum cha las brjod //
NK072(nu)002:3294: he ru ka gal po las /
NK072(nu)002:3295: dbyings las ye shes shar ba kun tu 'od //
NK072(nu)002:3296: pad+ma'i spyan 'dra mi 'gag longs spyod rdzogs //
NK072(nu)002:3297: yi ge 'khor lo gdul byar sprul pa 'byed //
NK072(nu)002:3298: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sa zhes bya ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:3300: des na ngo bo la khyad par med kyang mtshon tshul la khyad par yod de /
NK072(nu)002:3301: dus thams cad du chos nyid mtha' ma sgribs par
NK072(nu)002:3302: gsal ba'i don mngon du byas pas kun tu 'od
NK072(nu)002:3303: de ye shes bla ma'i sa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK072(nu)002:3304: de'i tshe thabs snying rje chen pos gzhan don mdzad
NK072(nu)002:3305: kyang dmigs pa med pa'i shes rab kyi gdengs kyis
NK072(nu)002:3306: nyes skyon gyis ma gos par mkhyen pas pad+ma can
NK072(nu)002:3307: / de'i tshe spyod yul thams cad sku dang ye
NK072(nu)002:3308: shes kyi dkyil 'khor du snang la ma zhen pas
NK072(nu)002:3309: ye shes 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa ste /
NK072(nu)002:3311: thabs dang shes rab sa yi mchog /
NK072(nu)002:3313: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK072(nu)002:3314: spyod yul kun tu man+dala la //
NK072(nu)002:3315: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par rol //
NK072(nu)002:3316: zhes pas 'khor lo tshogs chen te thun mong du ma grags pa'i sa gnyis bstan no //
NK072(nu)002:3317: 'o na bla ma gong ma dag /
NK072(nu)002:3318: kun tu 'od phar phyin theg pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
NK072(nu)002:3319: pad+ma can ma h+aa yo ga'i yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen a nu yo ga'i sa /
NK072(nu)002:3320: zhes bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:3322: de dag ni sa'i dbye tshul 'di dang tha dad pa gzhan te /
NK072(nu)002:3323: 'dir bshad par bya ba ma yin no //
NK072(nu)002:3325: mthar thug sa gsum cha las brjod /
NK072(nu)002:3326: ces pa'i skabs nas bstan pa'i chos sku'i sa ye shes bla ma'am kun tu 'od dang /
NK072(nu)002:3327: phar phyin theg pa'i bcu gcig pa kun tu 'od gnyis gcig par 'gyur la de ltar na /
NK072(nu)002:3329: lam gyi rtsol bas ngal ba rnams //
NK072(nu)002:3330: brod pa skye phyir kun tu 'od //
NK072(nu)002:3331: rdo rje 'dzin pa bkod par bstan //
NK072(nu)002:3332: mthar thug sa gsum cha las brjod //
NK072(nu)002:3333: ces pa'i rgyu'i theg pa'i kun tu 'od dang /
NK072(nu)002:3334: mthar thug gi sa gsum gyi nang tshan gyi kun tu 'od gcig par thal /
NK072(nu)002:3338: rang sa thob la ngo bo nyid //
NK072(nu)002:3339: gcig par smra ba mun sprul lo //
NK072(nu)002:3341: kri ya'i rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa /
NK072(nu)002:3342: yo ga'i stug po bkod pa'i sa /
NK072(nu)002:3343: mthar thug ma h+aa yo ga'i sa rnams kyi 'bras
NK072(nu)002:3344: bu la khyad che bas gzhan dag khyad med ces
NK072(nu)002:3345: smra ba ni mun sprul lo zhes bzhed pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:3346: ro // de bas na rgyu'i theg pa'i kun tu
NK072(nu)002:3347: 'od sngags lam gyi lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi sa
NK072(nu)002:3348: ro // yin pas / lam gyi chos sku zhes kyang miing du btags te /
NK072(nu)002:3349: dbu ma'i mkhan po +aar+ya de bas /
NK072(nu)002:3350: rgyu yis theg pa'i kun tu 'od //
NK072(nu)002:3351: thabs chen lam gyi chos sku ste //
NK072(nu)002:3352: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la //
NK072(nu)002:3353: rgya mtsho rlabs bzhin shugs kyis 'char //
NK072(nu)002:3355: smon lam stobs la rag ma nus //
NK072(nu)002:3357: bsam gtan mig sgron gyi rang 'grel las /
NK072(nu)002:3358: dbu mas bskal par sbyangs pas grub pa'i kun tu
NK072(nu)002:3359: 'od smon lam dang snying rje'i stobs kyis gzugs sku
NK072(nu)002:3360: 'char ba dang / thabs chen po gnyis med kyi sku lnga ma btsal rdzogs pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:3361: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos rim
NK072(nu)002:3362: gyi bdag nyid du bzhugs pas rgya mtsho rlabs bzhin
NK072(nu)002:3363: sprul pa rang la 'char bas ga la brdo ste
NK072(nu)002:3364: / kun tu 'od ni bsti gnas kyi sa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3365: de ni 'dir lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dngos so //
NK072(nu)002:3367: gnyis pa gzhan don mdzad pa la /
NK072(nu)002:3368: gdul bya la thugs rjes gzigs tshul /
NK072(nu)002:3369: gzigs nas thugs rje skye tshul /
NK072(nu)002:3370: skyes nas 'gro don mdzad tshul lo //
NK072(nu)002:3372: ye shes rgyun chad nas mi gzigs par 'dod pa'i
NK072(nu)002:3373: lugs dang rgyun dang bcas te gzigs par 'dod pa'i
NK072(nu)002:3374: lugs dang mtha' gnyis dang bral bas /
NK072(nu)002:3375: yul med rang gsal du gzigs par 'dod pa'i lugs so //
NK072(nu)002:3380: spyir sangs rgyas la mtshan nyid pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3382: mtshan nyid la ni chos sku ste /
NK072(nu)002:3383: dper na bsreg bya zad pa'i sreg byed me'i rgyun mi gnas pa ltar /
NK072(nu)002:3384: sgrib pa phra rag pa thams cad spangs pa'i shul du /
NK072(nu)002:3385: spong byed gnyen po'i ye shes kyang dbyings su zhi ste /
NK072(nu)002:3386: rten dang brten pa'i ye shes rgyun chad pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:3387: gzigs bya gzigs byed kyi tha snyad las grol bas
NK072(nu)002:3388: mi gzigs la / btags pa ba gzugs sku gnyis
NK072(nu)002:3389: ni sngon gyi bsod nams kyi tshogs mi 'gag pa'i
NK072(nu)002:3390: 'bras bu'am smon lam gyi 'phen pa tsam gyis gdul
NK072(nu)002:3391: bya la snang ba'o zer ro //
NK072(nu)002:3393: de ltar na ye shes de nyid rang ldog nas chad dam /
NK072(nu)002:3394: gnyen po gzhan zhig gis chad /
NK072(nu)002:3396: sangs rgyas kyi sa nas sems can gyi don la
NK072(nu)002:3397: gzigs pa 'jug pa'i ji lta ba dang ji snyed
NK072(nu)002:3398: mkhyen pa'i ye shes med par thal /
NK072(nu)002:3399: ye shes rgyun chad pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3402: thun mong gi lung las kyang /
NK072(nu)002:3403: ji lta ji snyed nang gi ni //
NK072(nu)002:3404: ye shes gzigs pa 'jug pa'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:3407: ye shes med na byang chub 'phel med 'grib pa med //
NK072(nu)002:3408: rgya mtsho 'dra ba'i sangs rgyas chos kyang med par 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:3409: zhes sogs lung du mas gnod do //
NK072(nu)002:3411: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi gnyen po
NK072(nu)002:3412: des rgyun bcad dam gzhan zhig gis bcad ha cang
NK072(nu)002:3413: thal bas bag yod par mdzod cig /
NK072(nu)002:3418: sangs rgyas kyi sa na rdo rje lta bu'i ting
NK072(nu)002:3419: nge 'dzin gyis sgrib pa spangs pa'i lag rjes su
NK072(nu)002:3420: ye shes rgyun dang bcas pa yod de /
NK072(nu)002:3421: de las kyang kun rdzob mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis yul dang yul can du gzigs te /
NK072(nu)002:3422: sngar rgyun chad pa bkag pa'i lung gis grub bo zer /
NK072(nu)002:3425: sangs rgyas pa'i ye shes de nyid 'khrul shes su thal /
NK072(nu)002:3426: kun rdzob yul du byed pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3427: so skye'i shes pa bzhin no byas pa la /
NK072(nu)002:3428: kho na re snang tsam yul du byed kyang zhen yul du mi 'dzin pas so zer /
NK072(nu)002:3429: 'o na sangs rgyas pa'i ye shes de spangs pa phyogs gcig pa thal /
NK072(nu)002:3430: zhen yul la 'khrul pa'i log shes spangs kyang /
NK072(nu)002:3431: snang yul la 'khrul pa'i log shes ma spangs pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3434: ye shes dam pa bdag med pas //
NK072(nu)002:3435: snang ba med pas ma gzigs so //
NK072(nu)002:3438: dngos dang rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:3440: ye shes rgyun chad ces bkur pa mi 'debs /
NK072(nu)002:3442: de gnyis char gyi mtha' dang bral ba'i ngo bo
NK072(nu)002:3443: nyid kyi tshul gyis rtog med rang gsal du gzigs
NK072(nu)002:3445: stong nyid bdag med ye mkhyen rang rig thugs //
NK072(nu)002:3446: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par dran dbang bsgyur //
NK072(nu)002:3449: mya ngan 'das pa'i chos la chos med de //
NK072(nu)002:3450: gang phyir de med nam yang med mi 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:3451: rtogs can dag ni yod dang med ces bya //
NK072(nu)002:3452: de ltar brtags pas sdug bsngal zhi mi 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:3455: yul yod med dbyer med kyi brtags pa gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:3456: yul du byas nas gzigs na /
NK072(nu)002:3457: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes gzugs 'dzin can du gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:3458: yul dang yul can 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3460: rgyud dag pa ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:3463: yang yul du ma byas par gzigs na /
NK072(nu)002:3464: mig gis kyang sgra thos par thal /
NK072(nu)002:3467: gzhan yang sangs rgyas nyid 'khrul par thal /
NK072(nu)002:3469: mig ser can gyi dung gi kha dog bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:3470: dbyer med du gzigs zer ba'ang mi 'thad de /
NK072(nu)002:3471: gzigs bya gzigs byed du 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3472: mig gis mig bzhin no zer /
NK072(nu)002:3474: rje sgro phug pa'i zhal nas /
NK072(nu)002:3476: yul yod med kyi sgro bskur spangs nas chos thams
NK072(nu)002:3477: cad me long nang gi gzugs brnyan ltar rtog med
NK072(nu)002:3480: rnam rtog mi mnga' cir yang sal le mkhyen //
NK072(nu)002:3483: yul du byas nas kyang gzigs te /
NK072(nu)002:3484: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos dang sems las byung
NK072(nu)002:3485: ba thams cad lag mthil du skyu ru ra bzhag
NK072(nu)002:3486: pa bzhin du gsal mkhyen ma 'gags par snang ba'i
NK072(nu)002:3487: phyir / yang yul med du'ang gzigs te /
NK072(nu)002:3488: ji ltar snang yang bden pa'i ngo bos stongs pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3490: shes bya'i gshis la thugs rje skye ba'i yul sems can dang /
NK072(nu)002:3491: skye mkhan rnam mkhyen gyi sangs rgyas gnyis dmigs su med pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3492: de thugs rjer cir 'gyur zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:3493: de ni dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje ste /
NK072(nu)002:3494: sdug bsngal mtha' dag las skyob pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK072(nu)002:3495: 'o na thugs rjes gang la gang ltar gzugs te /
NK072(nu)002:3496: gzugs pa'i tha snyad mi 'thad do zer na /
NK072(nu)002:3498: 'khrul pa can gyi blo ngo na snang ba ltar
NK072(nu)002:3499: ma 'gags par gzigs pas skyon gnyis pa med cing
NK072(nu)002:3500: / ji ltar snang yang gshis la ma grub par mkhyen pas skyon dang po las grol lo //
NK072(nu)002:3501: de gnyis pos rtsod pa gsum pa'ang zhor la khegs te /
NK072(nu)002:3502: gshis la gdul bya 'dul byed dbyer med du gzigs la /
NK072(nu)002:3503: de ltar ma rtogs pa rnams 'khor ba'i chu bo
NK072(nu)002:3504: bzhis rgyun phyogs su khyer bas sdug bsngal ba'ang gzigs
NK072(nu)002:3505: shing de las grol ba'i thabs kyang mkhyen nas ston
NK072(nu)002:3507: dper na skyes bu mngon shes can gcig gi drung na /
NK072(nu)002:3508: skyes bu gzhan zhig gnyid du song ba'i rmi lam
NK072(nu)002:3509: du sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba rmi ba na
NK072(nu)002:3510: / mngon shes mkhan des mkhyen na'ang rang rgyud la bden zhen mi 'byung zhing /
NK072(nu)002:3511: gnyid sad na sdug bsngal de las grol ba yang mkhyen pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:3512: 'dir yang gzigs lugs rje sgro phug pa'i dgongs pas gsum ste /
NK072(nu)002:3513: dbyings las mi gzhan pa'am ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i
NK072(nu)002:3514: ye shes gzigs tshul dbyings ye shes dbyer med dam
NK072(nu)002:3515: ji lta ji snyed dbyer med du mkhyen pa'i ye
NK072(nu)002:3516: shes kyis gzigs tshul gsum du bzhed de /
NK072(nu)002:3517: gnyis pa gzigs nas thugs rje skye tshul ni /
NK072(nu)002:3519: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs gsol dang //
NK072(nu)002:3520: yul dang 'phrad nas byung bar snang //
NK072(nu)002:3522: rtag pa rgyun gyi thugs rje chu bo'i rgyun lta bu dang /
NK072(nu)002:3523: rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje nyi ma dang 'od zer lta bu dang /
NK072(nu)002:3524: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'i thugs rje snying rje can la dbul pos slong ba lta bu dang /
NK072(nu)002:3525: yul dang 'phrad pa'i thugs rje 'dzangs pa spyod log byed pa lta bu'o //
NK072(nu)002:3526: gsum pa skyes nas 'gro don mdzad tshul la /
NK072(nu)002:3527: rten can gyis don byed par 'dod pa /
NK072(nu)002:3528: rten med kyis don byed par 'dod pa /
NK072(nu)002:3529: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyis don byed par 'dod pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3531: bram ze mchod sdong sgrub pa lta bu ste /
NK072(nu)002:3532: dper na rigs sngags grub pa'i bram ze zhig gis
NK072(nu)002:3533: rin po che'i mchod sdong bsgrubs nas bzhag pas rang
NK072(nu)002:3534: nyid tshe'i dus byas kyang rjes 'jug rnams kyi 'dod
NK072(nu)002:3535: pa mchod sdong gis skong bar byed pa ltar /
NK072(nu)002:3536: sngon lam du tshogs bsags pa'i 'bras bu mthar thug
NK072(nu)002:3537: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa chos sku sgrib bral gyi
NK072(nu)002:3538: ye shes de nyid la brten nas /
NK072(nu)002:3539: gdul bya las dag pa la mdzad pa gzugs sku
NK072(nu)002:3540: gnyis su snang nas don mdzad par bzhed ba ni
NK072(nu)002:3541: / rgya gar na slob dpon seng ge bzang po dang /
NK072(nu)002:3542: bod na 'bring mtshams kyi zhang shes rab bla ma la sogs pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3544: drang srong dmod pa grub pa lta bu ste /
NK072(nu)002:3545: dper na dmod pa grub pa'i drang srong gis dmod
NK072(nu)002:3546: pa bsgrubs nas bzhag pas rang tshe'i dus byas kyang
NK072(nu)002:3547: gzhan snang du kho'i dmod pa ji lta bar 'byung
NK072(nu)002:3548: ba bzhin mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa na chos
NK072(nu)002:3549: kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa tsam las rang rgyud
NK072(nu)002:3550: kyis bsdus pa'i ye shes ma grub kyang sngon lam
NK072(nu)002:3551: du tshogs bsags zhing smon lam btab pa'i mthus gdul
NK072(nu)002:3552: bya rang gi blo snang du gzugs sku gnyis su
NK072(nu)002:3553: snang nas don byed par bzhed pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:3554: rgya gar na slob dpon klu sgrub dang /
NK072(nu)002:3555: bod na rong zom chos kyi bzang po'i dgongs pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3557: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bu ste /
NK072(nu)002:3558: dper na nor bu rin po che byas shing mchod
NK072(nu)002:3559: na rang rang gi bsod nams dang mtshams pa'i dgos
NK072(nu)002:3561: 'on kyang rin po che la rtsol rtog dang nye ring med pa ltar /
NK072(nu)002:3562: mthar thug rgyal ba'i dgongs pa yod med kyi mtha' las grol ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3563: mtha'i sgro bskur dang bral ba'i ngo bo nyid kyi
NK072(nu)002:3564: sku de nyid gdul bya'i blo dang mtshams par sna
NK072(nu)002:3565: tshogs su snang nas don mdzad par bzhed pa ni
NK072(nu)002:3566: rgya'i mkhas pa chen po sh+r+ai sed+ha dang /
NK072(nu)002:3567: bod na zur chung shes rab grags pa la sogs pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3569: thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK072(nu)002:3570: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
