NK072(nu)002:3571: 'gro ba'i phrin las bsam mi khyab //
NK072(nu)002:3572: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang //
NK072(nu)002:3573: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyi //
NK072(nu)002:3574: gdul bya rnams ni chud ma zos //
NK072(nu)002:3575: ngan song sbyong zhing byang chub zhing //
NK072(nu)002:3576: ye shes tshogs rdzogs kun tu ston //
NK072(nu)002:3579: gnyis pa lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bcu bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:3580: lta ba spyod pa dkyil 'khor dbang //
NK072(nu)002:3581: dam tshig phrin las sgrub pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:3582: ting 'dzin mchod pa sngags phyag rgya //
NK072(nu)002:3583: phyi ma gnyis sdoms bcu ru 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:3585: dang po de kho na nyid lta ba la /
NK072(nu)002:3589: rnam grangs ma rtogs pa'i skyon /
NK072(nu)002:3590: rtogs pa'i yon tan dang drug /
NK072(nu)002:3593: gzhan pa'i lta dmigs gsal ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:3594: mchog gi spyan rab mngon bya'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:3596: don du gnyer ba'i dgos pa gnyis /
NK072(nu)002:3599: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK072(nu)002:3600: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK072(nu)002:3602: mu stegs phyal pa dang rgyang 'phen /
NK072(nu)002:3603: log par rtogs pa mu stegs rtag chad gnyis /
NK072(nu)002:3605: yang dag nyid ma rtogs pa dbu sems gnyis kyi lta ba sel lo //
NK072(nu)002:3607: chos nyid yang dag par rtogs pa'i dgos pa /
NK072(nu)002:3608: las gang la spyad kyang mi 'ching ba'i dgos pa /
NK072(nu)002:3609: sangs rgyas nyid thob pa'i dngos rgyur gyur pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3610: dang po ni rgyas pa las /
NK072(nu)002:3611: chos kyi rang bzhin ji lta bu //
NK072(nu)002:3612: bdag gis yang dag rtogs par bya //
NK072(nu)002:3616: thabs dang shes rab rtogs pa yis //
NK072(nu)002:3617: dug gsum dug lngas gnod mi 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:3620: de las rang rig ye shes don rtogs na //
NK072(nu)002:3621: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung thob //
NK072(nu)002:3623: de yang dbu sems gnyis kyis yang dag nyid ma rtogs pa'i tshul cung zad brjod na /
NK072(nu)002:3624: de la sems tsam pa dang dbu ma pa'i lugs gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:3626: dkar dmar sna tshogs su snang ba shes pa dang
NK072(nu)002:3627: bcas pa 'di thams cad rang gi sems kyi rnam
NK072(nu)002:3628: par bden par 'dod pa sems tsam rnam bden pa
NK072(nu)002:3629: dang / shes pa'i rnam par rdzun par 'dod pa sems tsam rnam brdzun pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:3631: don du snang ba rang gi shes pa'i rnam pa phyir shar ba tsam ste /
NK072(nu)002:3633: rdzing 'gram gyi nor bu'i shing gi yal ga la
NK072(nu)002:3634: btag pa'i nor bu ke ke ru'i gzugs brnyan chu
NK072(nu)002:3635: nang du shar ba na nor bu'i rnam pa phyi
NK072(nu)002:3636: rol du shar ba bzhin no zhes 'dod do //
NK072(nu)002:3638: rnam pa'i grangs de snyed la shis pa'i grangs kyang de snyed du 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3639: rnam pa dang shes pa sgo nga bkas pa ltar 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3640: rnam pa dang shes pa sna tshogs gnyis med du 'dod pa gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:3642: sgra thos pa'i dus na sgra 'dzin gyi shes pa gcig tu skye yi /
NK072(nu)002:3643: gzugs la sogs pa 'dzin pa'i shes pa mi skye bar ltar /
NK072(nu)002:3644: yul gang la 'jug pa de'i shes pa skye yi gzhan mi skye bas /
NK072(nu)002:3645: rnam pa'i grangs ji snyed pa'i shes pa 'dod pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3647: phyi rol sna tshogs su snang ba'ang shes pa las byung la /
NK072(nu)002:3648: de 'dzin pa'i shes pa'ang sems las byung bas /
NK072(nu)002:3649: sgo nga bkas pa ltar rnam pa dang shes pa yul yul can sems gcig la shar ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:3650: de lta yul 'dzin pa na phyi rnam pa'i shes
NK072(nu)002:3651: pa gcig pa nang 'dzin byed kyi shes pa gcig
NK072(nu)002:3652: shar ba yang / thog ma med pa'i bag chags kyis de ltar gnyis su snang yang /
NK072(nu)002:3653: rang rig pa gcig pu las gzhan du grub pa med pas sgo nga bkas pa lta bu'o //
NK072(nu)002:3654: 'o na phyi rnam pa'i shes pa gcig la de'i
NK072(nu)002:3655: tshe 'dzin pa'i shes pa gcig byung dus rtog pa
NK072(nu)002:3656: gnyis cig char 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:3658: rnam pa'i shes pa de rtog med yin pa'i phyir ro zhes 'dod do //
NK072(nu)002:3660: phyi yul gyi rnam pa sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK072(nu)002:3661: nang 'dzin byed kyi shes pa gcig gis shes te /
NK072(nu)002:3662: mkhar gyi nang du spre'u gcig 'jug pa myur bas
NK072(nu)002:3663: glo skar bzhir ske rib rib byung nas lta ba
NK072(nu)002:3664: ltar / sgo lnga la shes pa gcig gis zhugs nas yul rig pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3667: shes pa gnyis ka sems gcig gi rang bzhin du tha mi dad de /
NK072(nu)002:3668: rmi lam gyi snang ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:3669: 'dzin byed rang du snang ba gnyis ka yang gnyid
NK072(nu)002:3670: gcig gi shes par tha mi dad pa bzhin no
NK072(nu)002:3671: zhes 'dod do // gnyis pa rnam rdzun pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:3672: phyi don gyi rnam par shes pa la 'khrul par snang ba'i bag chags rdzun pa ba yin gyi /
NK072(nu)002:3673: shes par bden pa ma yin la /
NK072(nu)002:3674: de 'jal byed kyi shes pa yang rdzun pa bas gzhal gyi /
NK072(nu)002:3675: myong ba bden pa bas gzhal ba ni med do //
NK072(nu)002:3676: yul shes gnyis ka yang 'khrul snang rdzun pa ba'i rang bzhin tsam du 'dod do //
NK072(nu)002:3678: dri bcas dag pa bar 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3679: dri med dag pa bar 'dod pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:3681: da lta'i rnam pa sna tshogs su snang ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:3682: de 'jal ba'i shes pa gnyis ka blo'i dri ma nyid snang tsam las /
NK072(nu)002:3683: don dam par gnyis su med pa'i ye shes khams
NK072(nu)002:3684: kyi yon tan dang bcas pa tsam zhig yod kyi
NK072(nu)002:3685: / rnam shes su grub pa ni ci yang med do //
NK072(nu)002:3686: sangs rgyas kyi chos sku lhag ma med pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:3687: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:3688: dri ma med pa'i de bzhin nyid yin la /
NK072(nu)002:3689: lhag bcas kyi gnas skabs na bag la nyal gyi dri ma cung zad yod pas /
NK072(nu)002:3692: ro rgyab snyung ba la sogs pa yod do //
NK072(nu)002:3694: da lta sems la nyon mongs pa dang ye shes
NK072(nu)002:3695: 'dres par gnas pa'i dri ma nyon mongs pa'i cha
NK072(nu)002:3697: lhag ma med pa'i ye shes dag pa mngon du byed pa'o zhes 'dod do //
NK072(nu)002:3698: dag pa ni rnam pa dang rnam shes brdzun pa tsam du'ang grub pa med do //
NK072(nu)002:3699: mngon par chags pa dag gis na chung yid la byed pa goms pa las /
NK072(nu)002:3700: ji zhig na bsam ma dgos par /
NK072(nu)002:3701: de'i byad bzhin gyi snang ba med pa gsal snang du shar ba bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:3702: des na yul gyi rnam pa dkar dmar sna tshogs su snang ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:3703: 'jal byed kyi blo gnyis ka med bzhin snang ba gzugs brnyan lta bu ste /
NK072(nu)002:3704: de'i don nyams su myong ba'i so so rang gi
NK072(nu)002:3705: rig pa'i ye shes tsam zhig don dam par yod
NK072(nu)002:3707: gnyis pa dbu ma pa la /
NK072(nu)002:3711: 'di ltar sna tshogs su snang ba'i rnam pa dang 'jal byed med pa gsal snang tsam du zad /
NK072(nu)002:3712: don dam par so so rang gi rig pa'i ye
NK072(nu)002:3713: shes de yang rang bzhin gyis ngo bo nyid med
NK072(nu)002:3716: sgyu ma don dam du 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3717: rab tu mi gnas pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:3719: yul yul can du grub pa med la /
NK072(nu)002:3720: ma grub pa rig pa'i ye shes smra bsam brjod
NK072(nu)002:3721: med tsam zhig don dam par sgyu ma'i tshul du
NK072(nu)002:3722: yod pas / sgoms pa'i yon tan pa lam dang /
NK072(nu)002:3723: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK072(nu)002:3724: sgyu ma lta bu thob nas chos kyi sku'i ngang
NK072(nu)002:3725: nas / sgyu ma lta bus don mdzad pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:3727: chos thams cad rmi lam lta bu /
NK072(nu)002:3729: mya ngan las 'das kyang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK072(nu)002:3730: mya ngan las 'das pa bas chos lhag ma'i chos shig yod de /
NK072(nu)002:3731: de yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu //
NK072(nu)002:3733: chos thams cad ni yul shes sna tshogs pa thams cad do //
NK072(nu)002:3734: mya ngan las 'das pa ni gzugs sku brnyes nas don mdzad pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3735: de nas lhag pa'i chos ni so so rang gi rig pa'i de bzhin nyid dang /
NK072(nu)002:3736: chos sku dam pa'o zhes 'dod do //
NK072(nu)002:3737: 'di la'ang sgyu ma rigs drug du 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3738: sgyu ma ltar snang du 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3739: sgyu ma tsam so sor 'dod pa la sogs pa rnam grangs rab tu mang ste /
NK072(nu)002:3740: rang rgyud 'og ma pa zhes grags pa yin no //
NK072(nu)002:3742: don dam par sgyu ma tsam du'ang mi gnas te /
NK072(nu)002:3743: yul dang rnam pa med pas de med par myong ba'i so so rang rig kyang med pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:3744: mo sham gyi bu med pas de 'jal byed kyi shes pa med pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:3745: kun rdzob la bden par med pas /
NK072(nu)002:3746: don dam la gang yang mi gnas te /
NK072(nu)002:3747: rmi lam sad pa'i dus na /
NK072(nu)002:3748: rta glang gi rnam pa 'gags kyang /
NK072(nu)002:3749: dang po nas med pas don la 'gags rgyur ma grub pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:3751: don dam par ni 'khor ba yang med /
NK072(nu)002:3752: mya ngan las 'das pa yang med /
NK072(nu)002:3753: stong pa nyid kyang med de /
NK072(nu)002:3754: tshig gi bla dwags tsam du bas lags so //
NK072(nu)002:3755: zhes gsungs pa lta bu'o zhes 'dod do //
NK072(nu)002:3756: 'di la kun rdzob rab tu mi gnas pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3757: rgyu mtshan mi gnas pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3758: ldog cha mi gnas pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3759: ldog byed mi gnas pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3761: du ma mi gnas pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3762: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba mi gnas pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3763: snang tsam rab tu mi gnas pa la sogs pa rnam grangs dpag tu med pa yod de /
NK072(nu)002:3764: dbu ma rang rgyud gong ma pa zhes grags so //
NK072(nu)002:3766: de ltar don dam par ma grub pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3767: kun rdzob tu snang tsam sgyu mar grub pa la sogs pa thams cad bkag nas /
NK072(nu)002:3768: yod med kyi mtha' las 'das pa'i rang bzhin khas len thams cad dang bral bar 'dod de /
NK072(nu)002:3769: 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyal po las /
NK072(nu)002:3770: rtag dang mi rtag 'di yang mtha' yin te //
NK072(nu)002:3771: yod dang med ces bya ba gnyis ka mtha' //
NK072(nu)002:3772: de phyir gnyis ka'i mtha' ni rnam spangs nas //
NK072(nu)002:3773: mkhas pas dbus la'ang gnas par mi byed do //
NK072(nu)002:3775: dkon cog ta la'i mdo las /
NK072(nu)002:3776: de bzhin gshegs pa rtag tu skye med chos //
NK072(nu)002:3777: chos rnams thams cad bde bar gshegs dang 'dra //
NK072(nu)002:3778: byis pa'i blo can mtshan mar 'dzin pas na //
NK072(nu)002:3779: 'jig rten dag na med pa'i chos la spyod //
NK072(nu)002:3783: 'gag pa med pas skye med pa //
NK072(nu)002:3784: chad pa med pas rtag med pa //
NK072(nu)002:3785: tha dad don min don gcig min //
NK072(nu)002:3786: spros pa nyer zhi zhir bstan pa //
NK072(nu)002:3787: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas smra rnams kyis //
NK072(nu)002:3788: dam pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK072(nu)002:3791: gal te ngas dam bca' 'ga' yod //
NK072(nu)002:3792: de tshe nga la skyon 'di yod //
NK072(nu)002:3793: nga la dam bca' med pas na //
NK072(nu)002:3794: nga ni skyon med kho na yin //
NK072(nu)002:3795: zhes sogs kyis blos bkod pa'i grub mtha' gang yang med de spros pa zhi ba'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:3797: sna tshogs su snang tsam 'jig rten pa ji ltar
NK072(nu)002:3798: 'jog pa ltar brda' shes pa'i yan lag tu bzhag
NK072(nu)002:3799: kyang / de yang khas len med pas chos su
NK072(nu)002:3800: snang ba bden rdzun las 'das pa yod med kyi
NK072(nu)002:3801: mtha' dang da lta'i dus nas bral bar 'dod do
NK072(nu)002:3802: kyang / // 'di ni dbu ma'i lta ba mthar
NK072(nu)002:3803: thug yin pa klu sgrub zhabs kyi dgongs pa thun
NK072(nu)002:3804: mong ma yin pa'ang 'di yin te 'di'i don gtan
NK072(nu)002:3805: la 'bebs bya'i gzhung chen po dbu ma'i rigs pa'i
NK072(nu)002:3806: kyang / // tshogs drug ste / rtsa ba shes rab /
NK072(nu)002:3811: tha snyad bsgrub pa rnams so //
NK072(nu)002:3813: gzhan stong gi tshul 'dzin pa'i dbu ma pa mang dag byung ste /
NK072(nu)002:3816: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK072(nu)002:3817: bsnan par bya ba'ang cung zad med //
NK072(nu)002:3818: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK072(nu)002:3819: yang dag mthong nas rnam par grol //
NK072(nu)002:3820: rnam dbyer bcas pa'i mtshan nyid can //
NK072(nu)002:3821: blo bur dag gi khams stong gi //
NK072(nu)002:3822: rnam dbyer med pa'i mtshan nyid can //
NK072(nu)002:3823: bla med chos kyis stong ma yin //
NK072(nu)002:3827: gang gi phyir rang bzhin gyis yongs su dag pa
NK072(nu)002:3828: de bzhin gshegs pa'i khams 'di la bsal bar bya
NK072(nu)002:3829: ba kun nas nyon mongs pa'i rgyu mtshan ni 'ga'
NK072(nu)002:3830: yang med de / glo bur gyi dri ma dang
NK072(nu)002:3831: bral ba ni 'di'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro
NK072(nu)002:3832: yang med de / / 'di la rnam par byang
NK072(nu)002:3833: ba'i rgyu mtshan gyis bsnan par bya ba'ang cung zad
NK072(nu)002:3835: rnam par dbye ba med pa'i chos dag pa'i chos nyid ni rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:3836: des na de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ni rnam par dbye ba yod pa dang bral ba /
NK072(nu)002:3837: shes pa nyon mongs pa'i sbub thams cad kyis ni stong pa yin la /
NK072(nu)002:3838: rnam par dbye ba med pa bral mi shes pa
NK072(nu)002:3839: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sangs rgyas kyi chos gang+ga'i
NK072(nu)002:3840: klung gi bye ma snyed las 'das pa ni mi
NK072(nu)002:3843: chos can ji ltar snang ba 'di dag snang tsam
NK072(nu)002:3844: nyid nas rang rang gi ngo bos stong bas med
NK072(nu)002:3845: dgag gi stong nyid don dam par bzhed cing /
NK072(nu)002:3846: ngo bo nyid med par smra ba'i dbu ma pa la don dam du tha dad med kyang /
NK072(nu)002:3847: kun rdzob tu grub pa sgyu ma lta bu zhes rang rgyud kyi dam bca' 'god pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3848: thal 'gyur kho na 'phen pas khas len pa'i kun rdzob tsam yang 'gog pa'i srol gnyis snang ngo //
NK072(nu)002:3849: gzhan stong du gtan la 'bebs pa'i dbu ma pa rnams la /
NK072(nu)002:3850: shes bya thams cad mtshan nyid gsum du 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3851: kun btags dang yongs grub gnyis su bsdu ba'i khyad par las /
NK072(nu)002:3852: chos can dngos 'dzin tshul mi 'dra ba gnyis byung ste /
NK072(nu)002:3854: stong gzhi gzhan dbang dgag bya kun btags kyis stong pa'i yongs grub tu bshad pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3855: rgyud bla ma sogs las chos nyid yongs grub dgag bya kun btags kyis stong par gsungs so //
NK072(nu)002:3856: des na yongs grub sems kyi chos nyid don dam
NK072(nu)002:3857: pa'i dbyings 'di'i ngo bo la dor bya'i dri ma
NK072(nu)002:3858: dang sngar med kyis yon tan gsar du sgrub tu
NK072(nu)002:3859: med de / ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing yon tan lhun grub yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3860: skyon yon grub bsal las 'das pas don dam gyi
NK072(nu)002:3861: dbyings de kho rang gi ngo bos stong pa yin
NK072(nu)002:3862: / blo bur 'khrul snang gi chos bzung 'dzin spros
NK072(nu)002:3863: pa'i cha rnams gshis la ma grub pas kun rdzob
NK072(nu)002:3864: rang gis ngo bos stong pa yin la /
NK072(nu)002:3865: de 'dra de don dam chos nyid las gzhan yin pas /
NK072(nu)002:3866: don dam gzhan gyi ngo bos stong pa zhes pa'i don no //
NK072(nu)002:3867: mdor na kun rdzob kyi phyogs nas gzhal na med dgag dang ma yin dgag gi stong nyid /
NK072(nu)002:3868: don dam dbyings kyi phyogs nas gzhal na rang las gzhan rtog pa'i yul gyi stong pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:3869: 'o na don dam rang gi ngo bos stong pa ltar gsungs pa'i dgos pa gang snyam na /
NK072(nu)002:3870: don dam la dmigs nas blos bzung ba ltar ma grub pa la dgongs pa yin no //
NK072(nu)002:3871: de ltar thos bsam gyis gtan la phab nas sgom pas nyams su myong ba'i lta ba la /
NK072(nu)002:3872: 'khor lor bar pa'i dngos bstan rigs tshogs su bkral ba ltar na /
NK072(nu)002:3873: nges don med dgag la bzhed pas /
NK072(nu)002:3874: ci yang mi sgom pa la stong nyid sgom pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3875: ci yang ma mthong ba la de kho na nyid rtogs par 'chad /
NK072(nu)002:3876: 'khor lo tha ma'i dgongs pa byams chos kyi gzhung
NK072(nu)002:3877: thogs med sku mched kyis bkral ba dang klu sgrub
NK072(nu)002:3879: gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi ye shes nyid sgoms pas nyams su myong bar byed cing /
NK072(nu)002:3880: de nyid gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde zab mo rnams dang yang dgongs pa mthun pa yin no //
NK072(nu)002:3881: de yang sngon gyi mkhas grub rnams kyis zung 'brel du nyams su bzhes pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:3882: so skye'i bar lta ba thos bsam gyi gtan la 'bebs pa'i tshe blo'i mtshan 'dzin gzhig dka' bas /
NK072(nu)002:3883: de thos bsam las byung ba'i shes rab kyis 'gog
NK072(nu)002:3884: par byed pa la sgro 'dogs gcod byed kyi rig
NK072(nu)002:3885: pa thal 'gyur pa rno ba'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:3886: yang sgom byung nyams myong gis gtan la 'beb pa'i
NK072(nu)002:3887: skabs su 'khor lo tha mar gsungs pa'i dbu ma'i
NK072(nu)002:3888: lta ba de nyid zab cing ches bzang ba yin
NK072(nu)002:3889: te / dbyiings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa
NK072(nu)002:3890: don dam pa'i bden pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK072(nu)002:3891: de nyid chos thams cad kyi gdod ma'i gnas lugs
NK072(nu)002:3893: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde zab mo rnams nas bshad
NK072(nu)002:3894: pa'i lta ba'i nyams len dang yang mthun pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:3896: des na shing rta'i srol 'byed pa po ni /
NK072(nu)002:3897: byams mgon dang slob dpon klu sgrub gnyis yin te /
NK072(nu)002:3898: dgongs 'grel mdzad pa po gzhan dag 'di gnyis kyi bstan bcos la brten nas 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:3899: de yang klu sgrub zhabs kyis 'khor lo bar pa'i
NK072(nu)002:3900: dgongs 'grel du chos thams cad rang stong gtan la
NK072(nu)002:3901: 'bebs byed dbu ma rig tshogs sogs dang /
NK072(nu)002:3902: 'khor lo tha ma'i dgongs 'grel gzhan stong gtan la
NK072(nu)002:3903: 'bebs byed bstod tshogs sogs kyis bka'i dgongs pa legs
NK072(nu)002:3904: par bkral zhing de dang de'i srol 'dzin rim bzhin
NK072(nu)002:3905: ngo bo nyid med par smra ba'i thal rang gi
NK072(nu)002:3907: 'jigs med chos skyong zhabs yin la /
NK072(nu)002:3908: rgyal tshab mi pham mgon gyis gzhan stong du gtan
NK072(nu)002:3909: la 'bebs pa'i bstan bcos byams chos sde lnga mdzad
NK072(nu)002:3910: de 'phags pa thogs med la bstan pa sku mched
NK072(nu)002:3911: gnyis kyis legs par bkral ba'i srol de nyid phyogs
NK072(nu)002:3912: glang chos grags dang tsan+d+ra go mi la sogs pas
NK072(nu)002:3913: bzung zhing / srol 'byed kyi slob dpon de gnyis
NK072(nu)002:3914: ka'ang dbu ma pa chen po nges don 'chad pa
NK072(nu)002:3915: la 'khrul med nyid du rgyal bas lung bstan pa
NK072(nu)002:3916: bzung zhing / yin te / ji skad du /
NK072(nu)002:3917: dge slong dpal ldan zhes grags pa //
NK072(nu)002:3918: de ming klu zhes 'bod pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:3919: yod dang med pa'i phyogs 'jig byed //
NK072(nu)002:3920: nga yi theg pa 'jig rten du //
NK072(nu)002:3921: bla med theg par rab bsgrubs nas //
NK072(nu)002:3923: thogs med ces bya'i dge slong ni //
NK072(nu)002:3924: bstan bcos de yi don la mkhas //
NK072(nu)002:3925: mdo sde drangs don nges pa'i don //
NK072(nu)002:3926: rnam pa mang po rab tu 'byed //
NK072(nu)002:3928: rin chen 'byung gnas zhi ba'i zhabs kyis kyang //
NK072(nu)002:3929: klu sgrub dang thogs med rnam gnyis grub mtha' gcig tu bkral te /
NK072(nu)002:3930: des mdzad pa'i dbu ma rgyan las /
NK072(nu)002:3931: byams pa thogs med kyis gsungs shing //
NK072(nu)002:3932: klu sgrub kyang ni bzhed pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:3933: tshad ma lung dang ldan gyur pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:3934: bden pa gnyis po 'dir bshad bya //
NK072(nu)002:3936: zhi ba 'tsho la sogs pa rnams kyang dgongs pa phyogs mthun par snang ngo //
NK072(nu)002:3937: slob dpon de nyid dgongs pa mi gcig par bkral
NK072(nu)002:3938: ba sogs kyi lo rgyus sngon gyi yig rnying dag
NK072(nu)002:3939: dang gter chen bla ma yab sras kyi gsung gi
NK072(nu)002:3940: bdud rtsi las thos pa cud zad brjod na /
NK072(nu)002:3941: slob dpon sangs rgyas bskyangs dang /
NK072(nu)002:3942: slob dpon legs ldan pa gnyis byung ba de gnyis kyis /
NK072(nu)002:3943: klu sgrub kyi slob ma slob dpon klu'i bshes gnyen dang /
NK072(nu)002:3944: de'i slob ma slob dpon dge 'dun bsrung ba la
NK072(nu)002:3945: klu sgrub kyi gzhung lugs rnams thob par byas nas
NK072(nu)002:3946: bsgoms pas ye shes mchog brnyes /
NK072(nu)002:3948: phyi mas phyag rdor gyi zhal gzigs chos mang du bstan /
NK072(nu)002:3949: dbu ma rtsa ba'i gzhung la slob dpon snga ma'i
NK072(nu)002:3950: bzhed pa rnams sun phyungs te 'grel ba mdzad cing
NK072(nu)002:3951: / klu sgrub kyi man ngag la rten par zhal
NK072(nu)002:3952: gyis bzhes nas mdo sde 'ga' zhig la 'grel pa
NK072(nu)002:3953: / mdzad nas / dbu ma ngo bo nyid med
NK072(nu)002:3954: par smra ba'i gzhung gtsugs shing sangs rgyas ba skyangs
NK072(nu)002:3955: slob ma ha cang mang ba ma yin kyang /
NK072(nu)002:3956: legs ldan pa slob ma shin tu mang bas dge
NK072(nu)002:3957: slong stong phrag mang po rjes su 'brang ba yin
NK072(nu)002:3958: pas shin tu dar bar gyur ro //
NK072(nu)002:3959: slob dpon 'di gnyis ma byon gong du theg chen mtha' dag bstan pa yug gcig tu gnas shing /
NK072(nu)002:3960: slob dpon 'di nyid kyis klu sgrub dang thogs med gnyis shin tu tha dad de /
NK072(nu)002:3961: thogs med kyis ni dbu ma'i lam mi ston sems tsam kho na yin pas /
NK072(nu)002:3962: kho bo cag gi 'di las gzhan du med //
NK072(nu)002:3963: ces mtha' gzhan 'gog par mdzad pas /
NK072(nu)002:3964: slob dpon de gnyis sku 'das pa'i 'og tu theg
NK072(nu)002:3965: chen la'ang nang du sde gnyis su gyes te rtsod
NK072(nu)002:3966: pa chen po byung bar grags /
NK072(nu)002:3967: bod rnams sangs rgyas bskyangs klu sgrub kyi sku tshe'i stod kyi slob ma dang /
NK072(nu)002:3968: legs ldan pa sku tshe'i smad kyi slob ma yin pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:3969: rtsod pa byas pa skad dang /
NK072(nu)002:3970: sangs rgyas bskyangs zla grags su skye ba bzhes zer
NK072(nu)002:3971: ba sogs rig pas gras pa'i bcol gtam du zad
NK072(nu)002:3972: do // de'i rjes su dpal ldan zla ba grags
NK072(nu)002:3973: pa byon nas legs ldan gyi slob ma mang po
NK072(nu)002:3974: do // dang / sangs rgyas bskyangs kyi slob ma ka ma la bud+d+hi la /
NK072(nu)002:3975: klu sgrub kyi gzhung lugs dang man ngag thams cad nos /
NK072(nu)002:3976: mkhas pa chen por gyur nas dpal na lan+da'i mkhan po mdzad /
NK072(nu)002:3977: rtsa 'jug gzhi gsum dang rig pa drug cu pa la sogs pa'i 'grel pa mdzad /
NK072(nu)002:3978: sangs rgyas bskyangs kyi lugs de nyid cher dar bar mdzad /
NK072(nu)002:3979: ri mor bris pa'i ba las 'o ma dang rtsig
NK072(nu)002:3980: pa sogs la thogs med du bzhud pa sogs ngo
NK072(nu)002:3981: mtshar ba'i mdzad pa du ma ston cing /
NK072(nu)002:3982: mu stegs kyi rgol ba ngan pa rnams tshar bcad /
NK072(nu)002:3983: bram ze dang khyim bdag mang po bstan pa la
NK072(nu)002:3984: bcug nas chos gzhi chen po mang du btab par
NK072(nu)002:3985: grags so // de dang dus mnyam slob dpon tsan+da go ma byung ste /
NK072(nu)002:3986: spyan ras gzigs kyi zhal mthong ba'i mu stegs kyi
NK072(nu)002:3987: pan+di ta rgyang 'phen pa'i ston pa zhig dang rtsod
NK072(nu)002:3988: par gyur te / de'i ring lugs sun phyungs yang
NK072(nu)002:3989: rig pa ni blos rnam par btags pa yin pas
NK072(nu)002:3990: gang blo bsgrin pa de rgyal ba yin gyi /
NK072(nu)002:3991: skye ba snga phyi yod pa'i rtags mngon sum med pas kho bo cag mi 'dod zer ba na /
NK072(nu)002:3992: der yul gyi rgyal po la sogs pa dpang por bzhag ste /
NK072(nu)002:3993: nga nyid skye ba len pa yin pas dpral bar rtags thob gcig byas nas /
NK072(nu)002:3994: des dpral bar mtshal gyis thig le sha la thim pa gcig byas /
NK072(nu)002:3995: kha nang du mu tig gcig bcug nas de nyid du 'das te /
NK072(nu)002:3996: de'i lus zangs kha sbyor gyi nang du bcug nas rgyal pos rgyas btab bo //
NK072(nu)002:3997: de rgyal rigs kyi pan+di ta bi shwa sa ga zhes pa'i bur skye bar khas blangs pa bzhin /
NK072(nu)002:3998: de la khye'u mtshan dang ldan pa zhig btsas ma
NK072(nu)002:3999: thag tu mtshal gyi ri mo dpral bar yod pa
NK072(nu)002:4000: kha nang du mu tig yod pa de byung /
NK072(nu)002:4001: rgyal po sogs kyis sngar gyi phung po de bltas pas dpral ba'i mtshal gyi ri mo yang byi /
NK072(nu)002:4002: mu tig gi shul har re 'dug /
NK072(nu)002:4003: der mu stegs de yang skye ba lnga phyi yod pa'i yid ches skad /
NK072(nu)002:4004: khye'u de btsas ma thag tu ma la phyag byas
NK072(nu)002:4005: te zla ba bcur 'o ma brgyal lam byas pas
NK072(nu)002:4006: btsas ma thag smra ba ltas ngan no snyam nas
NK072(nu)002:4007: kha rog 'dug byas pas lo bdun bar cang ma
NK072(nu)002:4008: smras pas lkug pa'o snyam mo //
NK072(nu)002:4009: skabs der mu stegs kyi rgol ba shin tu go
NK072(nu)002:4010: dka' ba snyan dngags kyi tshigs bcad sangs rgyas pa
NK072(nu)002:4011: rnams kyi grub mtha' 'gog par byed pa gcig brtsams
NK072(nu)002:4012: nas rgyal po dang mkhas pa'i tshogs thams cad la
NK072(nu)002:4013: grims so // der bi shwa sa ga'i khyim du byung ba na /
NK072(nu)002:4014: don de yun ring brtag pas ma go bas lan gdab par ga la nus /
NK072(nu)002:4015: lan gcig bya ba gcig gi phyir khyim gyi phyi rol du song ba na /
NK072(nu)002:4016: der tsan+d+ra go mi lo bdun 'gro ba des bltas pa na /
NK072(nu)002:4017: don de shes par dka' ba med /
NK072(nu)002:4019: lan gyi tshigs bcad kyang bris so //
NK072(nu)002:4020: phas nang du 'ongs pa na de ltar bris pa mthong nas /
NK072(nu)002:4021: khyim du su byung zhes tsan+d+ra go mi'i ma la dris so //
NK072(nu)002:4022: gzhan du su yang ma 'ongs bu lkugs pas blta zhing bris so //
NK072(nu)002:4023: der phas bu la dris pa na ma'i gdong la blta zhing 'dug /
NK072(nu)002:4025: 'di ni bdag gis bris te rgol ba 'di zlog pa ni dka' ba ma yin no zhes zer /
NK072(nu)002:4026: de nas nang par tsan+d+ra go mi dang mu stegs
NK072(nu)002:4027: kyi ston pa de gnyis brtsod pas tsan+d+ra go mi
NK072(nu)002:4028: rgyal te bya dga' chen po thob /
NK072(nu)002:4029: phyogs thams cad du mkhas pa'i grags pas khyab bo //
NK072(nu)002:4030: de nas nam zhig gi tshe dpal na lan+d+rara byon pas /
NK072(nu)002:4031: de'i tshe mkhan por gyur pa zla ba grags pa yin pa dang 'jal nas /
NK072(nu)002:4036: bstod pa brgya lnga bcu pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4037: mtshan yang dag pa rjod pa gsum shes byas pas /
NK072(nu)002:4038: 'di gzhung gsum las mi shes zhes tshig khengs skyung yang /
NK072(nu)002:4039: don la thams cad shes par khas blangs pa yin pas tsan+d+ra go mi yin nam snyam dris pas /
NK072(nu)002:4041: de nas tsan+d+ra go mis thogs med kyi srol la
NK072(nu)002:4042: brten te rnam rig gi phyogs bzung zla grags kyis
NK072(nu)002:4043: klu sgrub kyi gzhung sangs rgyas bskyangs kyis bkral ba
NK072(nu)002:4044: la brten te ngo bo nyid med par smra ba'i
NK072(nu)002:4045: phyogs bzung / lo bdun gyi bar du bgro gleng gi brgal brtag mdzad de /
NK072(nu)002:4046: rtsod pa de blta ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4047: skye bo mang po rtag tu 'dus pa las /
NK072(nu)002:4048: grong pa'i khye'u dang bu mo tshun chad kyis kyang phyogs tsam rig nas /
NK072(nu)002:4049: kye ma 'phags pa klu sgrub gzhung //
NK072(nu)002:4050: la la'i sman la la la'i dug /
NK072(nu)002:4051: mi pham 'phags pa thogs med gzhung //
NK072(nu)002:4052: skye bo kun la bdud rtsir gyur //
NK072(nu)002:4053: ces glur len pa byung ngo //
NK072(nu)002:4055: 'di la rtsod pa slob mi zhig yod dam bsam nas //
NK072(nu)002:4056: tsan+d+ra go ma'i phyi bzhin byon pa na spyan ras gzigs kyi lha khang zhig yod par bzhud /
NK072(nu)002:4058: spyan ras gzigs kyi rdo sku des slob dpon gyi
NK072(nu)002:4059: slob ma la ston pa bzhin chos gsung gzigs pas
NK072(nu)002:4060: / 'phags pa la nye ring mi manga'am /
NK072(nu)002:4061: zhes sgo phye bas de nyid du rdo skur gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:4062: chos slob bzhin pa'i phyag rdor sor ke re lus pas spyan ras gzigs mdzub ker mar grags /
NK072(nu)002:4063: de skabs nas rtsod pa rang zhi'o zhes byung ngo //
NK072(nu)002:4064: de ltar rang stong dang gzhan stong gis grub pa'i
NK072(nu)002:4065: mtha' mi gcig pa du ma byung ba de dag
NK072(nu)002:4066: phyogs gcig dag la phyogs gcig ma dag ces bskur
NK072(nu)002:4067: pa gdab tu mi rung ste /
NK072(nu)002:4068: 'gro ba blo mtho dman la ltos nas de dang
NK072(nu)002:4069: de 'dul ba'i thabs su ston pa yin pa dang
NK072(nu)002:4070: / slob dpon de dag kyang 'phags pa kho nar zad pas /
NK072(nu)002:4071: byis pas 'phags pa'i spyod yul la sgro skur btab
NK072(nu)002:4072: par mi bya ste 'gro ba 'dul ba'i sangs rgyas
NK072(nu)002:4073: kyi phrin las pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:4074: de'ang nam mkha' dri ma med pa'i mdo las /
NK072(nu)002:4075: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'gro ba thams cad la dngos su snang ba'ang ma yin gyi /
NK072(nu)002:4076: dge ba'i gshes gnyen ni yongs su snang bas de
NK072(nu)002:4077: bzhin gshegs pa bas dge ba'i bshes gnyen lhag par
NK072(nu)002:4079: yon tan rin chen sdud pa las /
NK072(nu)002:4080: rgyal ba'i nyan thos pa dag ji snyed chos ston cing /
NK072(nu)002:4081: 'chad dang rig pa dag dang ldan par brjod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4082: mchog 'phags bde ba bskyed dang de yin 'bras thob pa /
NK072(nu)002:4083: de dag kun kyang de bzhin pa yi skyes bu'i mthu //
NK072(nu)002:4085: de yang nges pa'i don du ni 'di ltar yin te /
NK072(nu)002:4086: bka' 'khor lo dang por ni las dang po pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4087: dbang po dman pa rnams la dgongs nas bden bzhi
NK072(nu)002:4088: spang gnyen du bya bas 'khor ba las bzlog pa'i
NK072(nu)002:4089: phyir spangs bya las rnam par grol ba'i thabs so
NK072(nu)002:4090: // bar par yongs su sbyong ba byas pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4091: dbang po 'bring po la dgongs nas gnyen por 'dzin
NK072(nu)002:4092: pa'i 'chi ba las grol ba'i thabs su sgyu ma'i
NK072(nu)002:4093: dpe brgyad dang nam mkha' lta bu'i stong pa nyid
NK072(nu)002:4094: bstan to // tha mar mthar phyin pa dang dbang
NK072(nu)002:4095: po rnon po'i ngor shes bya'i gshis ji ltar gnas
NK072(nu)002:4096: pa de ltar gsungs pa yin no //
NK072(nu)002:4097: de la 'dir bka' tha ma nges pa don gyi
NK072(nu)002:4098: mdo sde sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsang ba chen
NK072(nu)002:4099: po ji lta ba bzhin mngon du ston pa ni
NK072(nu)002:4100: / 'phags pa gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK072(nu)002:4101: dpal phreng seng+ge'i nga ro sgras zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK072(nu)002:4102: bu mo rin chen gyis zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK072(nu)002:4103: lha mo dri ma med pas zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK072(nu)002:4104: mi'u thung sor phreng can gyi mdo dang /
NK072(nu)002:4105: 'phags pa yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK072(nu)002:4106: byams pas zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK072(nu)002:4107: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i mdo las sogs pa rnams yin te /
NK072(nu)002:4108: de dag las sems can thams cad ye nas gnas
NK072(nu)002:4109: pa'i chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i de
NK072(nu)002:4110: bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ste /
NK072(nu)002:4113: de'i snang cha las gzugs sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyi 'byung khungs dang /
NK072(nu)002:4114: stong cha las chos kyi sku spros pa'i mtha' thams
NK072(nu)002:4115: cad dang bral ba ye nas lhun grub tu gnas
NK072(nu)002:4116: pa nyid / yon tan lhun gyis pas nor bu dang /
NK072(nu)002:4117: gzhan du mi 'gyur bas nam mkha' dang /
NK072(nu)002:4118: sems can thams cad rlan zhing khyab pas chu dag pa'i dpes bstan te /
NK072(nu)002:4120: rin chen nam mkha' chu dag bzhin //
NK072(nu)002:4121: rtag tu rang bzhin nyon mongs med //
NK072(nu)002:4123: de nyid sems can thams cad la yod par rgyud bla ma las /
NK072(nu)002:4124: rdzogs sangs sku ni 'phro phyir dang //
NK072(nu)002:4125: de bzhin nyid dbyer med phyir dang //
NK072(nu)002:4126: rigs yod phyir na sems can kun //
NK072(nu)002:4127: rtag tu sangs rgyas snying po can //
NK072(nu)002:4130: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK072(nu)002:4131: 'on kyang blo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK072(nu)002:4132: de bsal na ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK072(nu)002:4134: de'ang sngar sems can pa'i dus na med pa'i yon
NK072(nu)002:4135: tan phyis gsar du bskyed par 'dod pa ni ma
NK072(nu)002:4136: yin te / 'pho 'gyur med pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:4137: snying po rab tu bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK072(nu)002:4138: thog ma med pa dus kyi dbyings //
NK072(nu)002:4139: chos rnams kun gyi gnas yin te //
NK072(nu)002:4141: mya ngan las 'das thob pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:4142: ji ltar sngon de phyis de bzhin //
NK072(nu)002:4143: 'gyur ba med pa'i de bzhin nyid //
NK072(nu)002:4145: de yang dpe dgus nyon mongs pa'i sbugs na gnas par bstan pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:4147: sangs rgyas pad ngan sbrang rtsi sbrang ma la //
NK072(nu)002:4148: sbun la snying po mi gtsang nang na gser //
NK072(nu)002:4149: sa la gter dang myug sogs 'bras chu dang //
NK072(nu)002:4150: gos hrul nang na rgyal ba'i sku dang ni //
NK072(nu)002:4151: bud med ngan ma'i lto na mi bdag dang //
NK072(nu)002:4152: sa ngan rin chen gzugs yod ji lta bar //
NK072(nu)002:4153: glo bur nyon mongs dri mas bsgribs pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:4154: sems can rnams la de bzhin khams 'di gnas //
NK072(nu)002:4156: gzhan yang 'phags pa yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs las kyang /
NK072(nu)002:4157: bcom ldan 'das kyi 'od srungs la bka' rtsal pa /
NK072(nu)002:4159: dper na rgyal po la gyad gcig yod pa'i dpral ba na rdo rje'i nor bu zhig yod pa /
NK072(nu)002:4160: gyad gzhan dang stobs bkye ba las /
NK072(nu)002:4161: gyad pha rol po'i mgos reg ste /
NK072(nu)002:4162: dpral ba'i nor bu sha'i nang du nub kyang nor bu gar song mi shes so //
NK072(nu)002:4163: rma byung ba'i phyir sman pa bos nas gsos shig ces bsgo ba las /
NK072(nu)002:4164: sman pa shin tu mkhas pas ni /
NK072(nu)002:4165: nor bu sha'i nang du song ba'i phyir rma byung ba de la sman mi byed de /
NK072(nu)002:4167: kye stobs po che khyod kyi dpral ba'i nor bu ga re zhes zer ro //
NK072(nu)002:4168: gyad de snga sa nas sman pa 'di skad du /
NK072(nu)002:4169: 'dag gi dpral ba'i nor bu gar yang ma song ba'i rigs te /
NK072(nu)002:4170: de med na sgyu ma yin nam snyam du sems te shin tu mya ngan byed de /
NK072(nu)002:4172: gyad de'i spro ba bskyed nas /
NK072(nu)002:4173: de ltar mya ngan ma byed cig /
NK072(nu)002:4174: khyod kyi stobs bkye ba na nor bu sha'i nang du nub ste /
NK072(nu)002:4175: gzugs brnyan tsam phyi rol du snang ngo //
NK072(nu)002:4176: khyod stobs bkye ba na zhe sdang skyes te /
NK072(nu)002:4177: nor bu'i mthus sha'i nang du nub kyang ma tshor ba yin no //
NK072(nu)002:4178: de skad smras kyang yid ma ches nas /
NK072(nu)002:4179: 'di skad du sman pa khyod rdzun ma zer gcig /
NK072(nu)002:4180: ci ste sha'i nang du nub na ni rnag dang /
NK072(nu)002:4181: khrag shin tu brtsogs pa yin pas gzugs brnyan phyir snang ba ni mi rigs so //
NK072(nu)002:4182: de nas sman pas me long ltar bcug nas me
NK072(nu)002:4183: long gi nang du nor bu yang gsal bar gyur
NK072(nu)002:4184: te / gyad des de ltar gyur pa mthong nas ngo mtshar rmad kyi 'du shes skyes so //
NK072(nu)002:4185: rigs kyi bu sems can thams cad de dang 'dra ste /
NK072(nu)002:4186: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la bsnyen bskur ma byas pas
NK072(nu)002:4187: sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin yod kyang mthong bar mi
NK072(nu)002:4190: gti mug gis bsgribs te zil gyis gnon pa 'gro
NK072(nu)002:4191: ba tha dad pa mang por 'khor zhing sdug bsngal
NK072(nu)002:4192: bar gyur to // zhes pa nas /
NK072(nu)002:4194: sems can thams cad kyi lus kyi nang na stobs bcu dang /
NK072(nu)002:4195: mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK072(nu)002:4196: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu yang yod do //
NK072(nu)002:4197: zhes pa'i bar tshul du mas gsungs so //
NK072(nu)002:4198: de ltar rang gnas kyi ye shes de nyid rtogs
NK072(nu)002:4199: pa'i thabs la rgyal bas 'khor lo rim pa gsum
NK072(nu)002:4200: bskor ba'i tshul dpe don sgo nas ston pa ni
NK072(nu)002:4201: / yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo las /
NK072(nu)002:4202: rigs kyi bu gzhan yang 'di lta ste /
NK072(nu)002:4203: dper na bud med bu chung ngu kha myags gos pa zhig nad kyis btab na /
NK072(nu)002:4204: bud med de mya ngan gyis gdungs te sman pa 'tshol lo //
NK072(nu)002:4205: de la sman pas sman mar dang 'o ma dang /
NK072(nu)002:4206: sha kha ra gsum du sbyor te bu la blud nas /
NK072(nu)002:4207: bud med de la 'di skad ces basgo'o //
NK072(nu)002:4208: bu 'dir sman btang gis re zhig ma zhu'i bar
NK072(nu)002:4209: du nu zho blud du mi rung ngo zhes basgo'o
NK072(nu)002:4210: // de nas bud med des nu zho mi snun pa'i phyir nu ma la mkhris pa byugs nas /
NK072(nu)002:4211: bu la kho mo'i nu ma la dug gis bskus te nur mi rung ngo zhes zer ro //
NK072(nu)002:4212: de'i bu de skom pas gdungs te /
NK072(nu)002:4213: nu ma nu 'dod kyang kha ba'i ro bro ba tshor ma thag tu nur mi btub bo //
NK072(nu)002:4214: sman zhu nas bud med kyis nu ma dag par bkrus te /
NK072(nu)002:4216: da nu ma nur gzhug go //
NK072(nu)002:4218: khye'u de skom pas gdungs kyang /
NK072(nu)002:4219: sngar kha ba'i ro myong bas bos kyang 'ong du mi gtub bo //
NK072(nu)002:4220: de la yang mas 'di skad du basgo'o //
NK072(nu)002:4221: khyed da ci sngar sman 'thungs te sman ma zhu
NK072(nu)002:4222: ba'i bar du nu ma blud du mi rung bas
NK072(nu)002:4223: / kho mos mkhris pa bskus pa yin gyi /
NK072(nu)002:4224: da khyod kyi sman yang zhu la /
NK072(nu)002:4225: kha ba yang bkrus kyi da ni kha ba'i ro med do //
NK072(nu)002:4227: gdod bag kyi nye ste 'thung du gtub bo //
NK072(nu)002:4229: de bzhin gshegs pa yang sems can bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4230: sems can thams cad la bdag med pa'i nan tan ston te /
NK072(nu)002:4231: de la nan tan byas pas bdag ces bya ba'i sems med de /
NK072(nu)002:4232: yongs su mya ngan las bazla'o //
NK072(nu)002:4233: de las 'jig rten rgyang 'phen pa'i ngan par lta ba bsal ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4234: bdag med pa'i chos bsgoms pas yongs su dag pa'i lus su 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4235: ji ltar bud med des bu'i mkhris pas nu ma bskus pa bzhin du /
NK072(nu)002:4236: de bzhin gshegs pa yang de dang 'dra ste /
NK072(nu)002:4237: stong pa nyid bsgom pa'i phyir chos thams cad la bdag med ces gsungs so //
NK072(nu)002:4238: ji lta bud med des nu ma phyis bkrus nas bu bos te /
NK072(nu)002:4239: nu zho blud de zhes bya ba bzhin du /
NK072(nu)002:4240: ngas de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po bstan pa yang de dang 'dra ste /
NK072(nu)002:4241: dge slong khyod kyang ma skrag par /
NK072(nu)002:4242: ji lta bu la mas bos te /
NK072(nu)002:4243: nu zho bgas kyis 'thungs pa bzhin du /
NK072(nu)002:4244: dge slong khyod kyang bye brag phyed par gyis shig /
NK072(nu)002:4245: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ni med par bya ba ma yin no //
NK072(nu)002:4246: ngas sngon pha rol tu phyin pa'i mdo brjod pa dag las /
NK072(nu)002:4247: stong pa nyid du bstan pa de yang /
NK072(nu)002:4248: rang bzhin med pa tsam la dgongs te gsungs par rig pa gyis shig /
NK072(nu)002:4249: gzhan du na ci yang med pa'i stong pa nyid bsgoms pa las ni /
NK072(nu)002:4250: sangs rgyas kyi sku dang ye shes kyang 'byung bar mi 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:4251: 'bras bu ni rgyu'i rjes su byed pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:4253: 'di nyid nges don mthar thug yin pa cis shes she na /
NK072(nu)002:4254: ston pa myang ngan las 'das pa'i khar so so'i
NK072(nu)002:4255: skad dang mthun par gsung gcig gis da mya ngan
NK072(nu)002:4256: las 'da' yi su dag the tshom dang som nyi
NK072(nu)002:4257: yod na nang gi tha ma 'dir zhus shig ces
NK072(nu)002:4258: pa'i sgra chen pos srid rtse'i bar du khyab par
NK072(nu)002:4259: mdzad cing zhal gyi sgo las 'od zer gyis phyogs
NK072(nu)002:4260: bcu'i sems can kun la rig pas sdug bsngal zhi
NK072(nu)002:4262: kun dga' bo la sogs pa rnams kyis zhus par
NK072(nu)002:4263: sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin lam dbu ma ston pa
NK072(nu)002:4265: deng phan chad mdo sde'i mtha' la 'jug par bya yi /
NK072(nu)002:4266: gang zag la 'jug pa ma yin no //
NK072(nu)002:4269: chos nyid dang mi 'gal na de la gus par bzung zhig /
NK072(nu)002:4270: de las ldog na de ni chos ma yin par
NK072(nu)002:4271: bzung zhig ces zhal gdams su brtsal ba yin no
NK072(nu)002:4272: // mdo sde dgongs pa nges 'grel las kyang /
NK072(nu)002:4273: 'khor lo dang po gnyis kyi skabs su /
NK072(nu)002:4274: 'khor lo bskor ba 'di yang bla na mchis pa skabs mchis pa /
NK072(nu)002:4276: rtsod pa'i gzhi'i gnas su gyur pa lags so //
NK072(nu)002:4279: chos ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba 'di ni /
NK072(nu)002:4283: rtsod pa'i gzhi'i gnas su gyur lags pa'o zhes gsungs so //
NK072(nu)002:4284: de la kha cig na re /
NK072(nu)002:4285: de ltar na gong du dbu ma yang dag nyid ma rtogs par bshad pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK072(nu)002:4286: mdo sngags gnyis mthar thug gi lta ba'ang khyad par med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:4288: mdo'i theg par sgrib pa shin tu phra ba nang
NK072(nu)002:4289: du dkar dmar rlung gsum 'grogs pas shes pa gnyis
NK072(nu)002:4290: snang 'khor ba'i chos su shar bar byed pa don
NK072(nu)002:4291: la dag byed gnyen po la zhen pa'i snyoms 'jug
NK072(nu)002:4292: gi sgrib pa shin tu phra ba de sngags kyi
NK072(nu)002:4293: theg pa kho nas sbyongs dgos shing /
NK072(nu)002:4294: de sbyong byed kyi snying po rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin yin mod kyang /
NK072(nu)002:4295: de ni nang gi mngon byang lnga la brten nas dkar cha dag pa sku rdo rje /
NK072(nu)002:4296: dmar cha dag pa gsung rdo rje /
NK072(nu)002:4297: shes rig dag pa thugs rdo rje ste rdo rje
NK072(nu)002:4298: gsum gyi ngo bor byang chub par byed pa'i lam
NK072(nu)002:4299: de yin kyang / mdo lam du rdo rje lta
NK072(nu)002:4300: bu'i ting 'dzin zhes pa las de ji ltar yin
NK072(nu)002:4302: gong gi lta ba'i steng du lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK072(nu)002:4303: mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen gyi ye shes de sngags
NK072(nu)002:4304: kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i lta ba yin par
NK072(nu)002:4305: de gnyis ma bshad pas khyad par byas pa ste
NK072(nu)002:4307: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK072(nu)002:4308: mi shig thig le bde chen po //
NK072(nu)002:4309: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK072(nu)002:4310: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK072(nu)002:4313: des na gtso bos gang zhig 'pho med lhan skyes
NK072(nu)002:4314: lus kyi bde ba sngags kyi theg par bstan zhes
NK072(nu)002:4316: gnyis pa sngags kyi lta ba'i ngo bo'am /
NK072(nu)002:4318: mtha' gang du yang ma reg pa'i sems nyid ye
NK072(nu)002:4319: nas dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub
NK072(nu)002:4320: pa ni lhag pa don dam bden pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4321: de nyid kyi rtsal snang snod bcud sku dang ye
NK072(nu)002:4322: shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang shar ba'i lhag pa
NK072(nu)002:4323: bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba ste
NK072(nu)002:4325: lhag pa'i rnam gnyis dbyer med don //
NK072(nu)002:4326: ming grangs cir yang bstan mod kyang //
NK072(nu)002:4327: don du smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK072(nu)002:4330: drish+ta'i sgra las lta ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:4331: gnas lugs dang rjes su mthun pa'i bden don /
NK072(nu)002:4332: mthong bas gdengs su gyur pa'i shes rab bo //
NK072(nu)002:4334: lta dang lta ba byar med de //
NK072(nu)002:4335: ye shes sgron ma sgreng bas ni //
NK072(nu)002:4336: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams ma lus mthong //
NK072(nu)002:4339: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4340: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs bzung ba gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:4343: gzhi dang gtan tshigs grub pa'i don //
NK072(nu)002:4344: zhes pas chos gsum gyi sgo nas rtogs par bya ste /
NK072(nu)002:4345: gang gzhal bya chos can gang gis 'jal byed gtan tshig /
NK072(nu)002:4346: de ltar gzhal ba'i grub mtha'o //
NK072(nu)002:4347: dang po la gzhal bya dngos /
NK072(nu)002:4348: zhar la dogs pa bsal ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:4358: brtags pa'i spyod yul gnyis la gzhal //
NK072(nu)002:4362: gzhal gyis mi long ba'i dogs pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:4364: dngos po gnyis kyi bsdus pa'i chos gzhal byar byas nas 'jal ba de /
NK072(nu)002:4369: mos spyod kyi rig shes la lkog tu gyur pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4370: 'o skol rnams kyi spyod yul ma yin pa'i gzhal byar mi rung ste /
NK072(nu)002:4372: 'das pa'i spyod yul ma gyur phyir //
NK072(nu)002:4373: gzhal bya'i yul du ji ltar rigs //
NK072(nu)002:4375: gal te 'das pa'i snang ba la //
NK072(nu)002:4376: 'jal na dang po'i lkog tu gyur //
NK072(nu)002:4378: der zhen pa'i sems de la 'jal lo zhe na'ang /
NK072(nu)002:4379: mi rigs te myang 'das 'khrul shes kyi yul du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4381: gal te zhen na sgro btags 'khor ba'i chos su
NK072(nu)002:4382: 'gyur bas 'das pa ma yin te snga ma las
NK072(nu)002:4383: / sems la mya ngan 'das zhen pa //
NK072(nu)002:4384: de nyid 'das par rung ma yin //
NK072(nu)002:4387: 'khor ba'i rang mtshan snang tsam nyid la 'jal lam /
NK072(nu)002:4388: zhes pa sgro btags kyi shes pa la 'jal /
NK072(nu)002:4391: ji ltar snang nyid dgag min te //
NK072(nu)002:4394: bden par rtog pa bzlog bya yin //
NK072(nu)002:4395: zhes pas rig pas dgag par mi nus shing /
NK072(nu)002:4396: bkag na skyon du 'gyur ba'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:4397: lam bsod nams kyi tshogs bkag pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4398: 'bras bu ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes rgyun chad par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:4400: da ltar gyi shes pa skad cig ma rang thad rang thad kyi zhen snang la 'jal te /
NK072(nu)002:4402: de shes shes pa skad cig ma //
NK072(nu)002:4403: de yang rang thad rang thad dpyad //
NK072(nu)002:4405: de ltar na yid so sor rtog pa'i shes rab
NK072(nu)002:4406: tu gnas 'gyur bas gzhal bya med do zhe na
NK072(nu)002:4407: / yid rtog bcas bsam shes su re zhig gnas
NK072(nu)002:4408: 'gyur kyang zhen pa'i ngo bo ma dag pas kun
NK072(nu)002:4410: zhen snang 'byung rung du yod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4412: yid rtog bcas kyi shes pa rtsa ba nas 'dag par byed pa'i gnyen po shes rab yin la /
NK072(nu)002:4413: de da dung rgyud la ma brten pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:4415: gal te yid 'gyur zhen pa yang //
NK072(nu)002:4416: skad cig mnyam par 'gag pas med //
NK072(nu)002:4417: de tshe brtags gzhi yod mi rung //
NK072(nu)002:4418: dogs na zhen pa'i yul rnams ni //
NK072(nu)002:4419: gtan du dag pa ma yin phyir //
NK072(nu)002:4420: so sor spyod kyang zhen yul mthong //
NK072(nu)002:4422: de yang shes rgyud skad cig gi steng du mngon
NK072(nu)002:4423: 'gyur dus gcig tu tshogs nas 'jal ba ma yin
NK072(nu)002:4424: gyi gcig mngon 'gyur gyi tshe gcig bag la nyal
NK072(nu)002:4428: phyi ma 'phrad pa'i tshul gyis 'jal te /
NK072(nu)002:4429: da ltar gyi skad cig ma dang po la 'phrad tsam /
NK072(nu)002:4431: gsum pa la bsam shes rdzogs par skyes pa'i tshe /
NK072(nu)002:4432: snga ma'i kun btags mngon 'gyur ci ris su 'gag cing /
NK072(nu)002:4433: rkyen gzhan gyis de'i rgyun brjod pa'i skad cig phyi ma la kun btags skye bzhin pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4434: yul shes ma 'dres pa'i phyir gzhal bya med pa'i skyon med de /
NK072(nu)002:4436: gzhal bya med par dogs pa yang //
NK072(nu)002:4437: zhen pa shes pa'i phyi yul yin //
NK072(nu)002:4438: skad cig gnas 'gyur shes nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:4439: de bas yul sems ma 'dres phyir //
NK072(nu)002:4440: zhen snang 'jal la skyon pa med //
NK072(nu)002:4443: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi rang mtshan la mi 'jal gyi /
NK072(nu)002:4444: 'khor ba phyi nang snod bcud du zhen pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4445: mya ngan 'das sku dang ye shes su zhen pa'i zhen byed kyi blo nyid gzhal bya ste /
NK072(nu)002:4447: nges par bzhag pa'i gzhal bya ni //
NK072(nu)002:4449: rang gi mtshan nyid mi 'dod de //
NK072(nu)002:4450: de ltar nang na zhan pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:4451: phyi rol med la yod par snang //
NK072(nu)002:4452: zhan dang snang ba gnyis la brten //
NK072(nu)002:4455: 'o na so sor rtog pa'i bsam pa'i shes rab de 'khrul shes su thal /
NK072(nu)002:4456: 'khor ba pa'i shes pa yin pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:4458: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab chos can /
NK072(nu)002:4459: khyod kyis don gtan la mi pheb par thal /
NK072(nu)002:4463: bsam shes skyes pa don med du thal lo //
NK072(nu)002:4465: ma 'khrul pa'i phyir 'bad med du grol bar thal zer na /
NK072(nu)002:4466: 'khrul ma 'khrul gnas skabs la 'jog ste dbang po'i mngon sum bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:4467: gnyis pa 'jal byed gtan tshigs la /
NK072(nu)002:4471: bsgrub bya'i don shes par byed pa'i thabs rtsod gzhi
NK072(nu)002:4472: la bkod nas dgag sgrub gnyis su byed pa'i las
NK072(nu)002:4474: de phyir gtan tshigs las la brjod //
NK072(nu)002:4478: de nyid dngos lnga tshul dang tshigs //
NK072(nu)002:4480: sngon byung dngos lnga'i gtan tshigs /
NK072(nu)002:4484: sngon byung du ston pa sku lngas rang rang gi
NK072(nu)002:4485: 'khor lnga la gsung lnga'i sgo nas chos nyid kyi
NK072(nu)002:4486: don dngos su gtan la phab pa ni dngos lnga'i
NK072(nu)002:4487: gtan tshigs te / de nyid las /
NK072(nu)002:4488: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas ston pa //
NK072(nu)002:4490: gsung lnga bstan pa de kho na //
NK072(nu)002:4493: gtan tshigs 'di ni rjes 'jug la ltos pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4494: sngon byung la ltos na gtan tshigs dngos ma yin par shes dgos so //
NK072(nu)002:4496: dbang po yang rab mchog tu gyur pa rnams la snang grags 'di dag gis mtshon nas /
NK072(nu)002:4497: sngon byung du dngos lngas gtan la phab pa'i sku
NK072(nu)002:4498: lnga'i gsung gi tshul du rtogs par byed pa ni
NK072(nu)002:4501: rtogs dang ldan pa'i blo rnams la //
NK072(nu)002:4502: dngos po sna tshogs sems gsang sngags //
NK072(nu)002:4503: nges lung yin phyir chos tshul ston //
NK072(nu)002:4504: brjod dang 'dra bar brda' sprod pas //
NK072(nu)002:4505: ngo bo nyid kyis bshad pa'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:4506: ma 'ongs don du gtan tshigs nges //
NK072(nu)002:4509: sngar gyi tshul lnga po nyid tshig tu dngos su brjod pa ni tshigs lnga'i gtan tshigs so //
NK072(nu)002:4511: chos sku'i tshig ni skye med rang snang du ston pa'i tshig dang yi ge rnams so //
NK072(nu)002:4512: de bzhin du longs sku'i ldem dgongs brda'i /
NK072(nu)002:4513: sprul sku'i bkri drang brgyud pa'i /
NK072(nu)002:4514: rdo rje'i sku'i dbyer med rdo rje'i /
NK072(nu)002:4515: mngon byang gi ye shes rang snang du ston pa'i tshig dang yi ge rnams te /
NK072(nu)002:4517: ngo bo snang tshig rang snang tshig /
NK072(nu)002:4518: ldem dgongs tshig dang bkri drang tshig /
NK072(nu)002:4519: 'dod rkyen tshig dang rdo rje'i tshig /
NK072(nu)002:4520: rang rig mngon gsal tshig gis mtshon //
NK072(nu)002:4523: dpyad du med pa go ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:4527: brtag dpyad la ma ltos par don go ba'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:4529: sprul sku'i gtan tshigs te brtag dpyad la brten nas don go ba'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:4532: sgra mthun don spags kyi gtan tshigs gnyis /
NK072(nu)002:4533: dang po la'ang rtogs pa bzhi'i /
NK072(nu)002:4536: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs dang bzhi /
NK072(nu)002:4539: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK072(nu)002:4540: byin gyis brlabs dang mngon sum pa //
NK072(nu)002:4541: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yi //
NK072(nu)002:4542: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK072(nu)002:4544: rgyu gcig pa ni 'khor 'das gnyis chos can /
NK072(nu)002:4546: sems nyid skye ba med pa'i dbyings su rgyu gcig pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4547: dper na rgyal bu dwa'u dmangs su 'dzin pa'i sgro
NK072(nu)002:4548: 'dogs dang rgyal por nges pa'i tshad ma gnyis ngo
NK072(nu)002:4549: bo rgyal bur gcig pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:4551: chos nyid dbyings su tshul gcig pas //
NK072(nu)002:4552: ma lus rang snang chos thams cad //
NK072(nu)002:4553: ma lus byang chub sems su rtogs //
NK072(nu)002:4556: sems nyid skye med kyi gdangs chos can /
NK072(nu)002:4557: rol pa 'gag med lha'i sku gsung thugs su rang snang ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:4558: mtshon byed ye shes mtshon nas rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4559: dper na mdzub mos ri bong can bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:4561: sku gsung thugs su snang ba yi //
NK072(nu)002:4562: ma lus gsung gi rgyan du rtogs //
NK072(nu)002:4563: thams cad gsung gi yi ge ste //
NK072(nu)002:4564: thabs dang ldan pas rgyas gdab bo //
NK072(nu)002:4566: gsum pa byin gyis rlabs pa'i tshul ni /
NK072(nu)002:4569: de gnyis dngos su rtogs pa'i mthus bden pa dbyer
NK072(nu)002:4570: med du ye nas sangs rgyas par rtogs pa'i byin
NK072(nu)002:4572: dper na ras dkar po dmar por bsgyur ba'i nus pa btsod la yod pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:4574: de nyid dbyer med byin rlabs las //
NK072(nu)002:4575: de nyid de yi byin rlabs te //
NK072(nu)002:4576: gnyis med tshul gyis rang snang ba //
NK072(nu)002:4577: byin rlabs ngo mtshar bsam mi khyab //
NK072(nu)002:4580: bden pa dbyer med chos can /
NK072(nu)002:4581: blo'i spyod las 'das pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:4582: rang rig mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal du rjen par rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4583: dper na mig skyon med pas dung dkar po mngon
NK072(nu)002:4584: sum du mthong ba de de'i gnas lugs yin pa
NK072(nu)002:4585: bzhin no // de yang rgya mtsho las /
NK072(nu)002:4586: rang snang rang byung chos 'di dag /
NK072(nu)002:4587: gnyis med rang rig ma skyes par //
NK072(nu)002:4588: gsal bar mngon sum the tshom med //
NK072(nu)002:4589: rtogs pa kun gyi mchog tu bshad //
NK072(nu)002:4592: gzhan la ma brten mi 'gal bar //
NK072(nu)002:4593: mngon sum rig pas thag chod na //
NK072(nu)002:4594: rnal 'byor pa la slob pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:4596: de'ang spyir mngon sum la bzhi yod kyang /
NK072(nu)002:4598: gnyis pa dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK072(nu)002:4599: 'di ltar snang ba phyi nang gi chos thams cad chos can /
NK072(nu)002:4600: ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:4601: dag pa gsum dang ldan pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:4603: bcud phung po lnga yab lngar /
NK072(nu)002:4604: rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4606: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK072(nu)002:4608: gsum pa mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK072(nu)002:4609: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams chos can /
NK072(nu)002:4611: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:4612: mnyam pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4614: rnam grangs dang rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam gnyis ka skye med dang /
NK072(nu)002:4615: yang log gi kun rdzob gnyis ka sgyu mar mnyam pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:4616: thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis so //
NK072(nu)002:4617: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK072(nu)002:4618: med dgag dang ma yin dgag gi stong pa nyid
NK072(nu)002:4619: gnyis ka don dam dkor bdun chos kyi sku dang
NK072(nu)002:4620: / ma dag pa las snang dang dag pa lhar
NK072(nu)002:4621: snang gi kun rdzob gnyis ka'ang gzugs sku lha'i dkyil
NK072(nu)002:4622: 'khor du mnyam pas lhag pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4624: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyi //
NK072(nu)002:4625: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK072(nu)002:4627: bzhi pa bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK072(nu)002:4629: snang lugs nas du mar snang yang yin lugs nas gzhal na de ltar ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:4630: sems nyid skye med rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK072(nu)002:4631: po gcig gi bdag nyid du ye nas gnas pa'i
NK072(nu)002:4632: phyir / dper na pha mes kyi lo rgyus brjod pas so so'i rigs brgyud shes pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:4634: snang ba 'di kun rang rang gi //
NK072(nu)002:4635: rang bzhin med pa'i rnam shes nyid //
NK072(nu)002:4636: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK072(nu)002:4638: gnyis pa sgra mthun don spags kyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK072(nu)002:4639: tshig mdo sngags thun mong du grags shing /
NK072(nu)002:4640: don 'di nyid ltar gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:4643: skabs 'phros kyi rtsod pa spong ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:4645: dri ma med pa'i shes rab gsum gyis yod med
NK072(nu)002:4646: la sogs pa'i sgro skur gyi mthar ma reg par
NK072(nu)002:4647: btsal ba las rtogs pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4649: yod las btsal na sgro btags te //
NK072(nu)002:4651: med las btsal na bskur btab ste //
NK072(nu)002:4652: bskur pa bcu yi gnas su lhung //
NK072(nu)002:4653: yod med gnyis las btsal byas na //
NK072(nu)002:4657: grub pa'i mtha'i ngo bo gnas lugs nyid rang gi
NK072(nu)002:4658: mtshan nyid du rtogs nas rig pa yul med du
NK072(nu)002:4659: gsal ba ste / lam rim las /
NK072(nu)002:4660: rgya mtsho dang ni gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK072(nu)002:4661: sgra brten yid la byed min par //
NK072(nu)002:4662: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral ba //
NK072(nu)002:4663: rang gsal gsum bral mi bsgul bar //
NK072(nu)002:4664: nges par gdengs su gang byas pa //
NK072(nu)002:4665: thos bsam brten pa'i lta mthar phyin //
NK072(nu)002:4668: lam la zhugs su chos nyid mngon sum du rtogs par yod par thal /
NK072(nu)002:4669: der lta bu'i rang mtshan mthong ba'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:4670: sgra brten yid la byed min par //
NK072(nu)002:4672: de ma rtogs na mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs kyang don med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK072(nu)002:4675: thos bsam gyi lta ba mthar phyin pa'i tshogs lam du 'jug kha ma'i gang zag de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:4676: lam stong pa chen po mngon sum du rtogs par thal /
NK072(nu)002:4677: lta ba 'khor 'das dbyer med du thos bsam gyis gtan la phebs pa'i gang zag yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4678: 'dod mi nus te lam stong pa chen po'i tshogs
NK072(nu)002:4679: lam du 'jug ma rag pa yin pa'i phyir ro
NK072(nu)002:4681: chos nyid spyi'i rnam pa don spyir mthong ba la 'jog go //
NK072(nu)002:4682: yang kha cig chos nyid rang mtshan de zag bcas su rang rig mngon sum dang /
NK072(nu)002:4683: zag med du rnal 'byor mngon sum gyis mthong ngo zhes zer ba'ang sngar gyi skyon dbab bo //
NK072(nu)002:4684: gsum pa rnam grangs rnam par phye ba la /
NK072(nu)002:4685: nyams su len byed lam gyi rim pa'i lta grangs dang /
NK072(nu)002:4686: blang bya rgyud don gyi lta grangs so //
NK072(nu)002:4688: khyab bya lam kun la khyab byed lta bas khyab pa'i phyir lam gyi lta grangs dgu ste /
NK072(nu)002:4690: mnyam nyid ngang las mi skrag pas //
NK072(nu)002:4691: mngon byas nges pa'i shes rab dang //
NK072(nu)002:4692: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK072(nu)002:4693: rang rig ye shes snying rjes gzigs //
NK072(nu)002:4694: phyag rgya gcig sku 'bras bur lta //
NK072(nu)002:4695: thams cad gsal ba'i lta ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:4696: bar chad med pa'i tshogs chen mthong //
NK072(nu)002:4697: dbang bskur mnyam nyid mi g.yo ba //
NK072(nu)002:4698: ye shes kun mkhyen lta ba dgu /
NK072(nu)002:4701: rgyud kyi dngos po rnams la /
NK072(nu)002:4702: khyab byed lta bas khyab pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:4703: rgyud don gyi lta grangs dgu ste /
NK072(nu)002:4705: rgyud don gzungs kyi zin pa ni //
NK072(nu)002:4706: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK072(nu)002:4707: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK072(nu)002:4709: lnga pa ma rtogs pa'i skyon la /
NK072(nu)002:4710: sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'khor ba'i gnas su mthong ba'i dang /
NK072(nu)002:4711: dge ba'i las ma spyad kyang 'khor ba las mi grol ba'i skyon no //
NK072(nu)002:4714: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK072(nu)002:4715: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK072(nu)002:4719: thabs la mkhas pas ma zin na //
NK072(nu)002:4720: lam gyi dge spyad rtag spyad kyang //
NK072(nu)002:4721: mtho ris lha dang mir skye yi //
NK072(nu)002:4722: skye shi med pa'i sa mi thob //
NK072(nu)002:4724: drug pa rtogs pa'i yon tan la /
NK072(nu)002:4725: ngan song gi gnas sangs rgyas kyi zhing du mthong ba'i dang /
NK072(nu)002:4726: las ci la spyad kyang mi 'ching ba'i dang /
NK072(nu)002:4727: 'khor bar mi ldog cing 'tshang rgya ba'i yon tan no //
NK072(nu)002:4730: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pa na //
NK072(nu)002:4731: ngan song gnas kyang 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK072(nu)002:4735: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK072(nu)002:4736: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang //
NK072(nu)002:4737: byas la mi gsob tshogs 'gyur te //
NK072(nu)002:4738: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK072(nu)002:4742: gang zhig 'di ltar mthong rtogs pa //
NK072(nu)002:4743: dngos grub mchog gi snying po de //
NK072(nu)002:4744: chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK072(nu)002:4745: dngos po don rtogs mtha' mi gtong //
NK072(nu)002:4746: spyod yul kun tu tshad dpag med //
NK072(nu)002:4748: gnyis pa zin chags med pa spyod pa la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:4750: gzhan sel sgrib pa 'byang zhing bag chags 'dag /
NK072(nu)002:4751: don gnyer tshogs rdzogs shing lta sgom gyi bogs 'byin par byed pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4753: de yang bdag gzhan don phyir du //
NK072(nu)002:4754: lam rjes mthun pa'i spyod pa yang //
NK072(nu)002:4755: skabs kyi ting 'dzin stongs phyir spyad //
NK072(nu)002:4757: gnyis pa ngo bo'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:4758: lam sa'i sgo gsum yongs su dag par byed pa'i
NK072(nu)002:4759: lus ngag yid gsum gyi bya bar gyur pa ste
NK072(nu)002:4761: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK072(nu)002:4762: gang na'ang mi gnas mi dmigs pas //
NK072(nu)002:4765: tsar+ya'i sgra las spyod pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4766: sgo gsum don yod par bya ba'i phyir sngags kyi spyad pa la spyod pa'i las can no //
NK072(nu)002:4768: sgo gsum las phyir nges tshig 'grub //
NK072(nu)002:4771: gang gi tshe spyod pa'i dus dang /
NK072(nu)002:4774: mnyam bzhag las langs nas rjes thob tu spyod pa ci la ma chags par spyod pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4776: kun kyang mnyam las langs che'o //
NK072(nu)002:4779: spyi dang khyad par gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:4781: spyir lus ngag yid gsum dag pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:4783: las dang po pa'i dus su bag dang ldan pa'i spyod pa ste dbye na /
NK072(nu)002:4784: mi mthun pa'i rkyen las byol ba'i dang /
NK072(nu)002:4785: mthun rkyen brten pa'i spyod pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:4787: 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad sogs kha na ma tho
NK072(nu)002:4788: ba thams cad las byol nas gzhan gyis dge ba
NK072(nu)002:4789: spel ba'i phyir mthun 'jug mtshams pa'i spyod pa la
NK072(nu)002:4790: 'jug ste / rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK072(nu)002:4791: brtan pa ma thob bar du'ang //
NK072(nu)002:4792: kha na ma tho rdul med cing //
NK072(nu)002:4793: sdom pa gsum la gnas par bya //
NK072(nu)002:4796: mnyam bzhag gi rtogs pa bag ldan du bsring zhing /
NK072(nu)002:4797: thun mtshams kyi bya ba'i cha gtso bor brten pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4799: yi ge 'bri mchod sbyin pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:4800: nyan dang klog dang 'dzin pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:4801: 'chad dang kha ton byed pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:4802: de sems pa dang sgom pa de //
NK072(nu)002:4803: spyod pa 'di bcu'i bdag nyid ni //
NK072(nu)002:4804: bsod nams phung po dpag tu med //
NK072(nu)002:4805: ces pas chos spyod bcu dang de nas cung zad
NK072(nu)002:4806: goms te dben par mnyam rjes khyad med du gyur
NK072(nu)002:4807: pa na rtogs pa rkyen thub tu byed pa smyon
NK072(nu)002:4808: pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:4809: shin tu goms nas rtogs pa la bri gang med
NK072(nu)002:4810: par gyur pa na bcos slad med par gzhan phan
NK072(nu)002:4811: byed pa rgyal po sa 'dzin gyi spyod pa lta
NK072(nu)002:4813: gnyis pa khyad par gyi spyod pa la grol lam bag yod kyi dang /
NK072(nu)002:4814: thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:4817: dang po la zag bcas kyi lam du dang /
NK072(nu)002:4818: zag med kyi lam du ji ltar spyod pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:4820: dad brtson gyi spyod pa shes rab dang mthun pa /
NK072(nu)002:4822: phyogs gcig pa spros bcas kyi /
NK072(nu)002:4823: tshogs kyi spyod pa dang drug ste go sla'o //
NK072(nu)002:4827: gnyis pa grol lam cig car ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:4828: rjes shes su ltar ji spyod kyang /
NK072(nu)002:4831: bya rtsol 'dzin rtog dang bral ba rmad du byung ba'i spyod pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4833: mi dmigs pa las rnam par spyod //
NK072(nu)002:4834: de ltar spyod pa kun spyod kyang //
NK072(nu)002:4835: dam pa'i don de spyod mchog yin //
NK072(nu)002:4837: gnyis pa thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:4838: thabs mkhas kyi rtsis zin pa'i gdengs dang ldan pas 'khor ba'i chos ci la'ang spyod pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4840: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK072(nu)002:4841: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang //
NK072(nu)002:4842: byas la mi gsog tshogs 'gyur te //
NK072(nu)002:4843: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK072(nu)002:4846: khyad par gyi spyod pa dang mi ldan na mthar thug gi 'bras bu mi thob ste /
NK072(nu)002:4848: khyad par dor na mthar phyin med //
NK072(nu)002:4851: spyod pa de dag gis bogs phyin nas dngos grub rnam pa gnyis myur du thob par 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:4853: bya byed med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis //
NK072(nu)002:4854: des ni byang chub snying po len //
NK072(nu)002:4856: gsum pa bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor la'ang drug las /
NK072(nu)002:4858: dbang sgrub mchod phrin la sogs pa'i dus su bdag
NK072(nu)002:4859: gzhan gyi don byed pa'i rten du gyur pa ni
NK072(nu)002:4860: spyi'i dgos ched dang bye brag dngos grub kyi thabs
NK072(nu)002:4861: dang rten ni dkyil 'khor yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:4862: gnyis pa ngo bo'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:4863: bkod pa lha'i 'khor lor rdzogs par snang ba'i rigs su gnas pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:4865: gnas skabs bdun du snying po len //
NK072(nu)002:4866: bkod pa gang rdzogs de ngo bo //
NK072(nu)002:4869: man+da la zhes pa'i sgra las /
NK072(nu)002:4871: snying po len pa'i don te /
NK072(nu)002:4873: man+da zhes bya snying po'i don //
NK072(nu)002:4874: la zhes pa ni len pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:4882: dbye ba rang bzhin ting 'dzin dang //
NK072(nu)002:4883: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum //
NK072(nu)002:4888: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK072(nu)002:4890: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK072(nu)002:4894: dkyil 'khor rnam pa bcu gnyis te //
NK072(nu)002:4895: de bzhin nyid dang rang bzhin dang //
NK072(nu)002:4897: ting nge 'dzin dang gzugs brnyan dang //
NK072(nu)002:4898: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gzugs brnyan dang //
NK072(nu)002:4899: byang chub sems dang lhag byang sems //
NK072(nu)002:4900: tshogs dang lhun grub dkyil 'khor ro //
NK072(nu)002:4903: rgyud tshod dang sbyar ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi dang /
NK072(nu)002:4904: de las skabs don deng sang gi gang zag phal
NK072(nu)002:4905: cher smin byed du rung ba'i dkyil 'khor gnyis so
NK072(nu)002:4907: rang bzhin ye shes dkyil 'khor dang /
NK072(nu)002:4908: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs brnyan ni sprul
NK072(nu)002:4909: pa'i dkyil 'khor dang rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor
NK072(nu)002:4910: dang / lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang
NK072(nu)002:4911: bzhi las dang po gsum ni rim par slob dpon
NK072(nu)002:4912: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang mtha' lam dang mthong sgom
NK072(nu)002:4913: dang / la gnas pas / slob ma sa mtha'i byang sems dang /
NK072(nu)002:4914: mthong sgom dang tshogs sbyor gyi yon tan mthar phyin
NK072(nu)002:4915: pa rnams la dbang bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor yin par
NK072(nu)002:4916: sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las bshad pas 'phags pa rnams
NK072(nu)002:4917: kyi spyod yul yin zhing de las 'dir sprul pa'i
NK072(nu)002:4918: dkyil 'khor la lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs
NK072(nu)002:4919: brnyan zhes pa ni 'dir skabs sgyu 'phrul ba'i skad
NK072(nu)002:4921: ting nge 'dzin la brten pa rjes mthun tsam thob
NK072(nu)002:4922: pa yan chad kyi slob dpon mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK072(nu)002:4923: pas / skal ldan gyi slob ma lhag pa gzugs
NK072(nu)002:4924: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba yin la
NK072(nu)002:4925: pas / / de la'ang gdul bya'i dbye bas /
NK072(nu)002:4926: skal dman 'jug pa la rdul tshon 'bring ras bris /
NK072(nu)002:4927: rab tshom bu lta bu dmigs rten rgyud dag nus
NK072(nu)002:4928: cung zad tsam la brten nas bskur ba yod de
NK072(nu)002:4929: / bka' brgyad bde 'dus kyi dbang chog rtsa bar /
NK072(nu)002:4930: dkyil 'khor gang du dbang bskur na //
NK072(nu)002:4931: rab 'bring tha mar gsungs pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:4932: me tog bris sku rdul tshon gsum //
NK072(nu)002:4933: dkyil 'khor gsum du dbang bskur ro //
NK072(nu)002:4935: de las kyang blo che ba'i skal ldan kha cig
NK072(nu)002:4936: thog ma nas slob dpon gyi lus dkyil du 'jug
NK072(nu)002:4938: lus dkyil la dkyil 'khor du 'du shes pa'i gang
NK072(nu)002:4939: zag mkhas pa des phyi dkyil brten dgos pa'i nges
NK072(nu)002:4942: bcos ma gnyis kyi ngo bo gang //
NK072(nu)002:4943: de ni gdul bya'i dbang las 'dod //
NK072(nu)002:4944: mkhas pa'i bsgrub bya de ma yin //
NK072(nu)002:4946: dong sprugs kyi 'jug pa'i me tog dor skabs su'ang /
NK072(nu)002:4947: slob dpon sku yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK072(nu)002:4949: de ltar gyi bla ma dam pa rnams kyi phyag
NK072(nu)002:4950: bzhes su rdul tshon dang ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor
NK072(nu)002:4951: gang rung du dbang bskur bar bzhed de //
NK072(nu)002:4952: de la ras bris su smin byed kyi dbang bskur rung ba'i khungs ni /
NK072(nu)002:4953: mi g.yo bla med kyi rgyud las /
NK072(nu)002:4954: yang na dkyil 'khor bri bya ba //
NK072(nu)002:4955: ras bris tshul du bri bar bya //
NK072(nu)002:4956: dkyil 'khor sngar bzhin bris byas nas //
NK072(nu)002:4957: dbus su mi g.yo mthing nag bri //
NK072(nu)002:4958: zhes sogs ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor bshad cing /
NK072(nu)002:4959: slob dpon dza ya se nas kyang /
NK072(nu)002:4960: rdul tshon bri bar ma nus na //
NK072(nu)002:4961: nges par bcom ldan he ru ka /
NK072(nu)002:4962: phyag rgya'i gzugs dang bcas par bri //
NK072(nu)002:4964: skabs don ding sang gi gang zag phal cher smin byed du rung ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK072(nu)002:4965: dbang bzhi la ltos nas rgyu rten gyi dkyil 'khor bzhi ste /
NK072(nu)002:4966: bum dbang la phyi lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rdul tshon ni /
NK072(nu)002:4967: dpe bzlas drangs pa'i chu tshon ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK072(nu)002:4968: mchog dbang gsum la spyir bdag gi de kho na nyid nang lus kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK072(nu)002:4969: khyad par gsang dbang la sngags kyi de kho na nyid yi ge b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor /
NK072(nu)002:4970: sher dbang la lha'i de kho na nyid kun rdzob byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK072(nu)002:4971: dbang bzhi pa la ye shes kyi de kho na
NK072(nu)002:4972: nyid don dam byang chub kyi sems snying po ye
NK072(nu)002:4975: b+ha ga dkyil 'khor zhes byar bshad //
NK072(nu)002:4976: byang chub sems kyang dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK072(nu)002:4977: lus ni dkyil 'khor nyid du brjod //
NK072(nu)002:4978: dkyil 'khor gsum du gsungs pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:4981: 'chad 'gyur gyi yon tan las bzlog pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:4983: de las zlog pa'i skyon can bzhi //
NK072(nu)002:4986: dkyil 'khor la brten pas rtogs pa'i ye shes 'phel
NK072(nu)002:4987: ba dang sdig sgrib 'byang zhing mtshan rtog 'grib pa
NK072(nu)002:4988: dang / tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i phan yon khyad par
NK072(nu)002:4989: can gyi thabs su gyur pa dang mthar thug 'grub
NK072(nu)002:4990: pa'i rten du 'gyur ba'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:4994: bzhi pa rim par bgrod pa dbang la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:4996: chos kyi rgyal po'i go 'phang rgyud la 'jog pa'i ched du ste /
NK072(nu)002:4997: de thob pa la sgrib pa 'joms shing nus pa
NK072(nu)002:4998: 'jog pa'i thabs 'dis rim par bsgrod dgos pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:4999: / de ltar yang thugs thig las /
NK072(nu)002:5000: bdag gzhan don nus tshogs las 'grub //
NK072(nu)002:5001: de la de yod phyir nod bya //
NK072(nu)002:5003: gnyis pa ngo bo'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:5004: rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi tshogs pa la brten nas
NK072(nu)002:5005: thob bya go 'phang gi 'bras bu rgyud la 'jog
NK072(nu)002:5006: pa'i las kyi thar pa'i myu gu mngon du bskyed
NK072(nu)002:5007: pa dang / skye nges gang rung gi rigs gnas /
NK072(nu)002:5009: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhis yan lag bsnyad //
NK072(nu)002:5010: drug pa gnas pa'i thob bya de //
NK072(nu)002:5011: ngo bo nyid ces rnam par bshad //
NK072(nu)002:5014: a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las mngon par gtor ba zhes bya ste /
NK072(nu)002:5015: dngos su dri ma 'khrud pa tsam la 'jug cing /
NK072(nu)002:5016: brgyud nas des 'bras bu ye shes kyi nus khyad par can 'jog pas na dbang ste /
NK072(nu)002:5018: gang gis gang la dbang bskur bas /
NK072(nu)002:5019: 'dir ma dpe la tshig chad yod snyam /
NK072(nu)002:5022: bzhi pa rnam grangs la dbye ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:5025: rten gyi dkyil 'khor gyi sgo nas dang /
NK072(nu)002:5026: bskur ba dus kyi sgo nas dbye ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:5027: mos pa tha dad pa'i sgo nas dbye ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:5029: rgyud tshod dang sbyar ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhir 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:5030: sngar bshad grub pa las shes par bya'o //
NK072(nu)002:5033: 'di ltar rgyu dus kyi dbang thog mar bskur te /
NK072(nu)002:5034: ma smin pa smin byed kyi dbang yin pas lam gyi sngon du 'gro dgos pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5035: lam dus kyi dbang ni dus la nam babs pa'i bskur te /
NK072(nu)002:5036: lam gyi bogs 'don yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5037: 'bras dus kyi dbang ni tha mar bskur te /
NK072(nu)002:5038: lam mthar phyin nas mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor byed yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5039: des na phyi ma gnyis ni grol byed lam gyi dbang yin no //
NK072(nu)002:5044: rtsa ba rnam lnga bco brgyad dang //
NK072(nu)002:5045: zhes pa'i rtsa ba lnga ni /
NK072(nu)002:5047: dang po sa bon 'jog pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:5048: gnyis pa nus pa bskyed pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:5049: gsum pas nyams myong bskyed pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5050: bzhi pas de nyid brtan par byed //
NK072(nu)002:5051: lnga pas brtan pa nyams blangs pas //
NK072(nu)002:5053: ces pas phan nus gnyis re re dang /
NK072(nu)002:5054: zab dbang gsum so sor ba grangs pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5057: nus dbang la lngar phye zhing /
NK072(nu)002:5058: zab dbang gsum dang bcas pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5061: bsgyur ba lnga la sum cu drug /
NK072(nu)002:5063: rtsa ba'i grangs zhi ba dang mtshungs la /
NK072(nu)002:5064: de'i yan lag so drug ni /
NK072(nu)002:5066: lha dbang phyag mtshan rgyan chas dang //
NK072(nu)002:5067: nus dbang lnga dang gdan gyi dbang //
NK072(nu)002:5068: sgrub rdzas gsang ba rnam gsum mo //
NK072(nu)002:5069: zhes pa'i nang gses kyi grangs so drug ste /
NK072(nu)002:5072: bsnams pa phyag mtshan gyi dang /
NK072(nu)002:5073: dregs pa gdan gyi dbang gsum ni re re dang /
NK072(nu)002:5074: de las gzhan rnams kyi bye brag bgrang ba'i sdom ni /
NK072(nu)002:5075: rgyan chas rtags la bcu yin te //
NK072(nu)002:5076: dbu rgyan bum pa snying po lnga //
NK072(nu)002:5077: cod pan go cha phreng ba rgyan //
NK072(nu)002:5078: thod phreng rtags gsum me dpung ngo //
NK072(nu)002:5079: nus pa'i dbang ni lngar nges te //
NK072(nu)002:5081: sgrub pa'i dbang la bco lnga ste //
NK072(nu)002:5082: bdud rtsi lnga dang sha lnga dang //
NK072(nu)002:5083: rak+ta rgyal mtshan gdugs kha t+wam //
NK072(nu)002:5084: phur pa rdor dril rnge'u chung //
NK072(nu)002:5085: yungs dkar gzungs ma phreng ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:5086: tshe dang bza' btung ming dbang ngo //
NK072(nu)002:5087: zab dbang gsum ste gsang ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:5088: shes rab ye shes bde chen po //
NK072(nu)002:5090: de'ang dbang bzhir bsdu ba'i las khrigs kyi sdom /
NK072(nu)002:5091: gdan dang lha dbang phyag mtshan dang //
NK072(nu)002:5092: chas bcu sgrub rdzas bco lnga ste //
NK072(nu)002:5093: phyi dbang nyer brgyad phan pa'i dbang //
NK072(nu)002:5094: nang ni nus pa'i dbang lnga ste //
NK072(nu)002:5095: gsang ba zab dbang rnam gsum mo //
NK072(nu)002:5102: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK072(nu)002:5103: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK072(nu)002:5104: bgegs bskrad lhar rlob dam tshig sbyin //
NK072(nu)002:5105: de nyid dbab dang chu nan dang //
NK072(nu)002:5106: sgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:5107: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK072(nu)002:5108: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK072(nu)002:5109: tshogs mchod yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK072(nu)002:5111: zhes pas rigs bsdu na slob dpon 'jug pa'i chos
NK072(nu)002:5112: gnyis dang slob ma 'jug pa'i chos bcu drug go
NK072(nu)002:5113: // gsum pa dbang bskur ba la /
NK072(nu)002:5118: dbang grangs dang rim pa la dpyad pa de dbang bzhir bsdu tshul lo //
NK072(nu)002:5121: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK072(nu)002:5122: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK072(nu)002:5123: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK072(nu)002:5124: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK072(nu)002:5126: de yang ji ltar bskur ba'i tshul la /
NK072(nu)002:5127: dbang thams cad la mtshungs ldan dbang rdzas /
NK072(nu)002:5128: bskur thabs la sogs pa don brgyad brgyad de /
NK072(nu)002:5130: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK072(nu)002:5131: rim las skyon yon brgyad ces bya //
NK072(nu)002:5139: nus pa dngos su 'jog byed yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5140: nus dbang du 'du bas grangs bco lnga kho nar 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5141: kha cig zab dbang gsum gcig tu byas te bcu drug tu 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5142: kha cig bum dbang dang gsang dbang gnyis su 'du bar 'dod pa las /
NK072(nu)002:5143: de dag dgag pa la lung rigs man ngag gsum ste /
NK072(nu)002:5145: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK072(nu)002:5148: nus dang phan pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK072(nu)002:5149: brtul zhugs ldan pa'i bu mchog la //
NK072(nu)002:5150: zhes sogs kyis gnod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5151: rig pa ni phan dbang chos can /
NK072(nu)002:5152: khyod las gzhan pa'i dbang grangs brjod pa dgos med du thal /
NK072(nu)002:5153: dbang thams cad khyod kyi nang du 'du ba gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:5154: khyod bdag gzhan gyi don la phan byed kyi dbang yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5155: zab dbang gsum po de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:5156: khyod ngo bo gcig ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:5157: khyod la go 'phang gi thob bya so sor yod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5158: gsum pa yang des khegs so //
NK072(nu)002:5159: man ngag gis kyang gnod de /
NK072(nu)002:5161: ngo bo snod kyi mtshan nyid las //
NK072(nu)002:5162: dbye ba rnam pa lnga ru 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:5165: dbang bco brgyad po de dbang bzhir 'dus ma 'dus kyi bzhed pa sna tshogs yod kyang /
NK072(nu)002:5167: rgyud phyi ma'i dri ba bcu gsum par /
NK072(nu)002:5168: dbang bskur ba yi don yod ci //
NK072(nu)002:5170: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK072(nu)002:5171: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:5172: rnam rtog dri ma dag bya'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:5173: dbang bskur rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK072(nu)002:5176: phan nus kyi dbang lnga po ni bum pa'i dbang du bsdu ste /
NK072(nu)002:5177: de thob pas lam bskyed rim bsgom pa'i snod rung du byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5178: de yang phan dbang thob pas phyi dkyil drang don gyi snod rung du byas pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5179: de'i steng du nyan sgom gyi dbang gnyis kyis nang
NK072(nu)002:5180: rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i lus dkyil la brten pa'i
NK072(nu)002:5181: nges don gyi bskyed rim sgom nus pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5183: rdo rje rgyal po ni rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dngos dang /
NK072(nu)002:5184: 'chad 'phrin gnyis de'i byed las yin pas /
NK072(nu)002:5185: de ltar na rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang thob
NK072(nu)002:5186: nas bum dbang dang rjes su 'brel ba'i lam thams
NK072(nu)002:5187: cad la spyod pa'i bdag por gyur pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5189: rim pa ltar gsang dbang dang /
NK072(nu)002:5191: tshig dbang rnams su 'dus par zad la de gsum thob pas /
NK072(nu)002:5192: rdzogs rim steng 'og gi sgo dang bde ba chen
NK072(nu)002:5193: po de kho na nyid sgom pa'i snod rung du
NK072(nu)002:5194: byas pa'o // gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:5195: dbang rtags rdor dril sbyin pa sogs nas shis pa brjod pas mtha' brgyan pa rnams so //
NK072(nu)002:5196: lnga pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK072(nu)002:5198: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK072(nu)002:5199: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK072(nu)002:5200: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa ni //
NK072(nu)002:5205: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK072(nu)002:5206: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:5207: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK072(nu)002:5208: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:5211: dkyil 'khor bdag po mthong nas ni //
NK072(nu)002:5212: cung zad de ni mi 'grub med //
NK072(nu)002:5213: sdig pa kun las rnam par grol //
NK072(nu)002:5214: dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:5216: lnga pa mi 'da' ba dam tshig la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:5218: gzhan sel ngan song dang theg dman du mi ltung zhing /
NK072(nu)002:5219: don gnyer zhing sa gnyen po la sa bon btab
NK072(nu)002:5220: na 'bras bu smin par 'gyur ba ltar lam dang
NK072(nu)002:5221: / 'bras bu'i gzhi dam tshig gis bzung ste lam gyi 'bad pa don can du byed pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5222: de ltar yang sngags 'chang rnams don yod par bya
NK072(nu)002:5223: ba'i phyir dam tshig chen po 'di ched du brjod
NK072(nu)002:5225: gnyis pa ngo bo'am mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:5226: bsrung bya'i don khyad par can las mi 'da' bar
NK072(nu)002:5227: sdom pa'i sems dpa' sa bon dang bcas pa ste
NK072(nu)002:5229: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK072(nu)002:5230: rmi lam du'ang dam tshig brjod //
NK072(nu)002:5231: dam dpa' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK072(nu)002:5234: sa ma ya'i sgra las don ji ltar bcas pa
NK072(nu)002:5235: las 'da' bar bya ba ma yin pa'i phyir dam
NK072(nu)002:5237: 'da' ka rdo rje dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
