NK072(nu)002:5240: thob byed kyi cho ga dang /
NK072(nu)002:5243: nyams na bskang ba'i thabs so //
NK072(nu)002:5245: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa'i cho ga kho na las thob kyi /
NK072(nu)002:5246: gzhan las ni dam tshig dang sdom pa med de /
NK072(nu)002:5247: brtul zhugs tsam du zad do //
NK072(nu)002:5248: de bas na rgyud sde so so'i dbang chog las so //
NK072(nu)002:5250: khas blangs kyi sngags sdom sbyor ba'i dus rigs lnga'i
NK072(nu)002:5251: sdom bzung lan gsum bzlas pa'i brjod pa gsum pa'i
NK072(nu)002:5252: cha tha la gang bzung ba'i sdom pa de nyid
NK072(nu)002:5255: sdom pa gsum la legs bkod nas //
NK072(nu)002:5256: de la dkyil 'khor bstan par bya //
NK072(nu)002:5258: thun mong gi lung las kyang /
NK072(nu)002:5259: sdom pa ji ltar khas blangs shing //
NK072(nu)002:5260: thob kyi rgyud las ma yin no //
NK072(nu)002:5262: 'on kyang de nyid sngags sdom btags pa ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:5263: slar dbang bskur bas ye shes khong chud kyis thob par bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5264: gal te dbang dus su ye shes dngos su ma
NK072(nu)002:5265: skyes kyang skye rung gi nus pa bzhag pa des
NK072(nu)002:5267: yon tan skye ba'i mgo rtsom pa yin pas rgyud 'gyur ba'i khyad par ste /
NK072(nu)002:5270: dam tshig dang sdom pa thob pa zhes pa'i tha snyad thob cing /
NK072(nu)002:5271: cho gas sems rgyud kyi yon tan dge ba'i sa
NK072(nu)002:5272: bon gsos btab pa'i cha de sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK072(nu)002:5273: gsang ba'i rdo rje gsum 'dzin pa'i cha nas dam
NK072(nu)002:5275: rang rgyud sdom pa'i cha nas sdom pa'ang yin pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:5277: de ltar sum brgya drug cu rnams //
NK072(nu)002:5278: bdag gi rdo rje mchog gsum pos //
NK072(nu)002:5279: log par mi gtong sdom pa'i dngos //
NK072(nu)002:5280: sa bzhi lta bur gsungs pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:5282: dam tshig dang sdom pa gnyis ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad pa lta bu yin kyang /
NK072(nu)002:5284: de yin pas ma khyab ste /
NK072(nu)002:5285: gsang ba bcu'i skabs kyi sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas /
NK072(nu)002:5286: bar du gsang la sgrub par bya //
NK072(nu)002:5287: zhes pa'i skabs kyi dam tshig de sdom pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5288: gsum pa ngo bo la sngags sdom gyi mtshan nyid /
NK072(nu)002:5291: de'i rnam grangs bshad pa dang bzhi las /
NK072(nu)002:5293: sdom byed thabs shes khyad par can gyis zin pa'i
NK072(nu)002:5294: bde ba chen po'i ye shes kyis bsdom bya sgo
NK072(nu)002:5295: gsum phra ba'i bag chags dang mtshan 'dzin gyi rtog
NK072(nu)002:5296: pa sdom par byed pa'i sems pa sa bon dang
NK072(nu)002:5298: rang rgyud dbang bskur ba las gsar du thob pa'i tshul khrims /
NK072(nu)002:5303: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i sngags sdom dang bzhi'i mtshan nyid rim bzhin /
NK072(nu)002:5306: lag bcangs kyi bde ba go rim bzhin du lam
NK072(nu)002:5307: du byas pa'i sgo nas chags pa de dang de
NK072(nu)002:5308: dag par byed pa'i ye shes rang rgyud la 'dzin
NK072(nu)002:5309: pa'i thabs shes kyis sgo gsum gyi bag chags dang
NK072(nu)002:5310: mtshan rtog sdom par byas pa'i sems pa sa bon
NK072(nu)002:5312: rang rgyu rgyud sde rang rang la ltos pa'i dbang las thob pa'i tshul khrims /
NK072(nu)002:5313: bla med kyi sngags sdom gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:5314: dbang po gnyis sbyor bde ba lam du byas pa'i
NK072(nu)002:5315: sgo nas chags pa de dag par byed pa'i ye
NK072(nu)002:5316: shes rang rgyud la 'dzin pa'i thabs shes khyad par
NK072(nu)002:5317: can gyis sgo gsum gyi bag chags dang mtshan rtog
NK072(nu)002:5318: sdom par byed pa'i sems pa sa bon dang bcas
NK072(nu)002:5319: pa gang zhig / rang rgyud bla med kyi dbang las thob pa'i tshul khrims /
NK072(nu)002:5321: bum dbang las thob pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5322: dbang gong ma las thob pa'i sdom pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5323: dang po'i mtshan nyid sbyor ba'i dus su rigs lnga
NK072(nu)002:5324: spyi dang bye brag gi dam tshig khas blangs shing
NK072(nu)002:5325: / dngos gzhi'i dus su bum dbang 'khor bcas bskur ba las gsar thob kyi tshul khrims gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:5326: thabs shes khyad par can bskyed rim gyis tha mal
NK072(nu)002:5327: snang zhen gyi mtshan rtog sdom par byed pa'i sems
NK072(nu)002:5328: pa sa bon dang bcas pa /
NK072(nu)002:5330: rang thob byed kyi rgyu dbang gong ma gang rung /
NK072(nu)002:5331: bskur ba la brten nas gya nom lhar zhen gyi mtshan rtog las skyob pa'i tshul khrims gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:5332: thabs shes khyad par can rang byin rlabs pas sems
NK072(nu)002:5333: gsal stong gi ngo bor sdom pa'i sems pa sa
NK072(nu)002:5334: bon dang bcas pa gsang dbang gi dang /
NK072(nu)002:5336: thabs shes khyad par can kun rdzob zhu bdes mtshon
NK072(nu)002:5337: byed dpe'i ye shes bde stong gi ngo bor sdom
NK072(nu)002:5338: pa'i sems pa sa bon dang bcas pa sher dbang
NK072(nu)002:5339: gi dang de dag gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:5340: thabs shes khyad par can 'pho med bde chen gyi
NK072(nu)002:5341: zung 'jug lhan skyes kyi ye shes mtshon bya don
NK072(nu)002:5342: dam pa'i ngo bor sdom pa'i sems pa sa bon
NK072(nu)002:5343: dang bcas pa dbang bzhi pa'i sngags sdom gyi mtshan
NK072(nu)002:5345: sangs rgyas kun gyi sdom pa ni //
NK072(nu)002:5346: e wam rnam par rab tu gnas //
NK072(nu)002:5347: e wam rnam pas bde chen po //
NK072(nu)002:5348: dbang las yang dag shes par bya //
NK072(nu)002:5350: gnyis pa dam tshig gi che ba la spyod sgo
NK072(nu)002:5351: yangs pa'i dang 'dul sdom thams cad 'dus pa'i che
NK072(nu)002:5353: gnas lugs la rtogs goms kyi gdengs dang ldan na mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig la gnas pa'am /
NK072(nu)002:5354: bla na med pa'i theg par nges pa zhes bya ste /
NK072(nu)002:5355: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa ji ltar spyad kyang phyogs 'dzin gyi blo mi skye ba'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5356: de 'dra ba'i gdengs kyis zin pa'i gang zag des /
NK072(nu)002:5357: las dang nyon mongs pa gang la spyad kyang sgyu
NK072(nu)002:5358: ma'i sprul pa la spyod pa ltar ma zhen pa'i
NK072(nu)002:5359: phyir / de'i sgrib pa dang bag chags mi gsog
NK072(nu)002:5360: pa'i steng du tshogs gnyis rdzogs par 'gyur ba dang
NK072(nu)002:5361: phyir / / so byang phyi rgyud kyi tshul khrims
NK072(nu)002:5362: dang sdom pa thams cad kyang dag par 'gyur ba
NK072(nu)002:5363: phyir / / nyid do // bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK072(nu)002:5364: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang //
NK072(nu)002:5365: byas la mi gsogs tshogs 'gyur te //
NK072(nu)002:5366: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK072(nu)002:5369: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK072(nu)002:5370: 'dul ba'i dbang gi tshul khrims dang //
NK072(nu)002:5371: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK072(nu)002:5372: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK072(nu)002:5374: de gsum yang rnam pa 'gal ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:5375: ngo bo tshang ba dang gnas gyur pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:5377: len dus kyi rnam pa so thar ji srid 'tsho'i bar dang /
NK072(nu)002:5378: byang sdom snying po byang chub la thug gi bar dang /
NK072(nu)002:5379: sngags sdom 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du khas len pa'i khyad par dang /
NK072(nu)002:5380: bslab tshul kyang so thar phyi lus ngag gi spang ba bdun la bslab pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5381: nang yid kyi las gsum gtso bor spong ba'i snying rje la bslab pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5382: rtogs goms kyi gdengs kyis mnyam pa'i don las mi 'da' bar bslab pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5387: so thar ni gzhan la gnod pa gzhi bcas las log pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5388: byang sdom ni de'i steng du phan 'dogs pa'i sbyor ba la zhugs pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5390: de gnyis ka la zhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi mdzad
NK072(nu)002:5391: pa nyams su blangs te mnyam pa chen po ngang
NK072(nu)002:5392: nas gzhan don rtsol med du mdzad pa'i thabs la
NK072(nu)002:5393: mkhas pas thams cad pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5394: bre gsum yod pa'i nang du do tshang ba'i dgos pa med pa ltar /
NK072(nu)002:5395: yon tan yar ldan du 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5396: de ltar yang gsal bkra las /
NK072(nu)002:5397: theg chen dam tshig la gnas na //
NK072(nu)002:5399: bsrung ba med par thub pas na //
NK072(nu)002:5400: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK072(nu)002:5403: gnyis pa gnas 'gyur pas rnam par dag pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:5404: so thar gyi gzhan gnod gzhi bcas spong ba dang
NK072(nu)002:5405: byang sdom gyi gzhan la phan 'dogs pa'i ldog cha
NK072(nu)002:5406: gnyis po de rdzas gong 'phel gyi tshul gyis sngags
NK072(nu)002:5407: kyi sdom rdzas su ngo bo gnas 'gyur zhing /
NK072(nu)002:5408: mnyam pa chen po'i thabs kyis mi zin pa'i tha
NK072(nu)002:5409: ma la snang zhen gyi ldog cha re yod pa
NK072(nu)002:5410: de rtsa ba nas btang nas mnyam pa chen po'i
NK072(nu)002:5411: dam tshig tu so byang gi sdom pa'i ngo bo
NK072(nu)002:5412: de nyid gnas gyur te rnam par dag pa yin
NK072(nu)002:5413: no // de yang bye brag tu bshad na /
NK072(nu)002:5414: de la so thar gyi sdom pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:5415: phas pham bzhi byung na zhig par gsungs pa las /
NK072(nu)002:5416: 'dir gnas lugs rtogs pa'i gdengs kyis zin na ji
NK072(nu)002:5417: ltar spyad kyang mi gos pas ngo bo yar ldan
NK072(nu)002:5418: dang / slar tshogs su 'gyur ba'i phyir yon tan yar ldan te /
NK072(nu)002:5420: byas la mi gsog tshogs 'gyur te //
NK072(nu)002:5421: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK072(nu)002:5424: skye bo phal cher mgo mang bye ba gcod byed kyang //
NK072(nu)002:5425: 'gro kun sprul 'drar rab shes de la 'jigs pa med //
NK072(nu)002:5427: gnyis pa byang sdom dang mi 'gal bar 'dus tshul ni /
NK072(nu)002:5428: nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims kyis rgyud sdom gnyen
NK072(nu)002:5429: po legs spyod dge ba'i tshogs sgrub pa dge ba
NK072(nu)002:5430: chos sdud kyis rtogs pa dang yon tan khyad par
NK072(nu)002:5431: can sgrub / sems can don byed kyi sgo nas
NK072(nu)002:5432: gzhan la phan 'dogs pa gsum du 'du ba las
NK072(nu)002:5433: can sgrub / / 'dir yang las dang nyon mongs
NK072(nu)002:5434: pa la spyod pa ltar yang ma zhen pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:5435: don gyi ngo bo la ci yang byas pa med
NK072(nu)002:5436: pa ni sdom pa'i tshul khrims /
NK072(nu)002:5437: gang ltar spyod kyang sgo gsum rdo rje gsum gyi
NK072(nu)002:5438: phyag rgyas btab ste mi 'da' ba ni dge ba
NK072(nu)002:5439: chos sdud / gzhan don du 'gyur na 'khor ba'i
NK072(nu)002:5440: chos gang yang mi 'dor bar spyod pa ni sems
NK072(nu)002:5443: gang dag sems can don 'gyur ba'i //
NK072(nu)002:5444: thabs de rgyal sras bslab pa'i mchog /
NK072(nu)002:5445: sprin las char chen bab pa yis //
NK072(nu)002:5446: lo tog phun sum tshogs par byed //
NK072(nu)002:5448: de dag la rtsod pa spong ba la /
NK072(nu)002:5453: bum dbang rdzogs par thob pa'i tshe /
NK072(nu)002:5454: sngags sdom rdzogs par thob pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:5455: mchog dbang gong ma gsum la sngags sdom gsar thob med pa'i phyir zer ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:5457: smin byed gzhi'i dbang bzhi bskur bas sngags sdom thob kyang /
NK072(nu)002:5458: slar sdom ldan rang nyid kyis dbang blangs pa'am /
NK072(nu)002:5459: bla mas bskur ba gang rigs la brten nas sngar ma thob pa'i sdom pa gsar thob yod de /
NK072(nu)002:5460: dbang bskur re re thob pa'i tshe gong 'phel du 'gro bas /
NK072(nu)002:5461: ji tsam 'phel ba'i cha de gsar thob yin pa'i phyir zer ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:5465: sdom pa 'og ma gnyis gong mar gnas gyur pa mi 'thad de /
NK072(nu)002:5467: so thar gyi pham pa bzhi 'chab bcas spang ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:5468: byang sdom gyi sems can la 'tshe ba cha bcas
NK072(nu)002:5469: las ldog nas gzhan la phan 'dogs pa'i ldog cha
NK072(nu)002:5470: gnyis po de / 'dir sngags sdom gyi spyad par
NK072(nu)002:5471: bya ba'i dam tshig lnga dang dngos su 'gal ba'i
NK072(nu)002:5472: gnyis po de / phyir zer ro // gnyis pa de dag dgag pa la lung rigs gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:5475: bla ma btsal la dbang bzhi blangs //
NK072(nu)002:5476: de yi sdom pa gsum ldan 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:5477: zhes pa la sogs kyis gnod do //
NK072(nu)002:5479: mchog dbang gong ma ma thob la /
NK072(nu)002:5480: bum dbang rdzogs par thob pa'i gang zag de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:5481: khyod rdzogs rim gyi sngags sdom pa'i gang zag du thal /
NK072(nu)002:5482: khyod sngags sdom rdzogs par thob pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:5483: bum dbang rdzogs par thob pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5486: de thob byed kyi mchog dbang gong ma ma thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5488: smin byed gzhi'i dbang bzhi thob pa'i gang zag de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:5489: khyod rim gnyis sgom pa la dbang ba'i gang zag ma yin par thal /
NK072(nu)002:5490: khyod la sngar ma thob pa'i sngags sdom rigs mi 'dra ba gsar du thob rgyu yod pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5491: dbang gi go ma phye bar lam la bslab par ma gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5495: khyod rgyud smin zin pa'i gang zag yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5499: ji ltar rma dang zas la de dag gis //
NK072(nu)002:5500: gzag dang spyad du rung bas smin 'dod ltar //
NK072(nu)002:5501: de phyir rten 'dir phyogs gnyis zhi ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:5502: yongs su spyad pa nyid du smin pa bstan //
NK072(nu)002:5503: zhes phar phyin theg par sbyor lam thob nas rten de nyid la mthong spangs spang rung dang //
NK072(nu)002:5504: mthong lam skye rung la smin pa'i tshad du 'jog pa ltar /
NK072(nu)002:5505: 'dir yang bla med kyi theg pa 'dir zhugs nas tshe 'di nyid la spangs bya spang rung dang /
NK072(nu)002:5506: thob bya mchog gi dngos grub thob rung gi nus pa thob pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5507: des na dbang thob pa nyid rgyud smin pa'i tshad de /
NK072(nu)002:5508: chu lud drod gsher 'dzom dus zhing la sa bon thob pa bzhin no //
NK072(nu)002:5510: sngar rgyud la yod pa'i sngags sdom gyi rgyun de
NK072(nu)002:5511: nyid phyis lam dbang bskur ba re re thob pa'i
NK072(nu)002:5513: ji tsam 'phel ba'i cha de gsar thob yin mod /
NK072(nu)002:5514: 'on kyang thob bya dbang gi ngo bo rigs mthun
NK072(nu)002:5515: phyin chad sdom pa rigs mi 'dra ba dang ngo
NK072(nu)002:5516: bo tha dad du 'jug pa'ang med pas dngos gzhi
NK072(nu)002:5518: dbang bzhi dang po de la smin byed kyi dbang
NK072(nu)002:5519: zhes sngags sdom gsar du thob byed kyi dbang yin
NK072(nu)002:5520: zhing / phyi ma rnams la'ang rang skal gyis smin
NK072(nu)002:5521: par byas pa'i cha re yod kyang smin byed dang
NK072(nu)002:5522: sdom pa gsar thob kyi tha snyad mi sbyor te
NK072(nu)002:5523: zhing / / smin tshul de tsam zhig sangs rgyas ma thob kyi bar du 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5524: lugs gsum pa la lung dang rnal lan gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:5527: rdo yi rigs kyi bye brag zhig /
NK072(nu)002:5528: bzhu bas lcags dang zangs dngul 'byung //
NK072(nu)002:5529: gser 'gyur rtsi yi dngos po yis //
NK072(nu)002:5530: kun kyang gser du bsgyur bar byed //
NK072(nu)002:5531: de bzhin sems kyi bye brag gis //
NK072(nu)002:5532: rigs can gsum gyi sdom pa yang //
NK072(nu)002:5537: de ltar 'og ma rnams dang rnam pa 'gal ba
NK072(nu)002:5538: ltar snang yang lta ba rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin
NK072(nu)002:5539: goms pa dang / thabs mkhas kyi spyod pas zin
NK072(nu)002:5540: pa'i gnad kyis mi 'gal bar 'og ma'i sdom pa
NK072(nu)002:5541: yar ldan du rdzogs pa yin te /
NK072(nu)002:5542: rgyu mtshan nyan thos kyi dge slong la /
NK072(nu)002:5543: pham bzhi 'chab bcas byung na so thar gyi sdom pa zhig par gsungs pa las /
NK072(nu)002:5544: 'dir mi tshangs spyod la bdag dang yul lha yab yum du gsal ba lha'i 'du shes /
NK072(nu)002:5545: mkha' gsang rdo rje pad+mara shes pa sngags kyi 'dus
NK072(nu)002:5546: shes kyis gzhi'i yan lag ma tshang thabs 'dis bde
NK072(nu)002:5547: ba chen po'i ye shes bsgrub par bya'o //
NK072(nu)002:5548: rnam pa chos kyi 'du shes kyis bsam pa'i yan lag ma tshang /
NK072(nu)002:5549: byed pa sdom pa'i thabs mkhas kyi spyod pas zin
NK072(nu)002:5550: cing chags pa'i ro ye shes su gsal bas mthar
NK072(nu)002:5551: thug gi yan lag ma tshang ba'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:5552: chos thams cad sems nyid kyi rang snang du shes
NK072(nu)002:5553: pas rmi lam du spyad pa ltar nyes pas mi
NK072(nu)002:5554: gos shing / 'dzag med kyi ye shes 'grub sogs
NK072(nu)002:5555: kyi don du 'gyur bas dgag dgos gnad gcig pa'i
NK072(nu)002:5557: 'di nyid las ma chags pa la chags pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5558: chags pa nyid na chags pa med //
NK072(nu)002:5559: de ni tshangs mchog rgyal po ste //
NK072(nu)002:5560: shin tu chags pa chen po yin //
NK072(nu)002:5562: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK072(nu)002:5563: sgyu mar snang ba mig yor tshul //
NK072(nu)002:5564: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK072(nu)002:5565: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK072(nu)002:5567: ye shes rgyas pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK072(nu)002:5568: ji ltar sgyu ma'i mkhan po dag /
NK072(nu)002:5569: rang gi sprul pa'i sgyu ma la //
NK072(nu)002:5570: dge dang mi dge 'du byed pa //
NK072(nu)002:5571: nyes pa gang gis mi gos ltar //
NK072(nu)002:5572: thabs la mkhas pas rnam par spyod //
NK072(nu)002:5574: yang kha cig sdom gsum gnas gyur ngo bo gcig
NK072(nu)002:5575: tu yod pa mi 'thad zer ba lung rigs gnyis
NK072(nu)002:5576: kyis dgag ste / lung ni 'di nyidalasa /
NK072(nu)002:5577: ji bzhin nyid dang 'dul ba'i thabs //
NK072(nu)002:5578: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK072(nu)002:5579: ma lus rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK072(nu)002:5582: gsum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyud kyi gzhan la phan pa sgrub pa'i sems dpa' de chos can /
NK072(nu)002:5583: khyod gzhan la gnod pa spong ba'i de dang /
NK072(nu)002:5584: sngags kyi dam tshig la bslab pa'i sems dpa' gnyis ka yin te /
NK072(nu)002:5585: khyod de gnyis dang ngo bo bdag gcig tu gnas pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5586: sdom pa gsum gyi ldog pa 'gal ba yin te /
NK072(nu)002:5587: dper na bsam pa sems bskyed kyis zin pas cho
NK072(nu)002:5588: ga nyan thos kyi lugs ltar blangs pa'i theg chen
NK072(nu)002:5589: so thar ram nyan thos kyi dge slong gi sdom
NK072(nu)002:5590: pa nyid slar sems bskyed blangs pas der gnas gyur
NK072(nu)002:5591: pa'i rgyud kyi sdom pa gang yin kyang rung ste
NK072(nu)002:5592: / de kun slong byang chub sems kyi ldog pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5593: sdom pa'i ldog pa gnyis yod pa las /
NK072(nu)002:5594: snga ma tshe 'phos pa'i dus du mi gtong ste /
NK072(nu)002:5595: de byang sems kyi sdom pa'i gtong rgyu ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5596: phyi ma sdom pa khas blangs pa'i dus kyi ldog
NK072(nu)002:5597: cha ni tshe 'phos pa'i dbang gis gtong ste dge
NK072(nu)002:5598: slong gi sdom pa de ji srid 'tsho'i mtha' can
NK072(nu)002:5599: gyi sdom pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK072(nu)002:5601: theg chen so sor thar yin yang //
NK072(nu)002:5602: dge slong la sogs sdom pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:5603: ldog pa shi ba'i tshe na gtong //
NK072(nu)002:5604: byang chub sems kyi ldog pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:5607: sdom pa gsum gyi sems dpa' ldog pa tha dad
NK072(nu)002:5608: pa gsum po de rnams skye 'jig gnas gsum dus
NK072(nu)002:5610: ji ltar khas blangs pa ltar gnas 'jig byed pa'i rang ldog ma 'dres pa'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:5611: gsum ldan gyi rgyud kyi sdom pa snga ma rnams
NK072(nu)002:5612: phyi ma dang ngo bo gcig phyi ma snga ma
NK072(nu)002:5613: dang / gnas 'gyur ngo bo gcig pa ma yin te /
NK072(nu)002:5614: snga ma snga ma las phyi ma phyi ma rgya che ba'i phyir dang /
NK072(nu)002:5615: phyi ma blangs tshe sngar gyi sdom pa'i rdzas rgyun
NK072(nu)002:5616: ma yin pa'i sdom rdzas gsar pa du ma zhig
NK072(nu)002:5617: skye ba yod dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5618: de la kha cig gsum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyud kyi dge slong gi sdom pa chos can /
NK072(nu)002:5619: de'i rgyud kyi byang sdom dang sngags sdom du thal /
NK072(nu)002:5620: de dang der gnas gyur pa'i phyir ro zer na /
NK072(nu)002:5621: lung rigs gnyis kyis gnod byed /
NK072(nu)002:5622: lung ni gsang ba spyod pa'i rgyud las /
NK072(nu)002:5623: dper na rdo las zangs su 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:5624: zangs las gser gyi rnam pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:5625: zangs kyi dus na rdo med la //
NK072(nu)002:5626: gser du gyur pas zangs mi snang //
NK072(nu)002:5627: rig 'dzin nang gi dge slong la //
NK072(nu)002:5628: gnyis po gnas pa nyid du ni //
NK072(nu)002:5629: sangs rgyas nyid kyis ma gsungs so //
NK072(nu)002:5630: zhes pas gnod la rigs pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:5631: kun gzhi'i rnam shes chos can /
NK072(nu)002:5632: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes su thal /
NK072(nu)002:5633: de der gnas gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5635: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK072(nu)002:5636: yan lag lnga tshan gnyis te bco lnga dang /
NK072(nu)002:5637: de las spros na sum brgya drug cur dbye ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:5638: mtha' yas par spro ba la sogs pa rnams so //
NK072(nu)002:5639: bzhi pa nyams na bskang ba'i thabs ni /
NK072(nu)002:5641: kun tu nyams pa chen po dang //
NK072(nu)002:5642: rtsa ba nyams dang yan lag nyams //
NK072(nu)002:5643: de bzhin bzlas nyams zhar nyams lnga //
NK072(nu)002:5645: de nyid bskang bas rdzogs par 'gyur ba'i phyir 'og ma dag las 'phags so //
NK072(nu)002:5646: de'ang nyan thos pa ni pham pa 'chab bcas byung
NK072(nu)002:5647: na gsor mi rung bas rdza be'u chags pa dang
NK072(nu)002:5648: 'dra la / byang sems ni gser dngul gyi snod
NK072(nu)002:5649: chag pa mgar bas byar rung ba ltar dge ba'i
NK072(nu)002:5650: bshes gnyen la brten nas nyams pa gsor rung bar
NK072(nu)002:5651: 'dra la / bzhed do // 'dir ni gser gyi
NK072(nu)002:5652: snod gzhom pa rang gis rtsol bas srong thub pa
NK072(nu)002:5653: ltar gzhan la ma brten par rang stobs kyis gsor
NK072(nu)002:5654: 'dra la / bzhed do // rung ba ste / dgong 'dus las /
NK072(nu)002:5655: gang de bskang bar bya ba yang //
NK072(nu)002:5656: las dang rdzas dang 'dun pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:5657: ting nge 'dzin dang de nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:5659: lnga pa nyams pa'i skyon ni /
NK072(nu)002:5661: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK072(nu)002:5662: sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:5664: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK072(nu)002:5665: 'bras bu med cing ngan song ltung //
NK072(nu)002:5669: rgyal ba'i rig pa 'dzin pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:5671: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK072(nu)002:5672: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlabs //
NK072(nu)002:5673: bde gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs //
NK072(nu)002:5674: 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK072(nu)002:5676: drug pa rol pa phrin las la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:5679: tshar bcad pa'i sgo nas bdag gzhan gyi don sgrub pa'i bya ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:5681: bdag gzhan don sgrub phrin las te //
NK072(nu)002:5682: de'ang zhi bas phyi ru nad gdon dang //
NK072(nu)002:5683: nang du mtshan rtog zhi bar byed //
NK072(nu)002:5684: rgyas pas phyi ru 'khor dang longs spyod /
NK072(nu)002:5685: nang du tshe bsod nyams rtogs 'phel zhing rgyas par byed /
NK072(nu)002:5686: dbang gis phyi ru gang dbang du sdud par 'dod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5687: nang du rang sems la dbang thob par byed /
NK072(nu)002:5688: mngon spyod kyis phyi ru dgra bgegs dang nang nyon mongs pa phra rags 'joms pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:5690: zug rngu phyi nang gi phyir dang //
NK072(nu)002:5691: spel bya gnyis po 'phel phyir dang //
NK072(nu)002:5692: dgug dbang bzhi po bsdu phyir dang //
NK072(nu)002:5693: gdug pa rnam gnyis 'joms phyir dang //
NK072(nu)002:5695: gnyis pa ngo bo'i mtshan nyid ni tshad med pa
NK072(nu)002:5696: gzhi'i rgyu las byung zhing thabs shes khyad par can
NK072(nu)002:5697: gyis zin pa'i sgo nas gtso bor gzhan don sgrub
NK072(nu)002:5698: pa'i thabs mkhas kyi mdzad spyod do //
NK072(nu)002:5700: phyi rol tshad med nyid las bzhi //
NK072(nu)002:5703: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i phrin las gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:5705: don bya ba'i yul byed pa'i phrin las /
NK072(nu)002:5706: bya thabs kyi rnam grangs so //
NK072(nu)002:5708: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad yin la /
NK072(nu)002:5709: de yang dmigs bsal gud du phye na /
NK072(nu)002:5715: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun gyis grub pa dang lnga'o //
NK072(nu)002:5718: mchod rten phyag rgya'i sgo dang ni //
NK072(nu)002:5719: hom bro glu dang rdzas kyi bya //
NK072(nu)002:5722: don gnyis mi 'grub pa la sogs pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:5724: don gnyis mi 'grub de yi skyon //
NK072(nu)002:5727: de las bzlog pas rang gzhan gyi don 'grub pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5729: de las bzlog pa'i tshul ldan pa //
NK072(nu)002:5730: yon tan nyid du shes par bya //
NK072(nu)002:5732: bdun pa don du gnyer ba sgrub pa la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:5734: gang don du gnyer ba'i bsgrub bya gnyis mngon du 'gyur ba'i chad du ste /
NK072(nu)002:5736: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NK072(nu)002:5737: bdag gzhan don thob bzhi yi phyir //
NK072(nu)002:5739: gnyis pa ngo bo'am mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:5740: mchog thun gyi dngos grub rnam gnyis gang rung sgrub pa'i thabs khyad par can no //
NK072(nu)002:5742: sid+d+hi'i sgra las dngos grub ste bsgrub bya'o //
NK072(nu)002:5743: sa d+ha n+aa'i sgra las kun tu len pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5744: 'dod pa'i don len cing thob par byed pa'am sgrub par byed pas na sgrub pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5747: tshe dang pra dang ro langs dang //
NK072(nu)002:5748: rkang mgyogs mkha' 'gro la sogs pa //
NK072(nu)002:5749: sgrub pas sgrub pa nyid du bshad //
NK072(nu)002:5752: mchog thun gyi sgrub pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:5756: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pas //
NK072(nu)002:5757: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK072(nu)002:5760: bshad rgyud las gsungs pa ltar na khog gzhung las /
NK072(nu)002:5761: yi ge sgyu 'phrul tshogs sgrub dang //
NK072(nu)002:5762: rdo rje sems dang sman sgrub dang //
NK072(nu)002:5763: rigs lnga sgrub dang yum lnga sems //
NK072(nu)002:5764: byin dbab sgrub pa rnam gnyis so //
NK072(nu)002:5767: yon tan 'byung ba'i dngos grub lnga las phran tshegs kyi dngos grub brgyad sgrub pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5768: bshad rgyud las gsungs pa ni khog gzhung las /
NK072(nu)002:5769: ro langs tshe dang pra sgrub dang //
NK072(nu)002:5770: lha chen po dang rgyal po bzhi //
NK072(nu)002:5771: gdug pa klu 'dul rgyal blon gyi //
NK072(nu)002:5772: chung ma dbang du bya ba gnyis //
NK072(nu)002:5773: yul khams ce spyang rkang mgyogs bskrad //
NK072(nu)002:5774: mi snang gzugs sgrub lha klu mo //
NK072(nu)002:5775: rgyal blon dmag dpon zhang blon sgrub //
NK072(nu)002:5779: sgrub pa'i thabs yal bar dor na bsgrub bya'i don mi 'grub pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5781: yal bas mi 'gyangs mi thob bcu //
NK072(nu)002:5785: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brten na //
NK072(nu)002:5786: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:5788: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK072(nu)002:5790: brgyad pa mi g.yo ba ting nge 'dzin la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:5792: rtogs pa'i don la mi yengs par dbang bsgyur bas sems las su rung bar byed pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5794: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK072(nu)002:5795: rtogs pa'i dbang bsgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK072(nu)002:5797: gnyis pa ngo bo'am mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:5798: bsgom bya'i don la mi g.yo bar gnas pa'i sems rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK072(nu)002:5800: gang dang gang du gsal ba'i yid //
NK072(nu)002:5801: ma yengs pa nyid ting 'dzin te //
NK072(nu)002:5804: bsgom bya ngos bzung ba dang /
NK072(nu)002:5805: ji ltar bsgom pa'i thabs so //
NK072(nu)002:5806: dang po la rim pa gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:5807: de gnyis kyi go don ni /
NK072(nu)002:5808: snod bcud tha mal du 'dzin pa spang zhing lam
NK072(nu)002:5809: ma dag pa bdun dang 'bras bu gzugs sku'i rten
NK072(nu)002:5810: 'brel sgrig pa / khyad par rang gi dngos 'bras
NK072(nu)002:5811: thun mong gi dngos grub 'grub par byed pa ni
NK072(nu)002:5812: 'brel sgrig pa / bskyed rim dang / 'pho ba'i
NK072(nu)002:5813: bag chags kyi dri ma sbyong zhing lam dag pa
NK072(nu)002:5814: sa gsum dang 'bras bu lhan cig skyes /
NK072(nu)002:5816: khyad par rang gi dngos 'bras mchog gi dngos grub 'grub par byed pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:5817: rdzogs rim gyi dgos pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5818: snying po'i rgyud phyi ma kha che 'gyur las /
NK072(nu)002:5819: 'jig rten pa yi dngos grub ni //
NK072(nu)002:5820: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas thob //
NK072(nu)002:5822: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas so //
NK072(nu)002:5824: sbyangs bya 'khrul pa glo bur ba kun brtags dang /
NK072(nu)002:5825: sa bon gyi cha gnyis la ltos nas kyang sbyong byed bskyed rdzogs gnyis gsungs te /
NK072(nu)002:5827: ut+parti kra ma'i sgra las drangs na /
NK072(nu)002:5828: ut+parti zhes pa bcos pa'am brtags pa la 'jug la /
NK072(nu)002:5829: gang las bcos shing gdags pa'i gzhi ni rdzogs rim ste /
NK072(nu)002:5831: nish+pan+na kra ma zhes pa'i nish+pan+na ni ma bcos pa'i grub pa dang rdzogs pa la 'jug cing /
NK072(nu)002:5832: gnyis ka'i kra ma ni rim pa ste thabs sam
NK072(nu)002:5833: lam gyi go rim du 'gyur bas bcos shing brtags
NK072(nu)002:5834: pa rjes dpag gi lha'i rnal 'byor 'khor bcas la
NK072(nu)002:5835: bskyed rim dang / bcos ma dang bral ba mngon
NK072(nu)002:5836: sum pa'i lha'i rnal 'byor gyi lam 'khor bcas la
NK072(nu)002:5839: lha yi rnam pa'i sbyor ba yi //
NK072(nu)002:5840: zla ba rdo rje la sogs rim //
NK072(nu)002:5841: bskyed pa'i rim pa zhes su bshad //
NK072(nu)002:5842: rang bzhin grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK072(nu)002:5843: rdzogs pa'i rim pa zhes byar brjod //
NK072(nu)002:5845: de la skye 'phags gnyis kyi lam gyi gnas skabs la /
NK072(nu)002:5846: so skye'i dus su bskyed rim gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:5847: zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan du gyur pa ang os
NK072(nu)002:5848: ing brtags pa las byung ba'i khyad par bzhi ldan
NK072(nu)002:5849: gyi lha sku snang stong ngo //
NK072(nu)002:5851: cho ga'i khyad par rgyud nas gsungs pa'i bskyed chog tshang ba /
NK072(nu)002:5852: rang 'bras kyi khyad par sngags kyi nus pa /
NK072(nu)002:5853: ngo bo'i khyad par zhu bde dang stong nyid kyi rang bzhin /
NK072(nu)002:5854: byed las kyi khyad par dag rdzogs smin gsum tshang ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:5856: zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan du gyur pa khyad par
NK072(nu)002:5857: gsum ldan bcos min gyi lha sku snang stong mi
NK072(nu)002:5858: brtan par gyur pa rgyu'i rdzogs rim gyi dang /
NK072(nu)002:5859: de brtan par gyur pa 'bras bu'i rdzogs rim gyi mtshan nyid do //
NK072(nu)002:5860: rdzogs rim rgyud la skyes zin nas bskyed rim la bslab mi dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK072(nu)002:5861: 'phags lam gyi dus kyi bskyed rim mi 'byung la /
NK072(nu)002:5862: rdzogs rim la slob pa dang mi slob pa'i ye shes gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:5864: 'phags rgyud kyi ye shes gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:5865: zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan du gyur pa'i lha sku kha sbyor /
NK072(nu)002:5867: dag pa gnyis ldan gyi ye shes mthar thug gang zhig /
NK072(nu)002:5868: kha sbyor la sogs pa'i yan lag bdun ldan te /
NK072(nu)002:5869: longs spyod rdzogs dang kha sbyor bde chen rang bzhin med /
NK072(nu)002:5870: snying rjes yongs gang rgyun mi chad dang 'gog pa med /
NK072(nu)002:5871: ces pa'i don de ba tsan+d+rasa longs spyod rdzogs pa ni rnam pa thams cad pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5872: kha sbyor ni stong nyid snying rje zung 'jug go //
NK072(nu)002:5873: bde chen ni gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa med pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5874: rang bzhin med pa ni skye ba med pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5875: snying rjes yongs gang ni mi 'gyur bde ba'o //
NK072(nu)002:5876: rgyun mi chad pa ni rgyun gyis rtag pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5877: 'gog pa med pa ni chad pa med pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5879: de yang 'bras bu'i rdzogs rim yin na /
NK072(nu)002:5880: gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi zlas phye ba'i 'bras bu yin pas ma khyab ste /
NK072(nu)002:5882: ye shes kyi sku 'grub pa'i so skye'i lam gyi
NK072(nu)002:5883: rdzogs rim de 'bras bu'i rdzogs rim yin pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:5886: sbyang bya 'khor ba'i chos sna tshogs par snang ba
NK072(nu)002:5887: 'di dag srid par skye ba blangs pa la brten
NK072(nu)002:5888: nas 'char bas 'khor ba'i chos kyi gtso bo skye
NK072(nu)002:5889: gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong ba dang bstun nas /
NK072(nu)002:5890: bskyed rim sgom tshul bzhi ste /
NK072(nu)002:5892: skye gnas bzhi po dag bya'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:5893: bskyed pa'i de bzhin rnam pa bzhi //
NK072(nu)002:5894: spros can spros dang spros pa med //
NK072(nu)002:5895: shin tu spros pa med bzhi'o //
NK072(nu)002:5897: rdzogs rim ni thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo la brten pa la sogs pa rnams /
NK072(nu)002:5899: ting 'dzin med na lta ba'i go yul bzang kyang 'grub par mi 'gyur te /
NK072(nu)002:5902: rgya mtsho 'jings kyi pha bong ltar //
NK072(nu)002:5903: bskal par lam la 'bungs byas kyang //
NK072(nu)002:5904: don med snying po bskam pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:5907: bsgrub bya gang yang ting nge 'dzin gyis 'grub pa'i phyir te /
NK072(nu)002:5909: bsgrub pa'i gtsor ni ting 'dzin pas //
NK072(nu)002:5912: dgu pa gnas su stob pa mchod pa drug las /
NK072(nu)002:5914: gzhan sel sgrib pa 'byangs zhing nyams chag skong /
NK072(nu)002:5915: don gnyer lha mnyes pas tshogs rdzogs shing las dang
NK072(nu)002:5916: dngos grub sogs bdag gzhan gyi don 'grub pa'i phyir
NK072(nu)002:5918: bdag gzhan don rjogs mnyes skong ba //
NK072(nu)002:5921: tshogs gnyis rdzogs phyir mchod pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:5923: gnyis pa ngo bo'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:5924: bkur bya'i yul du gyur pa rnams sgo gsum gyis bkur zhing /
NK072(nu)002:5925: yo byad stobs pa'i sgo nas kyang mnyes byed pa'i rigs gnas te /
NK072(nu)002:5927: bya byed bya ba byed 'dus pas //
NK072(nu)002:5928: dgyes tshim 'gyur ba'i dngos po nyid //
NK072(nu)002:5931: p+au dza'i sgra las mchod pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5932: dge las thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba'i phyir bskyed par byed pa'i don dang /
NK072(nu)002:5933: yang dang yang du dgyes pa bskyed pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5934: bkur ba'i don gyi gnas su stob pa'i phyir mchod pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5936: gnas su stob phyir mchod pa ste //
NK072(nu)002:5940: yongs su bsngo ba'i dang 'bras bu la dmigs pa'i dang /
NK072(nu)002:5942: dang po gsum ni rim par 'phags pa mchod pa dang /
NK072(nu)002:5943: thar pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba'i mchod pa rnams ni 'jig rten las 'das pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5944: de las gzhan pa rnams ni 'jig rten pa'o //
NK072(nu)002:5945: bzhi pa dngos po'i bye brag ni bsam gyis mi khyab kyang /
NK072(nu)002:5946: mdor bsdus zhi khro'i mchod pa bcu bzhi sdoms su ston na /
NK072(nu)002:5947: gus pas phyag dang phyag rgya gar //
NK072(nu)002:5948: kun mtshan zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol te //
NK072(nu)002:5949: bdud rtsi gtor ma gsang bsnan dang //
NK072(nu)002:5950: lhag pa ting 'dzin sgrol dang sbyor //
NK072(nu)002:5951: 'dod yon rol mo glu ye shes //
NK072(nu)002:5953: de rnams ji ltar 'bud tshul kyang //
NK072(nu)002:5955: rdo rje lha mo rab mdzes ma //
NK072(nu)002:5956: so so'i yo byad rab thogs nas //
NK072(nu)002:5957: nam mkha' khyab par rab sprul zhing //
NK072(nu)002:5958: yo byad rang lus thim pa mchod //
NK072(nu)002:5961: 'chad 'gyur gyi yon tan las ldog pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:5963: de las bzlog dang mi skongs g.yel //
NK072(nu)002:5964: nyams chag mthu byin bral bar 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:5967: dgos ched du bstan pa'i rjes su 'gro ba ste /
NK072(nu)002:5969: thun mong khyad par yon tan ldan //
NK072(nu)002:5971: bcu pa 'ching bzlog sngags dang phyag rgya la drug las /
NK072(nu)002:5974: ting nge 'dzin gyi stongs su gyur pa las dang
NK072(nu)002:5975: dngos grub thob par byed pa'i nus pa bskyed pa
NK072(nu)002:5977: sbyang zhing nye bar bskyed pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:5978: thob bya lnga po rdzogs bya'i phyir //
NK072(nu)002:5980: gnyis pa ngo bo la gnyis las /
NK072(nu)002:5981: dang po sngags kyi ngo bo'am mtshan nyid ni /
NK072(nu)002:5982: thabs shes kyi yi ge 'dus shing grub pa bzhis
NK072(nu)002:5983: byin gyis barlobasa pas mthu can du gyur pa'i rigs
NK072(nu)002:5985: yi ge 'dus pa grub pa bzhi //
NK072(nu)002:5986: mthu can red pa gang yin pa //
NK072(nu)002:5989: rig pa phyag rgya bzhi rdzogs kyi lha'i skur bsal ba las mi 'da' ba'i rigs gnas /
NK072(nu)002:5991: bzhi rdzogs nyid las mi 'da' ba //
NK072(nu)002:5992: gang la snang ba de ngo bo //
NK072(nu)002:5996: ma na ni yid dam shes pa //
NK072(nu)002:5997: tra ya ni skyob pa'i dpung gnyen la 'jug pas /
NK072(nu)002:5998: yid shes bde myur du skyob cing byin rlabs 'byung ba'i phyir sngags te /
NK072(nu)002:6000: man ni yid ces bya ba ste //
NK072(nu)002:6001: tra ni skyob pa nyid du bshad //
NK072(nu)002:6004: mu tra'i sgra las mtshan ma'i don te /
NK072(nu)002:6006: rgyas btab pa las 'da' bar dka' ba'i phyir phyag rgya zhes bya'o //
NK072(nu)002:6011: 'da' dka' ji bzhin mi shigs pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:6012: rgyal po'i phyag rgya mchog gi gnas //
NK072(nu)002:6013: bdag nyid chen po'i mtshan ma'i gzugs //
NK072(nu)002:6014: phyag rgya zhes ni bsgrags pa yin //
NK072(nu)002:6021: dang po spyir sngags la gsang sngags /
NK072(nu)002:6024: de yang thabs shes kyi bdag nyid /
NK072(nu)002:6025: de'i sgo yig 'brur snang bas gsang sngags te ngag
NK072(nu)002:6026: tu brjod par byed pa dang bcas shing shes skyob
NK072(nu)002:6027: kyis log rtog gi gnyen por gyur pa ni gsang
NK072(nu)002:6028: sngags / shes rab ye shes kyi bdag nyid dngos
NK072(nu)002:6029: po'i don rig par byed pa'i las kyi ma rtogs
NK072(nu)002:6030: pa'i gnyen por gyur pa ni rig sngags /
NK072(nu)002:6031: dran pa dang shes rab kyi bdag nyid chos kyi
NK072(nu)002:6032: tshig don mi brjed par 'dzin pa'i las kyis dran
NK072(nu)002:6033: nyams kyi gnyen por gyur pa ni /
NK072(nu)002:6036: dang po lha pho'i dbyibs dang /
NK072(nu)002:6037: phyi ma gnyis lha mo'i gzugs su bzhugs zhes 'byung ngo //
NK072(nu)002:6038: gnyis pa bye brag tu gsang sngags kyi sgor gyur pa'i sngags la /
NK072(nu)002:6040: rtsa ba bskyed dang las sngags dang //
NK072(nu)002:6045: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya dang gsum las /
NK072(nu)002:6047: rtog tshogs thams cad sgyu dra'i dkyil 'khor du ye nas rdzogs pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:6049: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bas mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK072(nu)002:6050: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK072(nu)002:6053: lta ba phyag rgya chen pos tha mal gyi rtog pa la rgyas 'debs par byed pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:6055: phyag rgya chen po'i tshogs mchog ni //
NK072(nu)002:6056: thabs dang shes rab ldan 'byor na //
NK072(nu)002:6057: ma bskyed ma bsgul thams cad kyang //
NK072(nu)002:6058: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK072(nu)002:6061: zhi khro'i lha tshogs gang bsgom yang //
NK072(nu)002:6063: bdun ldan du bsgom pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:6065: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK072(nu)002:6066: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK072(nu)002:6069: sngags dang phyag rgya spangs na gsung gi dam tshig
NK072(nu)002:6070: nyams pas phung zhing 'bras bu med par 'gyur te
NK072(nu)002:6072: ral gri'i so la bzung nyes ltar //
NK072(nu)002:6073: nan tan med pa'i gsang sngags pa //
NK072(nu)002:6078: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK072(nu)002:6079: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK072(nu)002:6080: yid la bsam pa thams cad 'grub //
NK072(nu)002:6082: lam gyi cha rkyen dngos bcu bshad zin to //
NK072(nu)002:6083: bzhi pa rgyud kyi dgos 'brel ni go sla'o //
NK072(nu)002:6085: 'khor rnams la zab mo'i rgyud gces spras kyi sgo
NK072(nu)002:6086: nas gdams shing bstan pa'i snying po de dar zhing
NK072(nu)002:6087: mi nub par bya ba'i phyir gtad pa ste /
NK072(nu)002:6089: nga yi thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK072(nu)002:6090: phyogs bcu kun tu spel ba dang //
NK072(nu)002:6091: de yi gzungs la gtad pa ni //
NK072(nu)002:6092: yid bzhin mdzod 'byor dka' yis gnas //
NK072(nu)002:6093: bstan pa 'dzin par nus pa la //
NK072(nu)002:6094: gsang ba'i snying po mchog tu gtad //
NK072(nu)002:6096: re zhig de tsam zhus nas /
NK072(nu)002:6097: sngon gyi mkhas pa rnams kyi 'grel bshad rnams su
NK072(nu)002:6098: brgal brtags kyi rig pa phra mo'i bshad pa mdzad
NK072(nu)002:6099: pa mi snang bas mtshan nyid kyis mtshon bya la
NK072(nu)002:6100: khyab ma khyab kyi mtha' ma chod cing /
NK072(nu)002:6101: 'gal ba dang ma 'brel ba dang ma rtogs log
NK072(nu)002:6102: rtog sogs kyi skyon mkhas pa'i dbang po rnams kyis
NK072(nu)002:6103: bzod par bzhes nas nyes skyon dag legs par 'chos
NK072(nu)002:6104: 'tshal lo // shin tu rnyed dka' gsang chen rdo rje'i tshig /
NK072(nu)002:6105: dang po'i 'gro la rtog ge rig pa'i lugs //
NK072(nu)002:6106: rnam par phye 'di dpal ldan rgyud rgyal gyi //
NK072(nu)002:6107: gsang chen lam 'dir 'jug la phan phyir dang //
NK072(nu)002:6108: khyad par skyabs mchog bla na med pa gang //
NK072(nu)002:6109: khyab bdag rje drung bzhad pa rdo rje la //
NK072(nu)002:6110: mkha' 'gro'i gsang lung nyid kyis legs bskul ba'i //
NK072(nu)002:6111: bka' lung spyi bor phebs phral gus btud de //
NK072(nu)002:6112: sngon rabs mkhas pa'i rnam bshad dpag med las //
NK072(nu)002:6113: bdag ltas don gzhan brjod par nus min kyang //
NK072(nu)002:6114: rgyud don ji bzhin 'chad la zla bral ba //
NK072(nu)002:6115: dpal ldan bla ma gter bdag gling pa dang //
NK072(nu)002:6116: ngag gi dbang phyug chos dpal rgya mtsho yi //
NK072(nu)002:6117: thugs mtshor 'khyil ba'i rgyud don bdud rtsi'i rgyun //
NK072(nu)002:6118: dad brtson rnga yab rtse mos bcud du blangs //
NK072(nu)002:6119: cung zad myong 'di bskal ba bzang por byas //
NK072(nu)002:6120: gsang chen zab mo byis pa'i spyod yul min //
NK072(nu)002:6121: 'on kyang dam pa'i gsung gi bskul bar brten //
NK072(nu)002:6122: blun pos tshul 'di grong tshig brjod pa'i gtam //
NK072(nu)002:6123: yi ger spel la nongs pa gang mchis bshags //
NK072(nu)002:6124: 'di las rnam dkar dge ba gang thob pa //
NK072(nu)002:6125: de yis mkha' mnyam lus can ma lus kun //
NK072(nu)002:6126: rmad byung lam gyis dri ma spangs sbyangs nas //
NK072(nu)002:6127: rang byung ye shes mngon du rtogs par shog /
NK072(nu)002:6128: ces pa 'di ni skyabs kun 'dus pa'i bdag nyid
NK072(nu)002:6129: rje bla ma blo bzang phrin las dbang po'i mtshan
NK072(nu)002:6130: / gzhan khyab bdag rje drung bzhad pa rdo rje
NK072(nu)002:6131: zhes snyigs dus 'gro ba kun gyi 'dren mchog dam
NK072(nu)002:6133: mkha' 'gro'i gsang lung du 'di ltar byung ste /
NK072(nu)002:6134: h+r+aih rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po gsang ba snying
NK072(nu)002:6135: po ni dus gsum gyi rgyal ba'i dgongs nyams gcig
NK072(nu)002:6138: brgal brtags kyis gtan la 'bebs pa smon lam gyi
NK072(nu)002:6139: mthu grub pa ni chos kyi mdzod 'dzin smin grol
NK072(nu)002:6140: gling du'o // de bas na der de bskul bar bya'o //
NK072(nu)002:6141: yang nas yang du yin no //
NK072(nu)002:6142: zhes lung bstan pa'i don bzhin /
NK072(nu)002:6143: 'di nyid la rigs lam nas drangs pa'i brgal brtags
NK072(nu)002:6144: kyi zin bris zhig rtsom par bgyis shig ces pa'i
NK072(nu)002:6145: bka' lung gnang skyes bzang po dang bcas spyi bor
NK072(nu)002:6146: phebs phral dang du blangs te /
NK072(nu)002:6147: mdo sngags gzhung lugs kyi tshig don ci rigs blo
NK072(nu)002:6148: yul du longs pa'i smin gling grwa pa'i tha shal
NK072(nu)002:6149: ba dge slong d+harma kirtisa rang lo nga bdun pa
NK072(nu)002:6150: bsam gtan gyi thun bar rnams su brtsam pa'i bya
NK072(nu)002:6151: ba zhugs te / chu byi hor zla gnyis pa
NK072(nu)002:6152: dbo zla ba'i dkar phyogs kyi bzang po'i tshes gnyis
NK072(nu)002:6153: gza' tshes phun sum tshogs pa rje bla ma'i dus
NK072(nu)002:6154: dran gyi mchod pa'i nyin rang gi grwa khang du
NK072(nu)002:6155: grub par bgyis pa dge legs su gyur cig //
NK072(nu)002:6156: 'dis kyang bstan pa rin po che dar zhing rgyas pa'i rgyur gyur shog /
